\id JOB
\h Ayub
\toc1 Ayub
\toc2 Ayub
\toc3 Ayub
\mt1 Ayub
\c 1
\s1 Aryaz Ayub
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa din ijj n weryaz di temmurt n Ɛuṣ qqaren as Ayub. Aryaz-a tuɣa ikmeř d amsegged, itteggʷed zi AREBBI u ittḥeyyad x min iǧan d aɛeffan. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Ayub 2:3\x*
\v 2 Ttwarwen as-dd sebɛa n iḥenjiren d třata n tḥenjirin. \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Ayub 42:13\x*
\v 3 Taḥimart n řmař nnes dayes sebɛa-ařaf n wuǧi u teřt-ařaf n iřeɣman d xemsa-mya n tyuyawin n iyenduzen d xemsa-mya n teɣyař, \add arni ɣares\add* abarru n isemɣan. Aryaz-a tuɣa d ameqqran x marra arraw n ccarq.
\m 
\v 4 Iḥenjiren nnes nnumen tteggen ijj n umensi, kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* \add s nnubet nnes\add* deg wass nnes di taddart nnes. Ssekken, ɛarḍen uřa x třata n suyᵉtmatsen ad kidsen ccent u ad kidsen swent.
\v 5 Řami ɛdun wussan n zzardet awarni nnḍen \add zi taddart ɣar taddart nneɣni\add*, issekk Ayub ḥima ad ten issqeddes. Zic ɣar tuffut ikkar uca yiwi din tiɣarṣi n wecmaḍ anect lɛadad n marra \add arrawen nnes\add*. Maɣar Ayub inna: “Ad taɣ xḍan arrawen inu u ḥeyyden x AREBBI deg wuř nsen.” Ammu i igga Ayub řebda. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Ica. 29:1\x*
\b
\s1 Cciṭan ittcetca zi Ayub
\m 
\v 6 Deg ijj n wass usin-dd arraw n AREBBI ḥima ad bedden zzat i SIDI, uca yusa-dd uřa d cciṭan di řwesṭ nsen.
\v 7 Inna SIDI i cciṭan: “Manis i dd-tusid cek?” Yarra-dd cciṭan x SIDI, inna: “Usiɣ-dd zeg wetlaɛ x temmurt, kkiɣ tt marra.” \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Bṭ. 5:8\x*
\v 8 Inna SIDI i cciṭan: “Ma teḥḍid amsexxar inu Ayub? Am netta war iǧi x temmurt: d aryaz ikmeř, iggur nican, itteggʷed AREBBI u ittḥeyyad x min iǧan d aɛeffan!”
\m 
\v 9 Yarra-dd cciṭan x SIDI, inna: “Ma amenni waha itteggʷed Ayub AREBBI?
\v 10 Ma war iǧi d Cek, wenni iggin ijj n useřqi i netta d taddart nnes d marra min ɣares? Aqa tbarked timegga n ifassen nnes uca řmař nnes imɣar aṭṭas di temmurt.
\v 11 Swiẓẓeḍ mɣir afus nnec \add ɣares\add*, ḥada marra min iǧan nnes, ma \add xenni\add* s tidett ad ibeɛɛed x wudem nnec?”
\m 
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i cciṭan: “Xzar, marra min ɣares aqa-t deg ufus nnec. Mɣir war d as swiẓẓiḍ afus nnec waha!” \add Xas uca\add* yuyur cciṭan zi zzat n wudem n SIDI.
\b
\s1 Ayub ittemɛařa ak-d ujarreb n cciṭan
\m 
\v 13 Deg wass min di tuɣa iḥenjiren nnes d yessis ttᵉtten u sessen binu di taddart n umatsen amenzu, imsar,
\v 14 aqa yusa-dd \bd ijj n ureqqas\bd* ɣar Ayub, inna: “Ifunasen tuɣa carrzen u tiɣyař heddant x uɣezdis nsen.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* hejmen ayt n Caba, ksin ten uca nɣin iḥudriyyen s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. Mɣir necc waha inejmen, ḥima ad ac t ɛawdeɣ.”
\m 
\v 16 Umi tuɣa wa ɛad issawař, yusa-dd \bd ijj nneɣni\bd*, inna: “Timessi n AREBBI tewḍa-dd zeg ujenna uca tarɣa deg wuǧi d iḥudriyyen uca tecca i-ten. Mɣir necc waha inejmen, ḥima ad ac t ɛawdeɣ.”
\m 
\v 17 Umi tuɣa wa ɛad issawař, yusa-dd \bd ijj nneɣni\bd*, inna: “Ayt n Ikaldaniyyen ssbedden třata n bandiyyat, hejmen x iřeɣman, ksin ten uca nɣin iḥudriyyen s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. Mɣir necc waha inejmen, ḥima ad ac t ɛawdeɣ.”
\m 
\v 18 Umi tuɣa wa ɛad issawař, yusa-dd \bd ijj nneɣni\bd*, inna: “Iḥenjiren nnec d yessic ccin u swin binu di taddart n umatsen amenzu.
\v 19 Uca xzar, yusa-dd ijj n usemmiḍ iwɛar x tiwa n řexřa, iřqef arebɛa n tɣemmura n taddart uca tewḍa \add taddart\add* x iḥudriyyen d tḥudriyyin uca mmuten nitni. Mɣir necc waha inejmen, ḥima ad ac t ɛawdeɣ.”
\m 
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Ayub, icarreg aseřham nnes, iḥeff azeǧif nnes, iwḍa x temmurt uca ibendeq,
\v 21 inna: “D aɛaryan i dd-usiɣ zeg uɛeddis n yemma u d aɛaryan i din i ɣa dewřeɣ. SIDI iwca, SIDI ikkes, ad ittwabarek Isem n SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 1:21 \xt Amb. 5:14; 1 Tim. 6:7\x*
\v 22 Di man aya marra war ixḍi Ayub ca u war inni min war iɛeddřen x AREBBI.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Cciṭan yarni acetci x Ayub
\m 
\v 1 Deg ijj n wass usin-dd arraw n AREBBI, ḥima ad bedden zzat i SIDI, uca yusa-dd uřa d cciṭan di řwesṭ nsen maḥend ad issbedd ixef nnes zzat i SIDI.
\v 2 Inna SIDI i cciṭan: “Manis i dd-tusid cek? Cciṭan yarra-dd x SIDI, inna: “Usiɣ-dd zeg wetlaɛ x temmurt, kkiɣ tt marra.”
\v 3 Inna SIDI i cciṭan: “Ma teḥḍid amsexxar inu Ayub? Am netta war iǧi x temmurt: d aryaz ikmeř, iggur nican, itteggʷed AREBBI u ittḥeyyad x min iǧan d aɛeffan! Ɛad yarni itteṭṭef di řeṣfayet nnes, x minni cek d ayi tɛarrned ḥima ad t ṣarḍeɣ x walu.”
\m 
\v 4 Yarra-dd cciṭan x SIDI, inna: “Tiřmect s teřmect, \add wah,\add* marra min ɣares ɣar bnadem, ad t iwc i tudart nnes.
\v 5 Swiẓẓeḍ mɣir afus nnec \add ɣares\add* uca ḥada iɣsan nnes d weysum nnes, ma \add xenni\add* netta s tidett war dayek ittceqqaf deg wudem nnec?”
\m 
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i cciṭan: “Xzar, netta deg ufus nnec, maca ejj i-t ad iddar!”
\b
\s1 Tiḥebba yewɛaren řeqqfent Ayyub
\m 
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* yuyur cciṭan zi zzat n wudem n SIDI uca iwta Ayub s tḥebba tiɛeffanin, zi třeqqa n iḍaren nnes ař tqiccet n uceqquf \add n uzeǧif\add* nnes.
\v 8 Netta iksi aceǧiq n tqedduḥt, ḥima ad zzayes iḥekk ixef nnes, uca iqqim di řwesṭ n yiɣɣeḍ.
\v 9 Tenna as temɣart nnes: “Ma ɛad tᵉtteṭṭfed di řeṣfayet nnec? Ini as i AREBBI: ‘D wenni netta!’, uca mmet!”
\v 10 Netta maca inna as: “Am mammec ssawařent temɣarin tibuhařiyyin tessawařed uřa d cem am yicten zzaysent. Ma neccin nkessi řxar zi AREBBI, \add maca\add* war nkessi xenni uřa d řɣar?” S marra man aya Ayub war ixḍi ca s iyencicen nnes.
\b
\s1 Tarzeft n imeddukkʷař n Ayub
\m 
\v 11 Sřin třata n imeddukkař n Ayub marra min xas ikkin d řɣar u nitni usin-dd kuř ijj zi temmurt nnes: Ilifaz zi Tayman, Bildad zi Cuḥa u Ṣufar zi Naɛmat. Ggin ad din uyuren, ḥima ad kides ssḥissfen u ḥima ad dayes ggen uř.
\v 12 Zi řaggʷaj ssgeɛɛden tamuɣři nsen, maca war tt ɛqiřen ca. Nitni ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen uca run. Kuř ijj icarreg aseřham nnes uca ssuysen iɣɣeḍ ɣar ujenna tiwa i izeǧifen nsen.
\v 13 Qqimen ɣares x temmurt, sebɛa n wussan d sebɛa n ǧiyaři. Uřa d ijjen war issiweř uřa d ijj n wawař ɣares, maɣar ẓrin, aqa řeḥriq nnes tuɣa d ameqqran aṭṭas.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Acetci n Ayub
\m 
\v 1 Awarni man aya yarzem Ayub aqemmum nnes, inɛeř ass \add n wexřaq\add* nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Irm. 15:10; 20:14\x*
\m 
\v 2 \bd Ayub\bd* iṭṭef deg wawař, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 3 Ad ifna ass i di dd-ttwaxeřqeɣ,
\m uřa d ǧiřet i di nnan:
\m ‘Ijj n weryaz ittwaksi.’
\m 
\v 4 Ejj ass nni ad idweř d taǧest,
\m ɛemmarṣ war xas ittsseqsi Arebbi
\m zeg ujenna,
\m u war xas tᵉttceɛciɛ tfawt n uziř \add ɛad\add*.
\m 
\v 5 Iři taǧest d tiři n řmewt ad xas arzunt,
\m ejj iseynuten ad zedɣen tiwa nnes.
\m Iři ad xas wḍant tkebbasin s uziř! \f ◼ \fr 3:5 \fk tikebbasin\ft - xmi i ɣa dd-tedweř tfuct u tziri tebbumbes, neqqar: ‘aqa din tikebbasin’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 6 Ad tekkes tkebbast yuǧɣen ǧiřet nni,
\m ejj \add ǧiřet nni\add* war tfarreḥ
\m jar wussan n useggʷas,
\m ejj i-tt war dd-tᵉttis
\m di řeḥsab n iyuren.
\m 
\v 7 Xzar, ejj ǧiřet nni
\m ɛemmarṣ war dd-tᵉttiruw,
\m war dayes ittidef usřiwřew.
\m 
\v 8 Ejj inni issfeṭṭḥen ass,
\m ad t neɛřen,
\m inni ittḥakan ad ssekkaren ‘Liviyatan’. \f ◼ \fr 3:8 \fk inni issfeṭṭḥen ass\ft - ixs ad yini inni iggin taseḥḥart d tagezzant d ɛřam kuř timesřayin tibarcanin war iḥḥřin, uřa d inni ittiraren ak-d řhaycet, qqaren as ‘Liviyatan’. \fk Liviyatan\ft - aqa-t d isem n ict n řhaycet d tameqqrant. Ad taɣ řhaycet-a d ijj n umedya n tgeldit n Miṣra, tammurt n firɛun. Di řweqt nni ař i řexxu aqa din iwdan di Sin u di Dzayer inni ittamnen aqa řḥaycet nni d řeɛdu n tfuct d tziri. Ttxarrṣen aqa řhaycet tegga ad tṣard tafuct d tziri. S uyenni umi temsar ict n tbarrcent n tfuct niɣ n tziri, ffɣen-dd nitni barra ḥima ad ggen ijj n ddriz d ameqqran s taǧunin d ɛřam kuř n řeqcuɛ n nnḥas ḥima ad aẓẓřen x řhaycet maḥend ad tban tfuct d tziri ɛawed. Isem ‘Liviyatan’ nufa i-t ɛawed di Ayub 40:25.\f*
\m 
\v 9 Ejj ad ttwakebbsen itran n tuffut nnes,
\m ejj i-t ad iraja tafawt, řami war din teǧi.
\m Ejj abřiwen n tfawt n řefjar
\m war tt ẓarren! \f ◼ \fr 3:9 \fk abriwen n tfawt n řefjar\ft - di timmura n Ccarq-Ameřwasu ḥessben ayt n cciɛr tafuct am ict n tiṭṭ ɣares abřiwen d timmiwin. Aqa Ayub iqqar deg wawař-a aqa ḥsen tafawt n tfuct ɣar uteffu n wass ɛemmarṣ war dd-tareqq x wass n třařit nnes.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 10 Maɣar netta war ibelleɛ tiwwura
\m n uɛeddis \add n yemma\add*,
\m war iffar řeɣben zzat i tiṭṭawin inu.
\m 
\v 11 Mayemmi war mmuteɣ
\m řami d ayi tuɣa deg uɛeddis \add n yemma\add*,
\m mayemmi war ssuffɣeɣ buḥbeř,
\m řami dd-ffɣeɣ zeg uɛeddis \add n yemma\add*?
\m 
\v 12 Mayemmi d ayi rajan ifadden
\m u mayemmi ibbac,
\m ḥima ad \add daysen\add* ṭṭeḍeɣ?
\b
\m 
\v 13 Xenni iři ad zzřeɣ řexxu, ad ssqareɣ.
\m Iři ad ṭṭṣeɣ.
\m Xenni balak ad ɣari tiři řhudnet
\m 
\v 14 \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d ijeǧiden
\m d imcawaren n temmurt,
\m inni ibnan i yixef nsen arrwinat ixřan,
\m 
\v 15 niɣ \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d řḥukkam
\m nni ɣar iǧa wureɣ,
\m inni iccuren tudrin nsen s nnuqart,
\m 
\v 16 niɣ necc war ttiřiɣ \add ɛad\add*
\m am yijj n weɣray \add n temɣart\add* ssnuffaren t,
\m amecnaw iseyman
\m nni ɛemmarṣ war iẓrin tafawt.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Dinni ssbedden iɛeffanen zi ṣṣdeɛ,
\m dinni ttareyyaḥen
\m inni umi ifna jjehd nsen.
\m 
\v 18 Dinni ttareyyaḥen imeḥbas \add munen\add*,
\m war qqimen ttesřan \add ɛad\add*
\m i tmijja n imzeyyaren \add n isemɣan\add*.
\m 
\v 19 Aqa din ameẓyan d umeqqran,
\m ismeɣ innufseř din zi bab nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Mayemmi temmewc tfawt i řmeskin,
\m u tudart i yinni
\m umi ittwassarzeg řeɛmar nsen,
\m 
\v 21 \add i yinni\add* ittmeẓren di řmewt,
\m maca war tt ufin,
\m inni iɣezzan x \add řmewt\add* ktar
\m x řeknuz innufaren,
\m 
\v 22 inni ifarrḥen aṭṭas
\m ařami dewřen neggzen,
\m u ttɣebban meẓri xmi ttafen anḍeř?
\m 
\v 23 \add Mayemmi temmewc tfawt\add* i weryaz
\m wenni umi ittwassnuffar webrid nnes,
\m \add i weryaz\add* wenni xef ibelleɛ Arebbi
\m zi marra iɣezdisen?
\b
\m 
\v 24 Minzi deg wemcan n weɣrum inu
\m ittas-dd uweḥweḥ inu,
\m iɣuyyan inu ttwazeǧɛen am waman. \x ◘ \xo 3:24 \xt Izhd. 42:4\x*
\m 
\v 25 Minzi tuɣa ttnexřaɛeɣ
\m u amenni dd-iffeɣ
\m min zi tuɣa tteggʷedeɣ, wḍiɣ dayes.
\m 
\v 26 War ɣari řhudnet, war arsiɣ ca
\m u war ttareyyiḥeɣ.
\m Aqa usin-dd imxumbar.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Řhard amezwaru n Ilifaz: Ksi awebbex n Arebbi!
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ilifaz\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Tayman, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Mařa \add ḥed\add* yarzu
\m maḥend ad kik issiweř,
\m ma war tᵉttwaceḍned qaɛ \add s man aya\add*?
\m \add Maca\add* man wen izemmaren
\m ad issbedd řhard \add nnes\add*?
\m 
\v 3 Xzar, tessɣared aṭṭas \add n iwdan\add*
\m u ifassen yarxun tessmeḥḍed i-ten.
\m 
\v 4 Wenni inqarḍen,
\m tessbedded i-t s wawař nnec,
\m u ifadden ifecřen
\m tewcid asen jjehd \add ɛawed\add*.
\m 
\v 5 Maca řexxu imsar aya i cek,
\m tᵉttwaceḍned qaɛ,
\m \add řexxu\add* iřqef i cek aya uca tarejfed.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Ma war teǧi tiggʷudi \add zi Arebbi\add*
\m d řaman nnec
\m u řeṣfayet n ibriden nnec d řayas nnec?
\m 
\v 7 Xemm maca!
\m Man wen ittwahellken am iǧa d amezdag
\m u mani ttwateḥḥan inni igguren nican?
\m 
\v 8 Ẓriɣ aqa inni icarrzen ddeǧ
\m d yinni izarrɛen řeɣben,
\m ad t mjaren \add ɛawed\add*. \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Ayub 15:35; Izhd. 7:15; Awřn. 22:8; Ica. 59:4; Ḥuc. 10:13; Gal. 6:7, 8\x*
\m 
\v 9 Ad hellken zeg usuḍi n nnefs n Arebbi,
\m ad fnan s usuḍi zeg wenzaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Ica. 11:4\x*
\m 
\v 10 Zzhir n weyrad
\m d tmijja n yizem ameẓyan \add ad ttwassbedden\add*
\m u tiɣmas n wayraden imeẓyanen
\m ad ttwarẓant.
\m 
\v 11 Ad ihellek wayrad,
\m minzi war yufi zzardet,
\m tarwa n tayradt ad ttwabezzɛen.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Di tnuffra yiweḍ ayi-dd ijj n wawař,
\m amezzuɣ inu iṭṭef zzayes řeḥmis,
\m 
\v 13 \add am tuɣa ɣarrqeɣ\add*
\m deg ixarriṣen issiggʷiden
\m zeg iweḥḥan n ǧiřet,
\m řami dd-iwḍa yiḍeṣ yuǧɣen x iwdan.
\m 
\v 14 Teřqef ayi tiggʷudi d tarjijit,
\m marra iɣsan inu nnxeřɛen.
\m 
\v 15 Ijj n buḥbeř iḥrara x uɣembub inu,
\m issbedd acuwwaf di arrimet inu.
\m 
\v 16 Netta ibedd,
\m \add maca\add* war ɛqiřeɣ x tefras nnes.
\m Ijj n waddud \add ibedd\add* zzat i tiṭṭawin inu.
\m \add Xenni\add* sřiɣ i tmijja tᵉttemtim, teqqar:
\b
\m 
\v 17 ‘Ma \add izemmar\add* ijj n bnadem
\m ad yiři isegged x Arebbi?
\m Ma \add izemmar\add* ijj n weryaz
\m ad yiři iṣfa x Wenni t iggin?’
\m 
\v 18 Xzar, war ittciři
\m uřa x imsexxaren nnes,
\m igga řɛib \add ́ɛad\add* ak-d lmalakat nnes
\m umi weddarent. \x ◘ \xo 4:18 \xt Ayub 15:15; 2 Bṭ. 2:4\x*
\m 
\v 19 Mahu inni izeddɣen di tudrin n ucař,
\m inni ɣar teǧa tɛejjajt d dsas nsen.
\m Aqa ad ttwařebzen amezwar x tcinda.
\m 
\v 20 Zi tuffut n ṣṣbeḥ ař tameddit
\m ad ttwafartken.
\m Břa i iwca \add bnadem\add* taynit \add i man aya\add*,
\m ad fnan i řebda.
\m 
\v 21 Ma war dd-tᵉttwaqřeɛ ɣarsen
\m tesɣunt n uqiḍun nsen \add n arrimet\add*?
\m Ad mmten, \add maca\add* war iǧi di tiɣit.
\b
\b
\c 5
\m 
\v 1 Řaɣa maca! Ma din ca n yijjen
\m i xak dd ɣa yarren?
\m Ɣar man zeg imqeddasen i ɣa tsewḍed?
\m 
\v 2 Minzi axeyyeq ineqq abuhaři,
\m u tusmi tneqq aqubbani.
\m 
\v 3 Ẓriɣ ijj n ubuhaři iḍřeq i weẓwar,
\m \add maca\add* x ict n řɣefřet
\m tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad neɛřeɣ tazeddiɣt nnes.
\m 
\v 4 Iggʷejen iḥenjiren nnes x usenjem,
\m ttwaddzen ɣar tewwart \add n tendint\add*
\m uca war tuɣi din wi ten i ɣa ifekken,
\m 
\v 5 \add umi\add* icca umehyuf ṣṣabet nnes
\m - \add wah, wanita\add* issuffeɣ i-t-i-dd \add ɛad\add*
\m zeg isennanen -
\m u isarḍ uxewwan agřa nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Maɣar war iǧi zi tɛejjajt
\m i zi dd-ittekk řɣar
\m u zi temmurt war dd-tɣemmi tamara,
\m 
\v 7 maca bnadem
\m d wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen i tamara,
\m am geɛɛdent tceɛɛařin n tmessi
\m maḥend ad ḍwint.
\m 
\v 8 Mři ufiɣ ad arzuɣ ɣar Arebbi,
\m ad ssiwḍeɣ tamesřact inu ɣar AREBBI,
\m 
\v 9 wenni itteggen timesřayin timeqqranin,
\m war din wi tent i ɣa ifehmen,
\m \add ittegg\add* lmuɛjizat
\m i war izemmar ad ttwaḥesbent. \x ◘ \xo 5:9 \xt Ayub 9:10; Izhd. 72:18; Rum. 11:33\x*
\m 
\v 10 Issakkʷaḍ anẓar x wudem n temmurt,
\m uca issekka aman x wudem n iyyaren, \x ◘ \xo 5:10 \xt Izhd. 104:10\x*
\m 
\v 11 ḥima ad issgeɛɛed imwaḍɛen,
\m uca inni iceḍnen ad ten ssuɛřan ɣar řaman. \x ◘ \xo 5:11 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:7; Izhd. 113:7, 8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 Netta issbeṭṭeř
\m ixarriṣen n iḥraymiyyen,
\m \add ařami\add* ifassen nsen
\m war zemmaren ad ggen walu. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Naḥ. 4:9; Izhd. 33:10; Ica. 8:10\x*
\m 
\v 13 Imiɣisen imenneɛ i-ten
\m di teḥraymect nsen,
\m ittwassbeṭṭeř ccwar n iḥraymiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 5:13 \xt 1 Kur. 3:19\x*
\m 
\v 14 Deg uziř mmsagaren ak-d taǧest
\m uca di ṭṭḥa n uziř
\m ttfafan am ttfafan \add di\add* ǧiřet. \x ◘ \xo 5:14 \xt Aɛwd. 28:29\x*
\m 
\v 15 Netta issenjam zi ssif \add i dd-itteffɣen\add*
\m zeg uqemmum nsen,
\m uřa d amezřuḍ zeg ufus n wenni ijehden.
\m 
\v 16 Ammu i yeǧa řayas i umezřuḍ
\m uca ddeǧ ad ibelleɛ aqemmum nnes. \x ◘ \xo 5:16 \xt Izhd. 107:42\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 Xzar, sseɛd n weryaz
\m wenni iseggem Arebbi.
\m \add S uya\add* war tesseḥqiri ca
\m ttarbiyyet n Umzemmar x kuřci! \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt Awřn. 3:11, 12; Ɛbr. 12:5; Yaɛ. 1:12; Asa. 3:19\x*
\m 
\v 18 Maɣar Netta issyezzim ayi
\m s ijj n uyezzim itteqqsen
\m uca \add xenni\add* ittcedda,
\m iccat uca \add xenni\add* ifassen nnes ssgenfan. \x ◘ \xo 5:18 \xt Aɛwd. 32:39; 1 Ṣm. 2:6; Ḥuc. 6:1\x*
\m 
\v 19 Di setta n řeḥṣarat ad cek ifekk,
\m di tenni wiss sebɛa war cek iřeqqef řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt Izhd. 91\x*
\m 
\v 20 Di řaẓ ad cek issenjem zi řmewt,
\m deg umenɣi zi tiyyita n ssif.
\m 
\v 21 Ad tiřid di řaman
\m zzat i urekkuḍ n yiřes,
\m war tᵉtteggʷeded ca zeg wareddeǧ
\m mařa yusa-dd.
\b
\m 
\v 22 X wareddeǧ d řaẓ
\m tzemmared ad tḍeḥced,
\m zi řewḥuc n řexřa n temmurt
\m war tᵉtteggʷeded,
\m 
\v 23 maɣar tqeḍɛed řɛahd ak-d iẓra n yeyyar,
\m \add xenni\add* řewḥuc n řexřa
\m ad kidek ddaren di řehna. \x ◘ \xo 5:23 \xt Ḥuc. 2:20\x*
\m 
\v 24 Ad targbed aqa řehna d aqiḍun nnec,
\m ad tbeqqced tazeddiɣt nnec,
\m ad tafed war cek ittxeṣṣi walu.
\m 
\v 25 Cek ad tessned aqa arraw nnec aṭṭas,
\m u ddurryet nnec
\m am wefsu \add aziza\add* n temmurt.
\m 
\v 26 Ad tadfed ɣar wenḍeř di tewsar,
\m am mammec ssgeɛɛden
\m ijj n uɛurric n tqebbiḍin n imendi
\m \add ɣar unedrar\add* di řḥař nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 27 Xzar, man aya, aqa neccin narzu dayes,
\m ammu i teǧa!
\m Seř ɣares, ssen i-t deg yixef nnec!
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Ilifaz: Afeqqus nnes
\m 
\v 1 Yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 A, mři weznen řhemm inu,
\m mři jjin ad igeɛɛed
\m x řmizan s tnayen n ṭṭawyat
\m uřa d řeɣben inu akides imun!
\m 
\v 3 Maɣar řexxu aqa-t idqeř x yejdi n řebḥur,
\m x uya \add tteffɣen\add* wawařen inu
\m nhřa axemmem. \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Awřn. 27:3 \x*
\m 
\v 4 Maɣar \add nnuɣent\add* dayi fřitcat
\m n Umzemmar x kuřci,
\m ařami buḥbeř inu isess arrhaj nsent.
\m Inexřiɛen zi Arebbi kkaren-dd akidi. \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt Izhd. 38:2, 3\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 Ma issḥundrut weɣyuř n řexřa
\m ɣar arbiɛ aziza?
\m Niɣ issmuhrut ufunas ɣar heddu nnes?
\m 
\v 6 Macca břa aředdi
\m ma ad tt yecc \add bnadem\add* břa tameǧaḥt?
\m Niɣ aqa din aředdi
\m di řmeḥḥ acemřař n tmeǧač?
\m 
\v 7 Min yugi řeɛmar inu ad t iḥada,
\m \add řexxu\add* aya marra i necc
\m am macca iɣummen.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Mři dd ɣa yas min ttareɣ
\m iwa, iwca Arebbi min sittimeɣ.
\m 
\v 9 Mři tuɣa ixs SIDI maḥend ad ayi iřbez,
\m maḥend ad issarxu afus nnes
\m u maḥend ad ayi iqess.
\m 
\v 10 Man aya ad ayi yiři ɛad d afewwej,
\m ad ayi inɛec di řeḥriq nni
\m war \add xafi\add* issɛizzi ca,
\m maɣar war nkareɣ ca
\m awařen n Umqeddas.
\b
\m 
\v 11 Min iɛna jjehd inu,
\m aqa zemmareɣ ad rajiɣ \add ɛad\add*?
\m Niɣ min iɛna uneggaru inu,
\m wenni x ttexseɣ
\m ad zzugarteɣ tudart inu \add ɛad\add*?
\m 
\v 12 Ma jjehd inu am jjehd n iẓra?
\m Ma aysum inu am nnḥas?
\m 
\v 13 Ma war ǧiɣ qaɛ břa twiza s yixef inu,
\m ma war xafi ittwakkes ufekki qaɛ?
\b
\m 
\v 14 Wenni umi iqḍeɛ řayas \add ittxeṣṣa as\add*
\m tamexsiwt icuwwaren
\m zeg umeddukkeř nnes,
\m mařa lla, \add izemmar\add* ad yejj tiggʷudi
\m zeg Umzemmar x kuřci.
\m 
\v 15 Aytma banen-dd d iɣeddaren
\m am tɣezrin \add deg idurar\add*,
\m am tassut n tɣezrin nni iɛeddun deɣya,
\m 
\v 16 \add am tiɣezrin\add* tinni ittbarrecnen s wejris,
\m nni di issnuffar wedfeř \add ixef nnes\add*.
\m 
\v 17 Deg wussan nni di dewřent
\m ḥṣarent, beddent,
\m xmi ḥemmant, ttaẓɣent,
\m imḥa wemcan nsent.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Ibriden n tecři nsen farɣen,
\m geɛɛden di řeɛwin uca weddaren.
\m 
\v 19 Imsebriden zi Tayma
\m qqimen ttmeẓrin daysent,
\m ikaravanen zi Caba ttrajan tent.
\m 
\v 20 Nitni ttwacemten
\m deg utecři nni ɣarsen.
\m Usin-dd ɣar tɣezrin \add deg idurar\add*
\m uca barrqen.
\m 
\v 21 S tidett, řexxu tdewřem d walu,
\m teẓrim arẓiyyet inu uca tᵉggʷedem.
\b
\m 
\v 22 Ma nniɣ: ‘Awyem ayi-dd \add ca\add*!’
\m niɣ: ‘Wcem ayi tirzifin zeg wagřa nwem!’
\m 
\v 23 niɣ: ‘Fekk ayi zeg ufus n wenni iḥeṣṣaren!’
\m niɣ: ‘Fdi ayi zeg ufus n ayt n bu-řexcunet!’
\b
\m 
\v 24 Sɣar ayi, \add xenni\add* ad sseɣdeɣ,
\m scen ayi min di weddareɣ!
\m 
\v 25 Mammec jehhden wawařen yecnan,
\m \add maca\add* min xef awebbex nwem?
\m 
\v 26 Ma tᵉttxarrṣem deg wawařen,
\m maḥend ad \add ayi\add* tᵉttwebbxem \add zzaysen\add*?
\m Ma \add xenni\add* awařen
\m n wenni umi qeḍɛen řayas
\m am řeɛwin i kenniw?
\m 
\v 27 Ɛad x yijj n unibu ayujiř
\m ad xas tenḍarem taqedduḥt
\m u ɛad x yijj n umeddukkeř nwem
\m ad xas teggem tameɛmuč.
\b
\m 
\v 28 Xenni řexxu, mařa texsem,
\m ḥḍam xafi mliḥ,
\m necc war xawem ssxarriqeɣ
\m deg uɣembub \add nwem\add*.
\m 
\v 29 Qeǧbem \add ayi\add*,
\m war iɛeddeř ad \add dayi\add* yiři ddeǧ.
\m Qeǧbem \add ayi\add* ɛawed,
\m tasegda inu tbedd ɛad \add nican\add*.
\m 
\v 30 Ma aqa din řɣecc x yiřes inu?
\m Ma war ittředdi waneɣ inu
\m x min war iḥřin?
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Ayub yarni di temwarrit nnes i Ilifaz: Ma war iddar bnadem tudart teqseḥ?
\m 
\v 1 Ma war \add din\add* iǧi umenɣi ittxeṣṣa
\m ad t immneɣ bnadem x temmurt,
\m ma war ǧin wussan nnes
\m am wussan n ucewwař?
\m 
\v 2 Am mammec ittmeẓri imseɣ ɣar tiři,
\m ammu ittraja ucewwař řmunet,
\m 
\v 3 S uya dewřen iyuren ccuren
\m s ubarreq d tasɣart inu
\m u ǧyaři ccurent s tamara
\m bḍan ayi tent.
\b
\m 
\v 4 Xmi ttezzřeɣ ttᵉṭṭṣeɣ, qqareɣ
\m ‘Meřmi zemmareɣ ad kkareɣ,
\m \add meřmi\add* i ɣa teɛdu ǧiřet?’
\m Jjiwneɣ s řeḥweř ař d yeffu řḥař.
\m 
\v 5 Arrimet inu tyarḍ deg ikeccawen
\m u di teqcurin n ucař,
\m tiřmect inu tqeṭṭa u tᵉttgeyyeḥ.
\m 
\v 6 Deɣya x umekkuk n uxeyyaḍ
\m ɛeddun wussan inu,
\m ɛeddun břa řayas.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Ɛqeř, aqa tudart inu
\m d asuḍi n nnefs \add waha\add*
\m u tiṭṭ inu war tẓarr ɛemmarṣ ɛad
\m min iṣebḥen. \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Ayub 8:9; 14:1, 2, 3; 16:22; Izhd. 90:5, 6, 9; 102:12; 103:15; 144:4; Ica. 40:6; Yaɛ. 4:14; 1 Bṭ. 1:24\x*
\m 
\v 8 Tiṭṭ n wenni d ayi ittwařan,
\m war d ayi tẓarr ɛad.
\m Tiṭṭawin nnec ad xafi iřint,
\m \add maca\add* nnec war da ttiřiɣ ɛad.
\m 
\v 9 \add Am mammec\add* ittdurruq useynu, iɛeddu,
\m ammu i ɣa ihwa di řaxart,
\m war \add zzayes\add* dd-ittgeɛɛid ɛad.
\m 
\v 10 Ɛemmarṣ war dd-ittɛiqqib
\m ɣar taddart nnes,
\m ɛemmarṣ war xas itteɛqiř wemcan nnes.
\m 
\v 11 Ammu i war tteqqneɣ aqemmum inu,
\m ad ssiwřeɣ di řeḥṣaret n buḥbeř inu,
\m ad cetciɣ di tarzugi n řeɛmar inu.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ma necc d řebḥar niɣ d řhaycet,
\m aqa Cek tessbedded xafi aɛessas?
\m 
\v 13 Mařa nniɣ necc: ‘Tassut ad ayi tɛezza,
\m qama inu ad xafi tessehwen acetci inu!’,
\m 
\v 14 ammu id ayi tᵉttɣezzid s tirjiwin
\m u s iweḥḥan tessaggʷaded ayi,
\m 
\v 15 ařami idweř řeɛmar inu
\m ittixḍar ajeyyef,
\m \add ittixḍar\add* řmewt x yeysan inu.
\m 
\v 16 Necc ttɛiffiɣ \add man aya\add*,
\m war ttexseɣ ad ddareɣ i řebda.
\m Arxu zzayi, maɣar ussan inu
\m \add am\add* asuḍi n nnefs \add waha\add*.\x ◘ \xo 7:16 \xt Izhd. 62:10; 144:4\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 Min iɛna bnadem aqa Cek tḥessbed t
\m d ameqqran \add ammu\add*,
\m aqa teřhid akides s wuř nnec? \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt Izhd. 8:5; 144:3; Ɛbr. 2:6\x*
\m 
\v 18 Aqa Cek tarezzfed ɣares qaɛ \add a\add*teffu,
\m tqeǧbed i-t qaɛ tazeḥziht?
\m 
\v 19 Mecḥař ɛad
\m war zzayi tᵉttekksed \add tiṭṭawin\add*,
\m war d ayi tarexxud
\m ḥima ad ssɣeřyeɣ ikuffan inu?
\b
\m 
\v 20 Ma xḍiɣ? Min d ac i ɣa ggeɣ i Cek,
\m \add i Cek\add* \add a-y-\add*aɛessas n bnadem?
\m Mayemmi d ayi tessbedded
\m d taḥjurt zzatek,
\m u dewřeɣ d ddqeř i yixef inu?
\m 
\v 21 Mayemmi war \add d ayi\add* tɣeffared
\m axeṭṭu inu,
\m u war tɛeddud x řmuɛṣiyyet inu?
\m Maɣar deɣya ad zzřeɣ di tɛejjajt
\m u Cek ad xafi tarzud,
\m \add maca\add* war ttiřiɣ \add ɛad\add*.
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Řhard amezwaru n Bildad
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* yarra-dd \bd Bildad\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Cuḥa, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Mecḥař i ɣa tekked tessawařed ammu,
\m ad iřin wawařen n uqemmum nnec
\m \add amecnaw\add* asemmiḍ n tharyaḍt.
\m 
\v 3 Ma ad issfarɣ Arebbi tasɣart,
\m niɣ ad issfarɣ
\m Umzemmar x kuřci tasegda? \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Aɛwd. 32:4; 2 Im. 19:7; Dan. 9:14\x*
\m 
\v 4 Mařa akides xḍan iḥenjiren nnec,
\m aqa issekk i-ten deg ufus n uxeṭṭu nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Mařa cek tarezzud Arebbi s jjehd,
\m tᵉttzawged aḥinni
\m ɣar Umzemmar x kuřci, \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Ayub 22:23\x*
\m 
\v 6 mařa teǧid d amezdag u tseggmed,
\m xenni ad ac iwca taynit nican,
\m ad iɛdeř tazeddiɣt nnec i cek.
\m 
\v 7 \add Waxxa\add* tamezwarut nnec
\m ad tiři d tuqřič,
\m taneggarut nnec ad tiři temɣar aṭṭas.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Wah, seqsa xenni ɣar jjiř iɛdun,
\m ḥekkar di řejdud nsen. \x ◘ \xo 8:8 \xt Aɛwd. 4:32\x*
\b
\m 
\v 9 Maɣar neccin n iḍennaḍ \add waha\add*,
\m war nessin walu,
\m maɣar ussan nneɣ x temmurt am tiři. \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt Amz. 47:9; 1 Im. 29:15; Ayub 7:5, 6, 7; Izhd. 39:13; 102:12; 144:4\x*
\m 
\v 10 Ma war cek sseřmiden nitni,
\m ma war ɣarek ssiwiřen,
\m ma war dd-ssuffuɣen awařen
\m zeg wuř nsen?
\b
\m 
\v 11 Ma iɣemmi uɣanim n papirus
\m břa ssebxet,
\m ma imeqqar uɣanim ɣar tma n iɣzar
\m břa aman?
\m 
\v 12 Xmi ittnewwar, war imjar ɛad,
\m ittaẓeɣ qbeř marra arbiɛ nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Izhd. 129:6; Irm. 17:6\x*
\m 
\v 13 Ammu i ǧan imesraq
\m n marra inni ittun Arebbi,
\m řayas n umnafeq ad ifna. \f ◼ \fr 8:13 \fk amnafeq\ft - bnadem nni itteggen s tnayen n wudmawen.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 8:13 \xt Ayub 11:20; 18:14; Izhd. 112:10; Awřn. 10:28\x*
\m 
\v 14 Min xef iɛemmed, ad ittwaqḍeɛ,
\m min xef ittcař,
\m ad dd-iban d axmař n qundɛa.
\m 
\v 15 Ad isenned x taddart nnes,
\m \add maca\add* war tᵉttbeddi,
\m ad dayes icebbar,
\m \add maca\add* war tᵉttɣimi tbedd.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Netta d aziza di tfawt n tfuct,
\m řefruɛ nnes imeẓyanen ttbezzaɛen
\m x weḥwic nnes.
\m 
\v 17 Iẓewran nnes mmuden ixef nsen
\m x ijj n uɛurric n yeẓra,
\m ittarja ict n taddart n yeẓra \add i yixef nnes\add*.
\m 
\v 18 \add Mařa\add* Netta iqeǧeɛ i-t
\m zeg wemcan nnes,
\m ad t inkar \add wemcan\add* nni, \add ad yini\add*:
\m ‘Ɛemmarṣ war cek ẓriɣ!’
\m 
\v 19 Xzar, ta teǧa d řefraḥet
\m n webrid \add n tudart\add* nnes
\m u inneɣni ad ɣemyen zeg ucař.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Xzar, Arebbi war ineṭṭar
\m wenni ikemřen
\m \add maca\add* war ittic \add a\add*fus i iɛeffanen.
\m 
\v 21 Ɛad ad iccur aqemmum nnec
\m s tḍeḥḥact,
\m u iyencicen nnec s usřiwřew.
\m 
\v 22 Imecrah nnec ad yarḍen řefḍiḥet
\m u aqiḍun n iɛeffanen war ittiři ɛad.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Bildad
\m 
\v 1 Yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ssneɣ nican, aqa ammu i teǧa,
\m maɣar mammec ɣa yiři bnadem
\m d amsegged ɣar Arebbi? \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt Izhd. 143:2\x*
\m 
\v 3 Mařa Netta ixs akides imcarreɛ,
\m iři netta war izemmar ad xas dd-yarr
\m uřa d ict n twařa x wařef n twařawin.
\m 
\v 4 Netta d amiɣis n wuř
\m d bu-tzemmar ijehden,
\m man wen izemmaren
\m ad isseqseḥ ixef nnes ḍidd nnes
\m uca ad iqqim iddar di řaman?
\b
\m 
\v 5 Netta d wenni issmuṭṭuyen idurar
\m am war tt tticin \add iwdan\add*,
\m d wenni ten issneqřaben
\m deg weɣḍab nnes,
\m 
\v 6 Netta d wenni issenhezzan tammurt
\m zeg wemcan nnes,
\m d wenni iggin ipilaren nnes ad arjijen,
\m 
\v 7 Netta d wenni ittamaren tafuct
\m ařami war dd-tenqir,
\m d wenni ittcemmaɛen itran!
\b
\m 
\v 8 Netta s Yixef nnes waha
\m ittbezzaɛ ijenwan,
\m Netta iṣurruf tiwa
\m n tɛurar \add n řemwaj\add* n waman. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Amz. 1:6\x*
\m 
\v 9 Netta d wenni iggin \add awraf n itran\add*
\m n Ddub \add Ameqqran\add* d Uryun,
\m \add agraw n\add* Sebɛa n Itran
\m d Ixammen n Ljanub,
\m 
\v 10 Netta d wenni iggin
\m timesřayin timeqqranin,
\m - war izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad tent ifhem -
\m uřa d řeɛjayeb břa řeḥsab. \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Ayub 5:9; Izhd. 72:18; 77:15; 86:10; Rum. 11:33\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Xzar, Netta iɛeddu xafi, war t ẓarreɣ,
\m iẓekkwa, necc war kides ttaciɣ.
\m 
\v 12 Xzar, mařa ixḍef Netta,
\m man wen i t ɣa imenɛen?
\m Man wen izemmaren ad as yini:
\m ‘Min din tᵉttegged Cek?’
\m 
\v 13 Arebbi war ittarri aɣḍab nnes
\m ad dd-idweř,
\m sadu nnes uḍaren imɛawanen n ‘Rahab’. \f ◼ \fr 9:13 \fk Rahab\ft - ixs ad yini: ‘wenni issaggʷaden’. ‘Rahab’ d isem n řhaycet. Řhaycet-a aqa-tt d tammurt n Miṣra, tenni am řeḥwec di řebḥar (ixs ad yini: ‘iɣzar n Nil’) issaggʷad řegnus s jjehd nnes cciṭani.\f*
\m 
\v 14 Mammec i ɣa ggeɣ ad xas dd-arreɣ,
\m mammec i ɣa farzeɣ
\m awařen inu \add mliḥ\add* zzates?
\m 
\v 15 Waxxa necc d amsegged,
\m war zemmareɣ ad xas dd-arreɣ,
\m \add maca\add* ad zawgeɣ Řqaḍi inu
\m maḥend ad xafi iḥinn,
\b
\m 
\v 16 Mařa xafi dd-yarr řami řaɣiɣ,
\m war ttɣiřeɣ aqa Netta ad iseř
\m ɣar tmijja inu.
\m 
\v 17 Aqa Netta iřebbez ayi s ict n tḥaryaḍt
\m u yarenni deg iyezzimen inu baṭeř.
\m 
\v 18 Netta war d ayi ittejji ad arreɣ nnefs,
\m maca issjawan ayi s tarzugi.
\m 
\v 19 Mařa teqqim \add tmesřact\add* di jjehd,
\m aqa Netta ijhed qaɛ,
\m mařa di ccreɛ, \add iqqar\add*:
\m ‘Wi d ayi ɣa iɛarḍen?’
\m 
\v 20 Waxxa necc d amsegged,
\m \add ɛad\add* aqemmum inu ad xafi iḥkem,
\m waxxa necc břa řɛib,
\m \add ɛad\add* Netta ad ayi iɛeyyeb.
\b
\m 
\v 21 Waxxa necc břa řɛib \add i ǧiɣ\add*,
\m war ssineɣ řeɛmar inu \add nican\add*,
\m tudart inu ḥessbeɣ tt d walu.
\m 
\v 22 X uya i ɣa iniɣ: ‘Qaɛ d ict!
\m Am wenni iǧan břa řɛib
\m am wenni iǧan d aɛeffan,
\m Netta ad ten iqḍa s tnayen idsen!’ \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt Amb. 9:2, 3; Mal. 3:14\x*
\m 
\v 23 Mařa arekkuḍ ineqq deg ict n tecti,
\m \add xenni\add* Netta istehezza
\m zi řeqḍeɛ n řayas i imezdagen.
\m 
\v 24 Tammurt ad temmewc
\m deg ufus n uɛeffan.
\m Iɣembab n řquḍat nnes ittřeḥḥef asen.
\m Mařa war \add t iggi\add* Netta, man wen xenni?
\b
\m 
\v 25 Deɣya x wenni ittazzřen
\m aqa ttqeǧiqen wussan inu,
\m arewřen ɣar din, war twiřin řxar. \x ◘ \xo 9:25 \xt Ayub 7:6, 7\x*
\m 
\v 26 Kkin am tɣarruba n uɣanim,
\m am ugider iḥewwmen x zzardet.
\m 
\v 27 Mařa nniɣ: ‘Ad ttuɣ acetci inu,
\m ad beddřeɣ aɣembub \add iceḍnen\add* inu,
\m ad ssfirnineɣ!’,
\m 
\v 28 \add ammu i\add* tteggʷedeɣ zi marra řeḥriq inu.
\m Necc ssneɣ Cek war zzayi tᵉttbarrid.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Necc d aɛeffan,
\m mayemmi ssḥissifeɣ i walu?
\m 
\v 30 Mařa ssirdeɣ s waman n wedfeř,
\m ad ssizedgeɣ ifassen inu s llixiya, \x ◘ \xo 9:30 \xt Irm. 2:22\x*
\m 
\v 31 \add ɛad\add* ad ayi tnetyed
\m deg weḥfur yarṣuden,
\m ař d ayi ɣa iɛiff warruḍ inu.
\m 
\v 32 Maɣar Netta war iǧi d bnadem am necc,
\m wenni xef zemmareɣ ad dd-arreɣ,
\m xmi nettaweḍ ɣar taddart n ccreɛ
\m ak-d wayawya. \x ◘ \xo 9:32 \xt Amb. 6:10; Irm. 49:19\x*
\m 
\v 33 War \add din\add* iǧi řɛadeř jar aneɣ,
\m wenni izemmaren ad issars afus nnes
\m xaneɣ s tnayen idneɣ.
\b
\m 
\v 34 Ejj i-t ad xafi iksi aɛmud nnes,
\m war d ayi issnexřiɛ \add ɛad\add* uhuddi nnes, \x ◘ \xo 9:34 \xt Ayub 13:20; 33:7\x*
\m 
\v 35 \add xenni\add* ad ssiwřeɣ
\m nhřa ad zzayes ggʷedeɣ,
\m maɣar necc war ǧiɣ ammu i yixef inu.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Ayub issiweř ak-d Bildad x lɣaraḍ n Arebbi s uweddeb
\m 
\v 1 Ittɛiffi řeɛmar inu zi tudart inu,
\m ad barrḥeɣ acetci inu
\m ammu waha břa amnaɛ,
\m ad ssiwřeɣ ɣar tarzugi n řeɛmar inu.
\m 
\v 2 Necc ad iniɣ i Arebbi:
\m ‘War d ayi ttegg d aɛeffan,
\m scen ayi, mayemmi akidi tᵉttmenɣid.
\b
\m 
\v 3 Ma ɣarek řefḍeř aqa Cek tḥeṣṣared \add ayi\add*,
\m aqa tneṭṭareḍ řxedmet n ifassen nnec,
\m \add am\add* tᵉttegged tafawt
\m x ixarriṣen n iɛeffanen?
\m 
\v 4 Ma ɣarek tiṭṭawin n bnadem,
\m ma tᵉttwařid Cek
\m am mammec ttwařan iwdan? \f ◼ \fr 10:4 \fk bnadem\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘aysum’.\f*
\m 
\v 5 Ma ussan nnec am wussan n bnadem?
\m Ma iseggʷusa nnec
\m am yiseggʷusa n weryaz,
\m 
\v 6 aqa Cek tarezzud
\m \add ammu\add* x řmuɛṣiyyet inu,
\m tᵉttbeqqced di ddnub inu?
\m 
\v 7 Waxxa Cek tessned
\m aqa necc war ǧiɣ d aɛeffan,
\m war din wenni i ɣa ifekken zeg ufus nnec.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Ifassen nnec xeřqen ayi, ggin ayi,
\m aqa ttennḍen ayi,
\m uca \add řexxu\add* Cek tṣarḍed ayi.
\m 
\v 9 Ɛqeř aqa Cek teggid ayi am tarrist,
\m u ɣar tɛejjact texsed ad ayi tarred. \x ◘ \xo 10:9 \xt Amz. 2:7; 3:19\x*
\m 
\v 10 Ma war d ayi tzeǧɛed am uɣi,
\m am kisu tejjid ayi ad ccreɣ? \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt Izhd. 139:15, 16\x*
\m 
\v 11 S teřmect d weysum tessyarḍed ayi,
\m s iɣsan d iẓewran temmuded ayi.
\m 
\v 12 Tudart d tmexsiwt icuwwaren
\m tewcid ayi tent,
\m aḥeṭṭu nnec iḥḍa buḥbeř inu.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Txemmřed aya deg wuř nnec,
\m necc ssneɣ belli aya tuɣa-t ɣarek di řbař.
\m 
\v 14 Mařa xḍiɣ, Cek ad ayi teḥḍid,
\m war d ayi tᵉttbarrid zi řmuɛṣiyyet inu.
\m 
\v 15 Mařa ggiɣ řɣar, uct xafi!
\m Mařa necc d amsegged \add i ǧiɣ\add*,
\m war zemmareɣ ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ azeǧif inu.
\m Jjiwneɣ s řefḍiḥet,
\m ttaciɣ ak-d řemḥayen inu.
\m 
\v 16 Mařa ssgeɛɛdeɣ ixef inu,
\m ad ayi tneymared am wayrad izehharen,
\m \add řebda\add* tᵉttneqřabed xafi s řɣefřet. \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Ica. 38:13; Igjd. 3:10\x*
\m 
\v 17 Meɛlik ufiɣ ad xafi tessbedded \add řebda\add*
\m icehhaden nneɣni,
\m ad tarnid ɛad deg weɣḍab nnec xafi,
\m iɛessasen i ixeǧfen \add ijj i wenneɣni\add* řebda,
\m \add wah,\add* ad ɣari \add tnedhed\add* ijj n řɛeskar.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Mayemmi d ayi tejjid ad dd-ffɣeɣ
\m zeg uɛeddis n yemma?
\m Mři ssuffɣeɣ buḥbeř,
\m war d ayi tẓar uřa d ict n tiṭṭ!’ \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Ayub 3:11\x*
\m 
\v 19 Meɛlik ufiɣ axmi war iřiɣ ɛemmarṣ,
\m mmeksiɣ ɣar wenḍeř
\m zeg uɛeddis \add n yemma\add*.
\m 
\v 20 Ma war ǧin wussan \add n tudart\add* inu udrusen?
\m Mři d ayi ijja, ad xafi inneqřeb
\m maḥend ad farheɣ cwayt \add ɛawed\add*,
\m 
\v 21 qbeř i ɣa uyureɣ - war dikkwiřeɣ \add ɛad\add* -
\m ɣar temmurt n taǧest d tiři n řmewt,
\m 
\v 22 \add ɣar\add* temmurt d tabarcant am tmeddit,
\m \add am\add* tiři n řmewt, war \add din\add* ittbin walu,
\m mani tegga tfawt am tmeddit.
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Řhard amezwaru n Ṣufar
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ṣufar\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Naɛma, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ma ad qqimen waṭṭas n wawařen
\m břa tamwarrit,
\m u ma ad ɣares yiři
\m i yijj n bu-uqemmum řḥeqq \add řebda\add*?
\m 
\v 3 Ma izemmar řhard nnec
\m ad issɣed iwdan,
\m \add ařami\add* \add tzemmared\add* ad testehzid
\m břa cek i ɣa isseḥcem uřa d ijj?
\m 
\v 4 Cek tennid: ‘Teṣfa tɣuri inu,
\m aqa ayi d amezdag di tiṭṭawin nnec!’
\m 
\v 5 Uh, mři Arebbi \add Simant nnes\add* issawař,
\m mři yarezzem iyencicen nnes qibač nnec.
\m 
\v 6 Mři Netta d ac i ɣa isscen
\m timesřayin ixemmřen n tiɣit,
\m maɣar nitenti sekkwant ddubel i ufekki.
\m Ssen, aqa Arebbi
\m ad ittu aṭṭas n řmuɛṣiyyet nnec
\m di tizi nnec.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Ma tzemmared ad tbeqqced
\m di mummu n Arebbi?
\m Ma tzemmared ad tadfed
\m ɣar řekmaret n Umzemmar x kuřci?
\m 
\v 8 \add Aqa-ten\add* di řuɛřat n ujenna!
\m Min texsed ad tegged \add ɛad\add*?
\m \add Tiɣit\add* tuǧeɣ x řaxart!
\m Min tzemmared ad \add zzayes\add* tessned?
\m 
\v 9 Řeɛbar nnes yuɛřa aṭṭas x temmurt,
\m tiru nnes \add teɛdu aṭṭas\add* x tmiriwt n řebḥar.
\b
\m 
\v 10 Mařa iɛdu Netta, ibelleɛ \add x ca n yijjen\add*
\m uca iřaɣa \add as\add* i ddeɛwet,
\m man wen i t ɣa issbedden?
\m 
\v 11 Maɣar Netta issen iɣeccacen,
\m ittwařa řɣecc břa ma t iḥḍa. \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt Izhd. 10:11, 14; 35:22\x*
\m 
\v 12 \add Maca mařa\add* abuhaři
\m \add izemmar\add* ad yaf řefhamet,
\m \add xenni\add* aɣyuř n řexřa \add izemmar\add*
\m ad idweř d bnadem. \x ◘ \xo 11:12 \xt Ayub 5:8; 22:21; Amb. 3:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 13 Mařa cek tɛedřed uř nnec,
\m \add xenni\add* bezzeɛ ifassen nnec ɣares.
\m 
\v 14 Mařa irṣeq řɣecc ɣar ufus nnec,
\m saggʷej i-t,
\m war ttejji ddeǧ ad izdeɣ di tqidunin nnec,
\m 
\v 15 maɣar xenni tzemmared
\m ad tessgeɛɛded udem nnec břa řɛib,
\m ad tbedded nican, war tteggʷeded ca.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Maɣar ad tᵉttud řeɣben nnec,
\m \add ɛemmarṣ war\add* dayes tᵉttxemmimed \add ɛad\add*
\m am \add ɛemmarṣ war tᵉttxemmimed ɛad\add*
\m ɣar waman iɛdun.
\m 
\v 17 Abrid n tudart nnec ad yarɣ
\m tiwa x ṭṭḥa n uziř,
\m waxxa din taǧest,
\m ad tiři am teffut. \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Izhd. 37:6; 112:4\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ad tacid ixef nnec di řaman,
\m minzi aqa din řayas,
\m ad texzared \add deg wenneḍ\add*,
\m ad tᵉṭṭṣed di řhudnet. \x ◘ \xo 11:18 \xt Lawi 26:5\x*
\m 
\v 19 Ad tezzřed nhřa \add cek\add* issnexřeɛ uřa d ijj,
\m uca aṭṭas i cek i ɣa zawgen
\m zzat i wudem nnec. \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Lawi 26:6; Izhd. 3:6; 4:9; Awřn. 3:24\x*
\m 
\v 20 \add Maca\add* tiṭṭawin n iɛeffanen
\m ad ddarɣřent,
\m qaɛ tarewřa ad asen tweddar,
\m ad meẓren ad deřqen i buḥbeř. \x ◘ \xo 11:20 \xt Ayub 8:13, 14; 18:14\x*
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Ṣufar
\m 
\v 1 Yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 D tidett, kenniw d ijj n ddarb n řgens,
\m aqa tiɣit ad temmet akidwem!
\m 
\v 3 Necc ɣari řeɛqeř am kenniw,
\m necc war weṭṭiɣ deg umquddi akidwem.
\m Wi war issinen \add marra\add* aya?
\b
\m 
\v 4 Necc am wenni iǧan i tseḍḥac
\m i umeddukkeř nnes,
\m \add necc\add* d wenni tuɣa ittřaɣan ɣar Arebbi
\m uca \add xenni\add* Netta isřa ɣari,
\m \add necc\add* d amsegged d nican,
\m aqa dewřeɣ d řqecɛet n tseḍḥact. \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt Ayub 16:10; 17:2; 21:3; 30:1; Awřn. 14:2 \x*
\m 
\v 5 ‘Řḥegra d tasɣart n wenni ittwarẓan!’,
\m ammu i ittxarraṣen yinni
\m umi ittɣiř aqa aten di řaman,
\m \add ittɣiř asen\add* aya ittraja
\m inni ittneqraḍen deg iḍaren \add nsen\add*.
\m 
\v 6 Iqiḍan n imteḥḥayyen arsan,
\m u inni iseɛɛaren Arebbi
\m ɣarsen aṭṭas n řaman.
\m \add Maca\add* wi izemmaren
\m ad yawi Arebbi s ufus nnes? \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt Ayub 21:7; Izhd. 73:11, 12; Irm. 12:1; Ḥab. 1:3, 4\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 Seqsa xenni řmař,
\m ad ac \add t\add* ssřemden,
\m ijḍaḍ n ujenna ad cek \add t\add* ḥajan.
\m 
\v 8 Niɣ xezzareɣ mliḥ ɣar temmurt,
\m nettat ad cek tessɣar,
\m uřa d iseřman n řebḥar
\m ad ac \add t\add* ɛawden.
\m 
\v 9 Man wen war issinen marra aya,
\m aqa afus n SIDI i t iggin?
\m 
\v 10 Netta d wenni deg ufus nnes iǧa
\m řeɛmar n marra min iddaren,
\m uřa d buḥbeř n kuř arrimet n bnadem.
\b
\m 
\v 11 Ma war ittqeǧib umezzuɣ awařen,
\m am ittqasa waneɣ macca? \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt Ayub 6:30; 34:3\x*
\m 
\v 12 Ɣar iwessura \add i teǧa\add* tiɣit
\m u di tudart tazirart \add teǧa\add* řefhamet?
\m 
\v 13 Netta ɣares \add i teǧa\add* tiɣit d jjehd \add s tidett\add*,
\m Netta ɣares \add i yeǧa\add*
\m ccwar d řefhamet \add nican\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Xzar, \add mařa\add* Netta iheddem,
\m war ibenni uřa d ijj \add ɛawed\add*,
\m mařa Netta ibelleɛ x ca n yijjen,
\m war d as yarezzem ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Ayub 9:12; 11:10; Asa. 3:7\x*
\m 
\v 15 Xzar, mařa Netta issbedd aman,
\m ad aẓɣen nitni,
\m mařa yarxu asen,
\m ad ssenqeřben tammurt.
\m 
\v 16 Netta ɣares jjehd d ufekki,
\m nnes d wenni iweddaren
\m uřa d wenni issweddaren.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Netta ittejja iryazen n ccwar
\m gguren s řeḥfa,
\m řquḍat ittarra i-ten d ibuhařiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 12:17 \xt 2 Ṣm. 15:31; 17:14, 23; Ica. 19:12; 29:14; 1 Kur. 1:19\x*
\m 
\v 18 Aziyyar n ijeǧiden issbeṭṭeř i-t
\m u \add xenni\add* Netta ittcedda i-ten
\m s ijj n webyas zi tejɛinna nsen.
\m 
\v 19 Netta ineddeh ikehhanen s řeḥfa,
\m ayt n jjehd iɣeṭṭer i-ten.
\m 
\v 20 Ittekkes awař i iryazen ittwaqeǧben,
\m i iwessura ittekkes asen řefhamet. \x ◘ \xo 12:20 \xt Ayub 32:9; Ica. 3:2, 3\x*
\m 
\v 21 Aseḥqar ittzeǧaɛ i-t x tarwa n taṣiřet,
\m i ayt n bu-řexcunet issarexxu asen abyas. \x ◘ \xo 12:21 \xt Izhd. 107:40\x*
\b
\m 
\v 22 Imucan yuǧɣen n taǧest ittɛarra xasen,
\m d tiři n řmewt issuffuɣ i-tt ɣar tfawt. \x ◘ \xo 12:22 \xt Mt. 10:26; 1 Kur. 4:5\x*
\m 
\v 23 Řegnus issemɣar i-ten uca iɣeṭṭer i-ten,
\m Netta ittbezzaɛ řegnus uca ineddeḥ i-ten.\x ◘ \xo 12:23 \xt Izhd. 107:38\x*
\m 
\v 24 Ittekkes řefhamet
\m i izeǧifen n řgens x temmurt,
\m ijja i-ten ttᵉtliɛen di řexřa
\m mani war \add ǧin\add* ibrid\add en\add*. \x ◘ \xo 12:24 \xt Izhd. 107:4, 40\x*
\m 
\v 25 Nitni ttemhafan da d diha di taǧest,
\m mani war teǧi tfawt,
\m Netta ittejja i-ten
\m ad mmhafan am yimescar\add en\add*.
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Ayub yarenni deg wawař nnes i Ṣufar
\m 
\v 1 Xzar, qaɛ man aya teẓra i-t tiṭṭ inu,
\m isřa i-t umezzuɣ inu, ifhem as mliḥ.
\m 
\v 2 Min tessnem kenniw,
\m ssneɣ t uřa d necc,
\m war weṭṭiɣ ca deg usemquddi akidwem.
\b
\m 
\v 3 Maca necc xseɣ ad ssiwřeɣ
\m ɣar Umzemmar x kuřci,
\m meẓreɣ ad wteɣ \add tamesřact inu\add*
\m zzat i Arebbi.
\m 
\v 4 Maca kenniw tessuffuɣem ixarriqen,
\m marra kenniw d iḍbiben ixwan. \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Ayub 16:2\x*
\m 
\v 5 Ax, mři tesseɣdem kenniw marra!
\m Aya ad tiři d tiɣit i kenniw. \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt Awřn. 17:28\x*
\m 
\v 6 Sřem xenni mammec ɣa wteɣ
\m x yixef inu,
\m ḥekkarem x umcarraɛ n iyencicen inu!
\b
\m 
\v 7 Ma texsem ad tinim řɣecc
\m i řefḍeř n Arebbi,
\m \add ma texsem\add* ad tessiwřem ixarriqen
\m di tizi nnes? \x ◘ \xo 13:7 \xt Ayub 17:5; 32:21; 36:4\x*
\m 
\v 8 Ma tzemmarem ad tewtem tamesřact
\m di ṭṭweɛ nnes?
\m Ma \add texsem\add* ad tcarrɛem i Arebbi?
\m 
\v 9 Ma mliḥ i kenniw,
\m mařa Netta ad kenniw iqeǧeb?
\m Ma texsem ad zzayes testehzam
\m am mammec stᵉhezzan \add iwdan\add*
\m zeg ijj n bnadem?
\m 
\v 10 Netta ad kenniw iwebbex,
\m mařa kenniw tᵉtteggem
\m s wudmawen s tnuffra.
\m 
\v 11 Ma war kenniw issnexřiɛ uɛuǧi nnes,
\m ma war dd xawem tweṭṭi tiggʷudi zzayes?
\b
\m 
\v 12 Awařen nwem i řidaret
\m aqa aten d řemtuř n walu,
\m řegɛudi nwem d řegɛudi n ubeǧaɛ.
\m 
\v 13 Seɣdem zzati, maḥend ad ssiwřeɣ,
\m ejj ad xafi dd-yas min \add i dd ɣa yas\add*.
\m 
\v 14 Mayemmi ɣa ṭṭfeɣ aysum \add n arrimet\add* inu
\m jar teɣmas inu,
\m \add mayemmi i\add* ɣa ṭṭfeɣ tudart inu
\m deg ufus inu?
\m 
\v 15 Xzar, Netta ixs ad ayi ineɣ,
\m necc ad t rajiɣ,
\m \add maca\add* ad wteɣ x ibriden inu zzates. \x ◘ \xo 13:15 \xt Izhd. 23:4; Awřn. 14:32\x*
\m 
\v 16 D wa i d ayi ɣa idweř d asenjem inu,
\m maca amnafeq war dd-ittis
\m zzat i uɣembub nnes. \f ◼ \fr 13:16 \fk amnafeq\ft - bnadem nni itteggen s tnayen n wudmawen.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 17 Sřem mliḥ ɣar řhard inu,
\m s imezzuɣen \add yarezmen\add* ɣar ucarreḥ inu.
\m 
\v 18 Xzar, necc iwyeɣ ddeɛwet s usettef,
\m ssneɣ ad ttwaseggdeɣ.
\m 
\v 19 Man wen \add izemmaren\add* ad kidi imcarrɛen?
\m Xenni ad seɣdeɣ deɣya,
\m ad ssuffɣeɣ buḥbeř.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Mɣir war d ayi ttegg tnayen n řeḥwayej,
\m xenni war zzayek ttnuffariɣ: \x ◘ \xo 13:20 \xt Ayub 9:34; 33:7\x*
\m 
\v 21 afus nnec siggʷej i-t xafi,
\m war d ayi snexřiɛ s uhuddi nnec!
\m 
\v 22 Řaɣa \add Cek\add*, necc ad \add xak\add* dd-arreɣ,
\m niɣ necc ad ssiwřeɣ
\m u Cek ad xafi dd-tarred!
\b
\m 
\v 23 Mecḥař xafi n řmuɛṣiyyet d ddenb?
\m Scen ayi axeṭṭu inu d ddenb inu.
\m 
\v 24 Mayemmi tessnuffared aɣembub nnec,
\m tḥessbed ayi d řeɛdu nnec? \x ◘ \xo 13:24 \xt Ayub 16:9; 19:11; 33:10; Igjd. 2:5\x*
\m 
\v 25 Ma texsed ad tessenxeřɛed
\m tafarct i iɛarren usemmiḍ ssa ɣar da,
\m ma texsed ad teḍfared iɣeǧ yuẓɣen?
\b
\m 
\v 26 Maɣar tᵉttarid xafi
\m timesřayin timarzagin,
\m tbeṭṭid ayi ddnub n temẓi inu. \x ◘ \xo 13:26 \xt Izhd. 25:7\x*
\m 
\v 27 Tessrusid iḍaren inu deg ukeccuḍ,
\m Cek tḥeṭṭid marra imesraq inu.
\m Tḥeṭṭid tiřeqqa n iḍaren inu, \x ◘ \xo 13:27 \xt Ayub 33:11\x*
\m 
\v 28 n wenni iggin am ukeccuḍ,
\m ccin t ikeccawen, \add xenni\add* yarecca,
\m am warruḍ icca i-t tcinda.
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Ayub issiweř ak-d Ṣufar x řmewt
\m 
\v 1 Bnadem i dd-ittwaxeřqen
\m zi temɣart,
\m aqa ussan \add n tudart\add* nnes udrusen
\m u netta iccur s řeḥweř. \x ◘ \xo 14:1 \xt Izhd. 90:5, 6, 9; 102:12; 103:15; 144:4; Yaɛ. 4:14\x*
\m 
\v 2 Netta iɣemmi am tnewwact,
\m xenni ittwaqḍeɛ.
\m Ittrakkwař am tiři, war ittɣimi. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Ayub 8:9; Izhd. 90:6, 10; 102:12; 103:15; 144:4; Ica. 40:6; 1 Bṭ. 1:24\x*
\m 
\v 3 Waxxa amenni tarezmed
\m tiwa nnes tiṭṭawin nnec,
\m tᵉttawyed ayi-dd di ddeɛwet akidek. \x ◘ \xo 14:3 \xt Ayub 7:17, 18; 10:20\x*
\b
\m 
\v 4 Man wen izemmaren ad issuffeɣ
\m ijj n umezdag zeg umexmuj?
\m Uřa d ijj! \x ◘ \xo 14:4 \xt Amz. 5:3; Izhd. 51:7; Yḥ. 3:6; Rum. 5:12; Afa. 2:3\x*
\m 
\v 5 Mara ussan nnes urin,
\m řqedd n iyuren nnes \add aqa ittwassen\add* ɣarek
\m uca teggid as řeḥdud nnes
\m nni war d as iɛeddeř ad ten iɛdu, \x ◘ \xo 14:5 \xt Ayub 7:1\x*
\m 
\v 6 neqřeb \add xenni\add* xas maḥend ad yareyyeḥ,
\m ařami izemmar ad yarr meẓri
\m am yijj n ucewwař deg wass nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt Ayub 7:1, 2, 16, 19; 10:20\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 Maɣar i tcejjart aqa din ɛad řayas!
\m Mařa tᵉttwaqess,
\m ad tessuffeɣ ɛawed \add řefruɛ\add*,
\m řefruɛ nnes war ttbeddin zeg uɣemmi.
\m 
\v 8 Waxxa iwsar weẓwar nnes di temmurt,
\m immut jjdeɛ nnes deg ucař,
\m 
\v 9 ad teɣmi tcejjart \add ɛawed\add*
\m xmi ɣa taca ak-d waman,
\m ad tessuffeɣ \add ɛawed\add* řefruɛ
\m am ict n tcejjart ẓẓun tt beḥřa.
\b
\m 
\v 10 \add Maca mařa\add* immut ijj n weryaz, ifenna,
\m \add mařa\add* iffeɣ as buḥbeř i bnadem,
\m mani iǧa xenni?
\m 
\v 11 Aman tteffɣen-dd zi řebḥar,
\m iɣzar ittaẓeɣ u ixekkwa.
\m 
\v 12 Izzeř bnadem din, war ittekkar ɛad.
\m Ař war ttiřin ɛad ijenwan, war d ttfiqin,
\m war ttwassekkaren zeg iḍeṣ nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Ax, mři d ayi ɣa tarred ɣar řaxart,
\m ad ayi tessnuffared
\m ař ɣa iḥeyyed weɣḍab nnec,
\m mři d ayi turid ijj n řmijař imten,
\m \add ḥima\add* ad ayi tidared \add ɛawed\add*!
\m 
\v 14 Mařa ijj n weryaz immut,
\m ma ad dd-idweř ɣar tudart?
\m \add Xenni\add* ad qqimeɣ ttrajiɣ
\m marra ussan n umenɣi inu,
\m ař dd-yusa ufekki inu.
\m 
\v 15 Mařa \add xenni\add* Cek třaɣid,
\m necc ad Cek dd-arreɣ
\m uca Cek ad temmeẓřed
\m ɣar řxedmet n ifassen nnec.
\m 
\v 16 Maca řexxu tḥessbed iṣuraf inu,
\m war tmennɛed \add lɣaḍab nnec\add* x ddnub inu. \x ◘ \xo 14:16 \xt Ayub 31:4; 34:21; Izhd. 56:9; 139:2, 3, 4; Awřn. 5:21; Irm. 32:19\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 Axeṭṭu inu ittwacemmeɛ di tcemmust,
\m ɣar řmuɛṣiyyet inu tarnid \add dayes\add* ktar.
\m 
\v 18 Wah, adrar iweṭṭan, ifessi,
\m jarf iḥruǧed zeg wemcan nnes,
\m 
\v 19 aman tteddzen iẓra,
\m iɣezran nnes ttekksen acař n temmurt,
\m ammu i tareddǧed řayas n bnadem.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Cek tarennid dayes i řebda, \add xenni\add* yuyur.
\m Tᵉttbeddařed udem nnes
\m uca tessekked i-t.
\m 
\v 21 \add Mařa\add* iḥenjiren nnes ṭṭfen ccan,
\m netta war t issin,
\m \add mařa\add* ten deǧen,
\m war kidsen ittici.
\m 
\v 22 Maca arrimet nnes tᵉttnezbar
\m di ṭṭweɛ n yixef nnes \add waha\add*,
\m u řeɛmar nnes ittecḍin
\m di ṭṭweɛ nnes.
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Řhard wiss tnayen n Ilifaz x uɛeffan
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ilifaz\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Tayman, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ma ittarra-dd ijj n umiɣis s tussna ixwan?
\m Ma ad iccur aɛeddis nnes s usemmiḍ
\m i dd-ittasen zi manis dd-tneqqar tfuct?
\m 
\v 3 Ma ittcarraɛ s řharي war ineffɛen,
\m s wawařen nni war ittakkwaḍen?
\m 
\v 4 Cek tarẓid tiggʷudi \add n Arebbi\add*,
\m tekksed taẓaǧit zzat i wudem n Arebbi.
\m 
\v 5 Maɣar aqemmum nnec issargeb
\m řmuɛṣiyyet nnec,
\m aqa itteɛjib ac řhard s tḥraymect
\m s yiřes \add nnec\add*.
\m 
\v 6 Aqemmum nnec ad cek iḥkem,
\m war iǧi necc,
\m iyencicen nnec ad xak cehden.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Ma cek d bnadem d amezwaru
\m nni dd-ittwaxeřqen?
\m Niɣ tᵉttwarwed qbeř tiwririn?
\m 
\v 8 Ma tessḥessed i wegraw
\m n imcawaren imtiqqan n Arebbi,
\m ma tjebbded tiɣit ɣarek? \x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt Rum. 11:34\x*
\m 
\v 9 Min tessned cek, neccin war t nessin?
\m Min tfehhmed cek, aqa inqeṣ ɣarneɣ?
\m 
\v 10 Uřa jar aneɣ d amcaybu d uwessar,
\m nitni d imɣaren deg wussan x babac. \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Ayub 32:7\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Ma asfewwej n Arebbi drus ɣarek,
\m niɣ ijj n wawař ssiwřen t akidek s terɣeɣ?
\m 
\v 12 Mayemmi cek issetlaɛ wuř nnec,
\m mayemmi qeǧɛent tiṭṭawin nnec,
\m 
\v 13 aqa tessneqřabed buḥbeř nnec x Arebbi,
\m \add ařami\add* tessuffuɣed \add marra\add* awařen nni
\m zeg uqemmum nnec?
\b
\m 
\v 14 Min iɛna bnadem aqa netta ad yiři d amezdag,
\m \add min iɛna\add* wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi temɣart,
\m aqa netta ad yiři d amsegged? \x ◘ \xo 15:14 \xt 1 Ij. 8:46; 2 Im. 6:36; Ayub 14:4; Izhd. 14:3; Awřn. 20:9; Amb. 7:20; 1 Yḥ. 1:8, 10\x*
\m 
\v 15 Xzar, imqeddasen nnes war xasen ittciř,
\m uřa d ijenwan war ǧin ṣfan di tiṭṭawin nnes! \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Ayub 4:18; 25:5\x*
\m 
\v 16 Ahtat ɛad ijj n nnɛi n bnadem
\m d bu-ufessad,
\m wenni isessen min war iḥřin am waman!
\b
\m 
\v 17 Necc xseɣ ad ac \add t\add* ssecneɣ, seř-dd ɣari,
\m \add xenni\add* ad ɛawdeɣ min ẓriɣ,
\m 
\v 18 min ɛawden imiɣisen,
\m am war ffaren \add ca\add* n řejdud nsen.
\m 
\v 19 I nitni waha umi temmewc temmurt,
\m uřa d ijj n řbarrani war xas iɛdu.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Marra ussan i iddar uɛeffan,
\m imarret ixef nnes,
\m řqedd n iseggʷusa
\m i ittwaxemmřen i bu-řexcunet,
\m aqa inuffar xas.
\m 
\v 21 \add Yudef-dd\add* řḥess n iɣuyyan issnexřaɛen
\m ɣar imezzuɣen nnes.
\m \add Ɛad di řweqt n\add* řehna ad xas iwḍa umteḥḥay. \x ◘ \xo 15:21 \xt 1 Ts. 5:3\x*
\m 
\v 22 Netta war ittriji ad dd-iɛqeb zi taǧest,
\m \add maca\add* aqa netta ittwagg i ssif.
\m 
\v 23 Netta ittemhafa da d diha x weɣrum.
\m ‘\add A,\add* mani \add i yeǧa\add*?’
\m Netta issen aqa ittraja i-t
\m wass d abarcan deɣya. \x ◘ \xo 15:23 \xt Ayub 18:12; Izhd. 109:10\x*
\m 
\v 24 Ḍḍiqet d řeḥṣaret ssaggʷadent netta,
\m arnint i-t am yijj n ujeǧid
\m iwjed i umenɣi.
\b
\m 
\v 25 Maɣar ɣar Arebbi
\m isswiẓẓaḍ netta afus nnes,
\m ak-d Umzemmar x kuřci
\m imenneɛ \add taɣennant\add* tameqqrant. \x ◘ \xo 15:25 \xt Asa. 13:5\x*
\m 
\v 26 S yiri imeḥḍen ittazzeř ɣares,
\m \add innufrar\add* ɣar ḍeffar
\m n tseddariyin nsen \add n uɛeskari\add*
\m s ibuṭunen igdaren.
\m 
\v 27 Maɣar iřeḥḥef i uɣembub nnes s tadunt,
\m igga tadunt i tejɛinna nnes.
\m 
\v 28 Izeddeɣ di tneddam ittwahedmen,
\m \add di\add* tudrin war daysent izeddeɣ
\m \add ɛad\add* uřa d ijj,
\m tinni yuran maḥend ad dewřent d řxirbat.
\m 
\v 29 Netta war iddikkwiř d bu-wagřa,
\m agřa nnes war ittɣimi,
\m mařa min dd-ikseb
\m war yarenni x temmurt.
\m 
\v 30 Netta war inejjem i taǧest,
\m aceɛɛař \add n tmessi\add* ad yecc řefruɛ nnes,
\m ad ifna s řeɛwin n uqemmum nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 31 Ejj i-t war ittciři x řɣecc,
\m maɣar \add xenni\add* i ɣa tiři
\m uřa d řmunet nnes d řɣecc.
\m 
\v 32 Mařa war dd-yusi \add ɛad\add* wass nnes,
\m ad ittwakemmeř \add ɛad\add*,
\m maɣar taseṭṭa n tini nnes war tzeyziw. \x ◘ \xo 15:32 \xt Ayub 22:16; Izhd. 55:24\x*
\m 
\v 33 Ad isseɣḍeř aḍiř war issnedyen nnes
\m am yict n tzayart,
\m ad immenḍar nnuwar nnes am tzitunt.
\m 
\v 34 Maɣar abarru n imnafqen
\m aqa-t břa řɣiǧet
\m u timessi tᵉttett iqiḍan \add i iccuren\add* s řɣecc. \f ◼ \fr 15:34 \fk amnafeq\ft - bnadem nni itteggen s tnayen n wudmawen.\f*
\m 
\v 35 Aqa aten s ddeyset zi tamara,
\m tturwen řɣecc,
\m řexdeɛ aqa-t deg uɛeddis nsen. \x ◘ \xo 15:35 \xt Izhd. 7:15; Ica. 59:4; Ḥuc. 10:13\x*
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Ayub iřaɣa x Arebbi am dd-ittarra x Ilifaz
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Manawya sřiɣ as aṭṭas,
\m kenniw marra idwem
\m tessbeṭṭřem ayi afewwej. \x ◘ \xo 16:2 \xt Ayub 13:4\x*
\m 
\v 3 Ma ad qḍan wawařen ixwan?
\m Niɣ min cek iɛarrnen \add ɛad\add*
\m ad dd-tarred awař?
\m 
\v 4 Uřa d necc \add zemmareɣ\add*
\m ad ssiwřeɣ am kenniw,
\m mařa aqa kenniw deg wemcan inu.
\m Iři ad mudeɣ awařen xawem
\m u ad xawem hezzeɣ azeǧif inu.
\m 
\v 5 Ad kenniw ssmeḥḍeɣ s uqemmum inu
\m u afewwej n iyencicen inu
\m ad awem yawi řefsaset.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Mařa ssiwřeɣ, war xafi ittejji řeḥřiq inu
\m u mařa sseɣdeɣ, ma ad xafi iḥeyyed?
\m 
\v 7 Řexxu issiḥeř ayi Netta,
\m tessarjfed Cek marra tawacunt inu.
\m 
\v 8 Cek tessduruyed ayi s teqcurt \add n teřmect\add*,
\m tenni d tacehhadt xafi,
\m uca tekkar xafi \add arrimet\add* inu tamusriwt,
\m tᵉttcetca zzayi deg uɣembub inu.
\m 
\v 9 Aɣḍab nnes imezzeq, iḍeffar ayi-dd.
\m Netta ittɣezza ɣari tiɣmas.
\m Aɣrim inu issqeṭṭaɛ-dd ɣari tiṭṭawin. \x ◘ \xo 16:9 \xt Ayub 10:16, 17; 13:24\x*
\b
\m 
\v 10 Nitni ttcarragen aqemmum nsen xafi,
\m ccaten ayi s řḥegra ɣar uqabsi,
\m ttekkaren xafi ttmunen.
\m 
\v 11 Isellem ayi Arebbi
\m i yijj n mmis n řmuɛṣiyyet,
\m iɛarren ayi deg ufus n iɛeffanen.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Tuɣa ayi di řhudnet,
\m maca Netta yarẓa ayi,
\m icebbar ayi deg ijiman, iřbez ayi.
\m Issbedd ayi d taḥjurt i Yixef nnes. \x ◘ \xo 16:12 \xt Ayub 7:20; Igjd. 3:12\x*
\m 
\v 13 Imjebbaden \add nnes\add* \add n řqews\add* nnḍen ayi-dd,
\m Netta issnuqqub ayi tiẓẓař břa ahaweř,
\m ittzeǧaɛ ɣar temmurt iẓi inu, \f ◼ \fr 16:13 \fk tiẓẓař\ft - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*
\m 
\v 14 yareẓẓa ayi tareẓẓit
\m awarni i treẓẓit nneɣni,
\m iɛref-dd xafi am bu-teɣruḍt.
\b
\m 
\v 15 Xeyyḍeɣ taxancet \add n wecḍan\add*
\m i teřmect inu,
\m icc inu sswessxeɣ di tɛejjact. \x ◘ \xo 16:15 \xt Ayub 30:19\x*
\m 
\v 16 Aɣembub inu izweɣ zeg imeṭṭawen,
\m tiři n řmewt aqa-tt x wabřiwen inu,
\m 
\v 17 waxxa war yarsi lɛunf x ifassen inu
\m u taẓaǧit inu teṣfa.
\b
\m 
\v 18 \add Uh\add* tammurt, war ddař idammen inu,
\m war ttejji iɣuyyan inu
\m ad afen amcan \add i arraḥet\add*!
\m 
\v 19 Xzar, uřa d řexxu,
\m Acehhad inu deg ujenna,
\m Amcafeɛ inu x řegɛudi.
\m 
\v 20 Imeddukkař inu d yinni zzayi isthezzan,
\m \add maca\add* tᵉttru tiṭṭ inu ɣar Arebbi.
\m 
\v 21 Ejj-i-t ad iwwet ddeɛwet
\m x weryaz ɣar Arebbi,
\m am ijj n mmis n bnadem
\m x umeddukkeř nnes. \x ◘ \xo 16:21 \xt Ayub 31:35; Amb. 6:10; Ica. 45:9; Rum. 9:20\x*
\m 
\v 22 Maɣar drus n iseggʷusa
\m i-dd ɣa yasen \add ɛad\add*,
\m qbeř i ɣa uyureɣ abrid
\m war zzayes ttɛiqqibeɣ.
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 Ayub issiweř ak-d Ilifaz x řemḥayem nnes
\m 
\v 1 Buḥbeř inu yarjef,
\m ussan inu \add ineggura\add* xesyen,
\m \add mɣir\add* imeḍřan d ayi iqqimen.
\m 
\v 2 S tidett, inni istehzan aqa aten ɣari,
\m u tiṭṭ inu tessɛeddu ǧiřet
\m jar ixarriṣen nsen imarzagen!
\b
\m 
\v 3 Egg Ixef nnec d aḍman i necc \add din\add* ɣarek.
\m Man wen \add xenni\add* i ɣa iwten \add afus nnes\add*
\m deg ufus inu \add i man aya\add*? \x ◘ \xo 17:3 \xt 2 Kur. 5:19\x*
\m 
\v 4 Maɣar Cek tekksed
\m \add marra\add* řefhamet x wuř nsen,
\m x uya Cek war ten tessɛuǧid ca.
\m 
\v 5 Wi ɣa iɣdaren imeddukkař nnes
\m di ṭṭweɛ n tkeccaḍt,
\m tiṭṭawin n iḥenjiren nnes ad nɛedment.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Netta igga ayi d lmatal jar řegnus,
\m ařami dewřeɣ am yijjen
\m ssusufen as x uɣembub. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Ayub 30:9\x*
\m 
\v 7 S uya i teɛmec tiṭṭ inu zeg wecḍan,
\m marra iɣezdisen inu aqa aten am tiři.
\m 
\v 8 Inni igguren nican
\m ttnexřaɛen zi man aya,
\m amezdag ittneqřab x umnafeq.
\m 
\v 9 Amsegged imenneɛ deg webrid nnes,
\m wenni ɣar iǧa ifassen imezdagen,
\m yarenni di jjhed.
\b
\m 
\v 10 Maca marra kenniw, dewřem-dd,
\m asettiw-dd da,
\m maɣar war ufiɣ
\m uřa d ijj n umiɣis jar awem. \x ◘ \xo 17:10 \xt Ayub 6:29\x*
\m 
\v 11 Ɛdun wussan inu,
\m ttwaqeḍɛen inwayen inu,
\m marra meẓri n wuř inu. \x ◘ \xo 17:11 \xt Ayub 7:6; 9:25\x*
\m 
\v 12 Ǧiřet tteggen tt d ass,
\m \add qqaren:\add* aqa tafawt tᵉttades-dd
\m xmi dd ɣa tewḍa taǧest.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Mařa ssitmeɣ \add ɛad\add*, \add ssitimeɣ\add*
\m aqa řaxart ad tiři d taddart inu,
\m ad bezzɛeɣ tassut inu di taǧest.
\m 
\v 14 Ɣar \add weḥfur n\add* turṣuḍi řaɣiɣ:
\m ‘Cek d baba!’,
\m ɣar ikecca: ‘Yemma!’ d: ‘Učma!’
\m 
\v 15 Mani iǧa xenni řayas inu?
\m Řayas inu,
\m man wen \add izemmaren\add* ad t iẓar?
\m 
\v 16 Ad hwan ɣar ṭṭrufa n řaxart,
\m xmi i ɣa naf nmun arraḥet deg ucař. \x ◘ \xo 17:16 \xt Ayub 3:17, 18, 19; 30:23, 24\x*
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Řhard wiss tnayen n Bildad: Aneggaru n bnadem d aɛeffan
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* yarra-dd \bd Bildad\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Cuḥa, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ař meřmi \add ɛad tarezzum\add*
\m ad tᵉṭṭfem \add ijj n bnadem\add* x wawařen nnes?
\m Mařa tfehmem, \add xenni\add* awarni i uya ad nessiweř.
\m 
\v 3 Mayemmi d aneɣ ittwagg am řmař
\m u nettwaḥṣar di buḥbeř
\m di tiṭṭawin nwem?
\b
\m 
\v 4 \add Cek, a yaryaz\add* wenni ittmezzqen ixef nnes
\m deg uxeyyeq nnes!
\m Ma ad jjen temmurt \add di ssibbet nnec\add*,
\m ad ittwassmuṭṭi jjarf
\m zeg wemcan nnes \add di ssibbet nnec\add*? \f ◼ \fr 18:4 \fk ixef nnes\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar nnes’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 18:4 \xt Ayub 13:14\x*
\m 
\v 5 Wah, tafawt n iɛeffanen ad texsi,
\m aceɛɛař n tmessi n \add uɛeffan\add*
\m war ittegg tafawt \add ɛemmarṣ ɛad\add*.
\m 
\v 6 Tafawt di tqidunt nnes ad tebbarcen,
\m řefnar nnes tiwa nnes ad t ssxesyen.
\m 
\v 7 Ttarjijen iṣuraf nnes ijehden,
\m ccwar \add n yixef\add* nnes ad t iɣḍeř.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Maɣar s iḍaren nnes ad innaɣ deg uṣennaj,
\m ad yuyur x tracca, mmuden tt i tneymart.
\m 
\v 9 Taxceft ad t temneɛ zeg unirz,
\m řfex ad dayes tᵉṭṭef. \x ◘ \xo 18:9 \xt Ayub 5:5\x*
\m 
\v 10 Tennuffar tesɣunt \add n řfex\add* di temmurt,
\m řfex aqa-tt x webrid.
\m 
\v 11 Ssiggʷeden t inexřiɛen
\m zi marra iɣezdisen,
\m ḍeffaren t ɣar iḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:11 \xt Ayub 15:21; Irm. 6:25; 46:5; 49:29\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ittwaḥṣar dayes jjehd nnes,
\m aḍeyyeɛ ittraja i-t ɣar uɣezdis nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt Ayub 15:23\x*
\m 
\v 13 \add Arẓiyyet\add* ad tecc
\m \add marra\add* iɣezdisen n arrimet nnes,
\m iɣezdisen \add n arrimet nnes\add*
\m ad ten yecc ijj n řeḥřac ineqqen.
\m 
\v 14 Minxef tuɣa ittceř,
\m ittwaqřeɛ zi tqiḍunt nnes.
\m Tneddeh i-t arẓiyyet
\m ɣar ujeǧid n inexřiɛen. \x ◘ \xo 18:14 \xt Ayub 8:13, 14; 11:20; Awřn. 10:28\x*
\m 
\v 15 Iwdan nni war ǧin d yinni nnes,
\m zeddɣen deg uqiḍun nnes,
\m řecbariyyet tᵉttwazuzzar
\m x tzeddiɣt nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Sadu netta ttaẓɣen iẓewran nnes,
\m zi sennej ttwaqessen řefruɛ nnes.
\m 
\v 17 Řidaret nnes ad tᵉttwakkes zi temmurt,
\m war d as ittɣimi \add ɛad\add* isem deg webriden. \x ◘ \xo 18:17 \xt Izhd. 109:13; Awřn. 10:7\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ad t ɛarnen zi tfawt ɣar taǧest,
\m ad sstewwjen zi ddunect. \f ◼ \fr 18:18 \fk zi ddunect\ft - niɣ ‘zeg umaḍal’.\f*
\m 
\v 19 War ɣares ittiři warraw
\m niɣ jjadira di řgens nnes,
\m war ittɣimi uřa d ijj ad iddar
\m di tzeddiɣin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 18:19 \xt Ica. 14:22; Irm. 22:30\x*
\b
\m 
\v 20 X wass nnes ad arjijen inni izeddɣen
\m ɣar mani tɣeǧi tfuct,
\m inni izeddɣen ɣar manis i dd-tneqqar tfuct
\m ad ten tᵉṭṭef tiggʷudi.
\m 
\v 21 Wah, ammu i tᵉttemsar
\m i tzeddiɣin n imeqjaḥen,
\m wa d amcan n yinni war issinen Arebbi.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Bildad x usitem nnes di Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 Yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Mecḥař ɛad i ɣa tekkem
\m tceḍnem řeɛmar inu,
\m ad ayi třebzem s wawařen?
\m 
\v 3 \add Řexxu\add* ɛad wiss ɛecra n twařawin
\m ttekkwarem ayi,
\m war tᵉttseḍḥim
\m umi d ayi dd-tɣeṭṭřem awař.
\m 
\v 4 Mařa s tidett weddareɣ,
\m ad iqqim uweddar inu i ixef inu.
\m 
\v 5 Mařa s tidett texsem ad xafi tessgeɛɛdem
\m ixef nwem s cciki,
\m ad ayi tessqenɛem s řefḍiḥet inu, \f ◼ \fr 19:5 \fk ad xafi tessgeɛɛdem ixef nwem s cciki\ft - niɣ: ‘ad xafi teggem ayaziḍ’.\f*
\m 
\v 6 snem xenni, aqa Arebbi inneqřeb xafi,
\m uca inneḍ ayi-dd s tracca nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Xzar, sɣuyyuɣ: ‘Řexcunet!’,
\m maca war xafi dd-yarri uřa d ijj,
\m ttřaɣiɣ i twiza,
\m maca řḥeqq war \add din\add* iǧi.
\m 
\v 8 Abrid inu iqqen i-t,
\m ařami war zemmareɣ ad ɛduɣ,
\m taǧest issu tt x imesraq inu.
\m 
\v 9 Řɛezz inu ikecceḍ i-t zzayi,
\m u ttaj i iǧan x uzeǧif inu ikkes i-t.
\m 
\v 10 Netta yareddeǧ ayi zi marra iɣezdisen,
\m ad ttwahellkeɣ!
\m Iqřeɛ řayas inu am yict n tcejjart. \f ◼ \fr 19:10 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\m 
\v 11 Aɣḍab nnes yarɣa dayi,
\m Netta iḥesseb ayi
\m am \add ijj zeg\add* iɣrimen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 19:11 \xt Ayub 13:24; 16:9; 33:10; Igjd. 2:5\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 Munent ffɣent-dd bandiyyat nnes,
\m sswejdent-i-dd abrid nsent ɣari
\m uca quwwarent i tqiḍunt inu.
\m 
\v 13 Aytma issiggʷej i-ten xafi,
\m inni d ayi issnen dewřen d midden xafi. \x ◘ \xo 19:13 \xt Izhd. 31:12; 38:12; 69:9; 88:9\x*
\m 
\v 14 Inni d ayi itteɛnan jjin ayi,
\m inni d ayi issnen ttun ayi.
\m 
\v 15 Imsexxaren n taddart inu d tiyya inu
\m ḥessben ayi d řbarrani,
\m necc d aɣrib jar tiṭṭawin nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Řaɣiɣ i umsexxar inu,
\m \add maca\add* war xafi dd-yarri,
\m tuɣa ittxeṣṣa ad t ḥeccmeɣ
\m s uqemmum inu.
\m 
\v 17 Řeɛwin n temwarrit n nnefs inu
\m issɛiff tamɣart inu,
\m arṣuḍeɣ i aytma.
\m 
\v 18 Ɛad iḥramen imeẓyanen sseḥqaren ayi.
\m Mařa kkareɣ beddeɣ, ttemɛarran xafi
\m s wawařen nsen. \x ◘ \xo 19:18 \xt Ayub 30:1\x*
\m 
\v 19 Marra immeddukkař inu iɛizzen
\m carrhen ayi,
\m inni ttexseɣ, nnqeřben xafi. \x ◘ \xo 19:19 \xt Izhd. 41:10; 55:14, 15\x*
\m 
\v 20 Ɣar teřmect d weysum inu
\m řessqen iɣsan inu.
\m Necc nejmeɣ
\m ak-d tiřmect n teɣmas inu \add waha\add*. \x ◘ \xo 19:20 \xt Ayub 30:30; Izhd. 102:6; Igjd. 4:8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 Ḥinnem xafi, ḥinnem xafi, \add a\add* kenniw,
\m imeddukkař inu!
\m Maɣar afus n Arebbi iřqef ayi.
\m 
\v 22 Mayemmi d ayi tḍaffarem
\m am tt ittegg Arebbi,
\m u mayemmi war ttjiwinem aysum inu?
\m 
\v 23 Mři uran awařen inu,
\m mři ttwazemmemen deg ijj n wedlis!
\m 
\v 24 Mři ttwaneqcen
\m s pluma n wuzzař u s řexfif
\m di jjarf i řebda.
\m 
\v 25 Necc ssneɣ: ‘Amefdi inu iddar
\m u Netta ad dd-ikkar d Aneggar x ucař.’
\b
\m 
\v 26 U awarni řami i ɣa tᵉttwařbez
\m teřmect inu ammu,
\m ad ẓareɣ Arebbi zi arrimet inu.
\m 
\v 27 Ad t ẓareɣ zzati,
\m tiṭṭawin inu ad t ẓarent,
\m war iǧi midden.
\m Ɣares i ttmeẓrent tiẓẓař inu
\m ɣar daxeř inu. \f ◼ \fr 19:27 \fk tiẓẓař\ft - niɣ ‘tigeẓřin’.\f*
\m 
\v 28 Waxxa amenni kenniw ad tinim:
\m ‘Mammec i nzemmar ad t neḍfar?’
\m \add maɣar\add* aẓwar n tmesřact ittwaf dayi.
\m 
\v 29 Ggʷedem zi ssif,
\m maɣar s ssif \add ad dd-yas\add* wesɛar
\m x ddnub ineqqen,
\m maḥend ad tessnem aqa \add ad yiři\add* řḥukm.
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Řhard wiss tnayen n Ṣufar x řefřeḥ d řḥukm
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ṣufar\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Naɛma, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ixarriṣen inu ttɣiman
\m dekkwařen-dd ɣari
\m zi ssibbet n uqeǧeq
\m \add i war ittbeddin\add* di \add řbař\add* inu.
\m 
\v 3 Sřiɣ ijj n uwebbex i d ayi issbehdařen,
\m \add maca\add* buḥbeř ad xafi dd-yarr
\m s řefhamet inu.
\m 
\v 4 \add Iwa\add* tessned aya,
\m aqa-t din zeg wecḥař uya,
\m zeg wami ittwassars bnadem x temmurt,
\m 
\v 5 aqa asřiwřew n iɛeffanen
\m ittekk drus \add waha\add*,
\m řefraḥet n umnafeq \add mɣir\add* ict n tzeḥziḥt. \x ◘ \xo 20:5 \xt Izhd. 37:35,36\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 Waxxa tᵉttgeɛɛad nnfaxet nnes ař ijenwan,
\m waxxa ittḥada azeǧif nnes ař iseynuten,
\m 
\v 7 am mammec isufɣan nnes
\m ad qḍan i řebda,
\m ad iqḍa uřa d netta i řebda.
\m Inni t iẓrin, ad inin: ‘Mani iǧa netta?’
\m 
\v 8 Am ict n tirja ad iḍuw,
\m ařami war ittwif \add ɛad\add*,
\m ad ittwassetleɛ am ijj n řewḥiy n ǧiřet.
\m 
\v 9 Tiṭṭ i t iẓrin war \add t\add* tẓarr ɛawed,
\m u amcan nnes war t iẓarr \add ɛemmarṣ\add*.
\m 
\v 10 Iḥenjiren nnes ad ssjiwnen imezřaḍ,
\m \add ammu\add* i dd ɣa yarren
\m ifassen nnes agřa nnes.
\m 
\v 11 Ixsan nnes iccuren s temẓi,
\m ad zzřen akides deg ucař.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Mařa řɣar deg uqemmum nnes d \add a\add*miẓid,
\m mařa issnuffar i-t sadu iřes nnes,
\m 
\v 13 mařa iḥḍa i-t, war ixs ad xas iḥeyyed,
\m \add maca\add* imenneɛ i-t deg waneɣ nnes,
\m 
\v 14 \add xenni\add* ad tbeddeř macca nnes
\m deg uɛeddis nnes,
\m di daxeř nnes ad tedweř
\m d arrhaj n trefsiwin.
\m 
\v 15 Iṣarḍ agřa, \add maca\add* ad t-i-dd-iɛuqq \add ɛawed\add*.
\m Ad t-i-dd-inḍar Arebbi
\m ɣar barra zeg uɛeddis nnes.
\m 
\v 16 Arrhaj n trefsiwin ad t iṭṭeḍ,
\m iřes n ufiɣar ad t ineɣ.
\b
\m 
\v 17 War iẓarr iɣezran,
\m tiɣezratin d taryawin
\m \add ittazzřen\add* s tamment d uɣi.
\m 
\v 18 Ad dd-yarr řefḍeř n umarret nnes,
\m war t isseɣřay,
\m war ineggez s řefraḥet
\m zi ssibbet n wagřa i dd-ikseb,
\m 
\v 19 maɣar ideǧ imezřaḍ,
\m ijja i-ten břa twiza,
\m yucar taddart nni war issbedd,
\m 
\v 20 maɣar war issin řhudnet di daxeř nnes,
\m \add s uya\add* war inejjem
\m s \add marra\add* min di tuɣa immeẓri.
\b
\m 
\v 21 War ittceṭṭi walu i umerɛiq nnes,
\m x uya war ittɣimi zzhar nnes ibedd.
\m 
\v 22 Mařa ɣares afeyyeḍ imun, ad ittwaḥsar,
\m ad xas yiři \add u\add*fus n kuř řmeskin.
\m 
\v 23 Aya ad yiři ḥima ad iccur aɛeddis nnes,
\m \add wah, AREBBI\add* ad xas issekk
\m řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes,
\m ad t yarr ad xas iwwet \add am wenẓar\add*
\m \add uca ad t yarr ad icukk\add* di arrimet nnes.
\m 
\v 24 Waxxa ad yarweř zi řesnaḥ n wuzzař,
\m ad t issnuqqeb řqews n nnḥas.
\m 
\v 25 Ijebbed \add ijjen zzayes fřitca\add*,
\m aqa teffeɣ-dd zi arrimet nnes,
\m řmacam yareqqen \add itteffeɣ-dd\add*
\m zeg iẓi nnes,
\m \add wah\add* inexřiɛen ad xas kken.
\b
\m 
\v 26 Taǧest tekmeř tᵉttḥama
\m ɣar txubay nnes inuffaren,
\m timessi war tt issiɣ uřa d ijj,
\m ad t tecc, ad tarr meẓri
\m ak-d yinni iceṭṭen di tqiḍunt nnes.
\m 
\v 27 Ajenna ad iɛarra řmuɛṣiyyet nnes,
\m tammurt ad xas tɣewweɣ.
\m 
\v 28 Řɣiǧet n taddart nnes ad traḥ,
\m ad tazzeř deg wass n weɣḍab nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Wa d min i dd-ikkaren
\m i iɛeffanen zi AREBBI,
\m tasɣart i d as inna Arebbi.
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Ṣufar: řefřeḥ n weryaz aɛeffan
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Sřem mliḥ i wawařen inu,
\m ḥima ad awem iřin i usfewwej.
\m 
\v 3 Ksim ayi, \add xenni\add* ad ssiwřeɣ,
\m u awarni řami ssiwřeɣ,
\m tzemmarem ad tɛeffarem.
\m 
\v 4 Ma acetci inu x ijj n bnadem?
\m Niɣ mayemmi war d ayi dd-ikkar
\m ad yiři buḥbeř inu břa ttasiɛ n řxaḍar?
\m 
\v 5 Qeřbem-dd ɣari uca jɛarem,
\m sarsem afus x uqemmum.
\m 
\v 6 \add Mařa\add* xemmeɣ \add waha\add* deg uya, ttnexřiɛeɣ
\m u tmenneɛ tarjijit arrimet inu.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Mayemmi ttɣiman iɛeffanen ddaren,
\m \add mayemmi\add* ddakkwařen iwessura,
\m ttmarnin ɛad di jjehd nsen? \x ◘ \xo 21:7 \xt Izhd. 17:10; 73:12; Irm. 12:1; Ḥab. 1:16\x*
\m 
\v 8 Tarwa nsen ttɣiman bedden
\m zzat i uɣembub nsen, aqa aten ɣarsen,
\m u \add iḥenjiren\add* iɣedduten nsen
\m zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen. \f ◼ \fr 21:8 \fk Tarwa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet’.\f*
\m 
\v 9 Tudrin nsen aqa atent
\m di řehna nhřa anexřiɛ,
\m aɛmud n Arebbi war ten iccit.
\m 
\v 10 Afunas nnes ittarra u war ixeṭṭi,
\m tafunast nnes tᵉttaru,
\m ɛemmarṣ war tɣeṭṭeř aɛeddis.
\m 
\v 11 Ttejjan imeẓyanen nsen
\m gguren am yict n tḥimart,
\m iḥenjiren nsen \add ttejjan ten\add* neggzen.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Nitni ssgeɛɛaden \add tmijja nsen\add*
\m ɣar ubendir d řgambri,
\m farrḥen ɣar tmijja n temja.
\m 
\v 13 Ssɛeddun ussan nsen di zzhar,
\m \add maca\add* hekkwan ɣar řaxart
\m deg wermac n wabřiwen.
\m 
\v 14 Qqaren i Arebbi: ‘Ḥeyyed xaneɣ,
\m maɣar war d aneɣ iɛjib
\m ad nessen ibriden nnec. \x ◘ \xo 21:14 \xt Ayub 22:17\x*
\m 
\v 15 Man wen iǧan d Amzemmar x kuřci
\m maḥend ad as nsexxar?
\m Man lfayda i ɣarneɣ
\m mařa nziyyar xas \add s tẓaǧit nneɣ\add*?’ \x ◘ \xo 21:15 \xt Uf. 5:2; Mal. 3:14\x*
\m 
\v 16 Xzar, zzhar nsen war iǧi deg ufus nsen.
\m Ccwar n iɛeffanen iggʷej xafi. \x ◘ \xo 21:16 \xt Ayub 22:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 17 Mecḥař n twařawin
\m txessi \add xenni\add* i iɛeffanen tfawt \add nsen\add*,
\m uca iřeqqef i-ten uḍeyyeɛ,
\m \add mecḥař n twařawin\add* ibeṭṭa Netta
\m \add xasen řeḥřiq\add* deg weɣḍab nnes, \x ◘ \xo 21:17 \xt Ayub 20:29; Izhd. 11:6, 7\x*
\m 
\v 18 \add ařami\add* i ɣa dewřen
\m am uřum zzat i usemmiḍ,
\m am iɣeǧ texḍef i-t tḥaryaḍt?
\m 
\v 19 \add Ma teqqarem\add*: ‘Arebbi ittxemmeř \add lɛiqab\add*
\m \add i\add* řmuɛṣiyyet nnes i iḥenjiren nnes!’
\m Ejj i-t ad as tt ixeǧeṣ
\m ař ɣa yaca netta \add simant nnes\add*!
\m 
\v 20 Ejj tiṭṭawin nnes
\m ad ẓarent ahellek nnes,
\m \add ejj i-t\add* ad isu \add s yixef nnec\add*
\m zeg wesɛar n Umzemmar x kuřci.
\m 
\v 21 Maɣar mammec i ɣa yarḍa ɛad
\m di \add aytbab n\add* taddart nnes
\m awarni \add i řmewt\add* nnes,
\m mařa tᵉttwagg \add ɛad\add* qedda n iyuren nnes? \f ◼ \fr 21:21 \fk awarni \bdit i řmewt\bdit* nnes\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘awarni as’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 22 Ma zemmaren ad ssřemden
\m tussna i Arebbi,
\m Wenni iḥekkmen
\m x yinni iǧan deg ujenna yuɛřan? \x ◘ \xo 21:22 \xt Ica. 40:13; Rum. 11:34; 1 Kur. 2:16\x*
\m 
\v 23 Aqa din ijjen immut di zzhar imun,
\m am \add iddar ɛad\add* qaɛ di řehna u di řhudnet.
\m 
\v 24 \add am\add* ɛemmaren řemdawed nnes s uɣi
\m u ittwabezzeg waduf n yeɣsan nnes.
\m 
\v 25 Wenneɣni immut s řeɛmar d amarzag,
\m war dd-yiwi řiqqi i walu n řxar.
\m 
\v 26 Munen zzřen nitni deg ucař
\m u ikeccawen dřin ten. \x ◘ \xo 21:26 \xt Ayub 17:14\x*
\b
\m 
\v 27 Xzar, ssneɣ ixarriṣen nwem,
\m uřa d timeɛmač nni zi d ayi tdeřmem,
\m 
\v 28 xmi teqqarem:
\m ‘Mani teǧa taddart n umcenneɛ
\m \add ittmeẓrin di ṣṣulṭa\add*,
\m mani teǧa tqiḍunt \add s tzeddiɣin\add*,
\m tazeddiɣt n uɛeffan?’
\m 
\v 29 Ma ɛemmarṣ war tesseqsim imsebriden?
\m Aqa iceyyaren nsen ittqarran
\m war tzemmarem ad ten tenkarem:
\m 
\v 30 maɣar aɛeffan ad ittwaḥḍa
\m deg wass n arẓiyyet,
\m deg wass n uduqqez \add n ufugem\add*
\m ad ttwawyen nitni \add di řaman\add*. \x ◘ \xo 21:30 \xt Awřn. 16:4\x*
\m 
\v 31 Man wen i t ɣa issecnen abrid nnes
\m deg uɣembub nnes?
\m Mařa igga \add ca n tuɛeffna\add*,
\m wi \add t\add* i ɣa ixeǧṣen?
\b
\m 
\v 32 Netta maca ad ittwaksi
\m ɣar wenḍeř nnes \add d ameqqran\add*
\m u ɣar tewrirt n wenḍeř nnes
\m ittɛess netta \add s yixef nnes\add*.
\m 
\v 33 Ttɛejiben as ibursa n teɣzurt,
\m ḍeffaren t marra iwdan
\m u inni d as ittizwaren,
\m war zemmaren ad ten ḥesben.
\b
\m 
\v 34 Mammec texsem ad ayi tɛezzam
\m s \add wawařen\add* ixwan?
\m Zi temwarrit nwem war ittɣimi \add walu\add*
\m mɣir řeɣḍar \add waha\add*.
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Řhard wiss třata n Ilifaz x ddenb d wedwař ɣar Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ilifaz\bd*, wenni dd-yusin zi Tayman, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ma izemmar bnadem ad infeɛ Arebbi?
\m Wenni iggin s řeɛqeř ineffeɛ
\m \add mɣir\add* i yixef nnes.
\m 
\v 3 Ma aqa-t d lfayda i Umzemmar x kuřci
\m aqa cek tseggded,
\m niɣ d řefḍeř mařa cek teggured
\m deg ibriden nnec s řeṣfayet?
\m 
\v 4 Ma iwti i cek
\m zi ssibbet n tiggʷudi nnec \add zzayes\add*,
\m niɣ ad yadef akidek ɣar taddart n ccreɛ?
\m 
\v 5 Ma war teǧi tuɛeffna nnec
\m d tameqqrant,
\m u řmuɛṣiyyat nnec
\m \add ma war ǧint\add* nhřa asbeddi?
\b
\m 
\v 6 Maɣar tḥewwsed ddiyyet
\m zeg aytmac baṭeř,
\m tekksed arruḍ
\m i yinni s drus n werruḍ waha. \x ◘ \xo 22:6 \xt Uf. 22:26, 27; Aɛwd. 24:6, 10-13; Ayub 31:1-34\x*
\m 
\v 7 Wenni yuḥřen war d as tewcid ad isu,
\m wenni iǧuzen tqeḍɛed as aɣrum.
\m 
\v 8 \add Maca\add* mařa din aryaz s uɣiř ijhed,
\m \add xenni\add* tammurt aqa-tt i wanita,
\m ad dayes izdeɣ ca n weryaz n ccan.
\m 
\v 9 Tijjař tsekked tent s ifassen xwan,
\m iɣaǧen n uyujiř ttwařebzen.
\b
\m 
\v 10 X uya nnḍent ac řefxux,
\m uca tewḍad-dd xak tiggʷudi.
\m 
\v 11 Niɣ war tᵉttwiřid taǧest,
\m d řḥemřet n waman nni cek yedřin?
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ma war iǧi Arebbi yuɛřa deg ujenna?
\m Xzar itran \add nni iǧan\add* sennej qaɛ,
\m mammec ɛuǧen!
\m 
\v 13 \add Maca\add* teqqared: ‘Min issen Arebbi?
\m Ma izemmar ad iḥkem \add nican\add*
\m zeg useynu ibbumbsen?
\m 
\v 14 Iseynuten d ařeḥḥef i Netta
\m ařami war ittwiři,
\m u x řqubbet n ujenna iggur Netta.’
\b
\m 
\v 15 Ma texsed ad teḍfareḍ amesruq n wecḥař uya,
\m amesruq nni kkin yeryazen
\m \add iccuren\add* s řmuɛṣiyyet,
\m 
\v 16 inni ittwakksen am war dd-yiwiḍ \add ɛad\add*
\m řmijař nsen,
\m \add umi\add* tfeyyeḍ řḥemřet dsas nsen,
\m 
\v 17 inni innan i Arebbi: ‘Aggʷej xaneɣ!’
\m Min izemmar Umzemmar x kuřci
\m ad yegg \add ɛad\add* i nitni? \x ◘ \xo 22:17 \xt Ayub 21:14\x*
\m 
\v 18 Iwa, waxxa Netta iccur
\m tudrin nsen s řxar!
\m Ccwar n iɛeffanen iggʷej xafi. \x ◘ \xo 22:18 \xt Ayub 21:16\x*
\b
\m 
\v 19 Ẓrin tt imseggaden uca farḥen,
\m amezdag istehza zzaysen. \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt Izhd. 107:42\x*
\m 
\v 20 ‘Aɣrim nneɣ ittwakeḥḥeḍ
\m u min zzaysen iqqimen tecca i-t tmessi.’
\b
\m 
\v 21 Qqen ɣares, ad ɣarek tiři řhudnet,
\m S uya ad ɣarek dd-yas min iṣebḥen.
\m 
\v 22 Ksi xenni taɣuri zeg uqemmum nnes,
\m egg awařen nnes deg wuř nnec.
\m 
\v 23 Mařa tdewřed-dd
\m ɣar Umzemmar x kuřci,
\m ad tᵉttwassbedded.
\m Siggʷej min war iseggden
\m x tqiḍunin nnec. \x ◘ \xo 22:23 \xt Ayub 8:5, 6\x*
\m 
\v 24 Sars ureɣ iqquren deg ucař,
\m ureɣ zi Ufir jar iẓra n tɣezratin.
\b
\m 
\v 25 \add xenni\add* Amzemmar x kuřci
\m ad yiři \add amecnaw\add* ureɣ iqquren nnec,
\m \add amecnaw\add* idurar yuɛřan n nnuqart i cek!
\b
\m 
\v 26 Maɣar xenni ad tfarḥeḍ
\m zeg Umzemmar x kuřci,
\m ad tessgeɛɛded aɣembub nnec
\m ɣar Arebbi.
\m 
\v 27 Ad as tᵉttared s tẓaǧit yuǧɣen
\m u Netta ad ac iseř,
\m u cek ad tkemmřed lwuɛud nnec.
\m 
\v 28 Mařa tekksed awař,
\m xenni ad ac dd-teffeɣ \add tmesřact\add*,
\m u tafawt ad tareɣ deg ibriden nnec.
\m 
\v 29 Mařa ssehwan nitni ijjen, ad tinid:
\m ‘Sgeɛɛed \add azeǧif nnec\add*!’,
\m Netta ad issenjem
\m wenni isshekkwan tiṭṭawin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:29 \xt Awřn. 29:23\x*
\m 
\v 30 Netta ad issenjem
\m wenni war iǧin břa řɛib,
\m minzi netta ad injem
\m s tezdugi n ifassen nnec!
\b
\b
\c 23
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Ilifaz d wedfaɛ nnes zzat i Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 Yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Uřa d ass-a acetci inu d aɣennan,
\m issedqeř afus inu x uneffes inu.
\m 
\v 3 Mři ssneɣ, mani zemmareɣ ad t afeɣ,
\m maḥend ad awḍeɣ ɣar tzeddiɣt nnes.
\m 
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* ad bezzɛeɣ zzates ddeɛwet,
\m ad ccureɣ aqemmum inu
\m s wawařen i ucarreɛ.
\m 
\v 5 Ad ssneɣ awařen i xafi dd ɣa yarr,
\m ad fehmeɣ min i d ayi ɣa yini.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Ma ittxeṣṣa as ad imcarreɛ akidi
\m s jjhed ameqqran?
\m Lla, ejj i-t ad ayi iwc \add taynit waha\add*.
\m 
\v 7 Dinni ad kides imcarreɛ wenni icnan
\m u \add ammu\add* necc ad nnufsřeɣ i řebda zi Řqaḍi inu.
\m 
\v 8 \add Maca\add* xzar, mařa uyureɣ ɣar ccarq,
\m \add ammu\add* war din iǧi Netta,
\m u mařa \add uyureɣ\add* ɣar řɣarb,
\m \add ammu\add* war d as ttḥekkareɣ.
\m 
\v 9 Mařa ɣares cɣeř di ccamal,
\m war t ttwiřiɣ,
\m \add mařa\add* inneqřeb-dd ɣar ljanub,
\m war t ẓarreɣ.
\b
\m 
\v 10 Maca Netta issen abrid i ggureɣ,
\m ittqeǧeb ayi, ad ffɣeɣ am wureɣ.
\m 
\v 11 Imneɛ uḍar inu di jjurrat nnes,
\m abrid nnes ḍfareɣ t, war zzayes ffiɣeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 23:11 \xt Ayub 31:4-8\x*
\m 
\v 12 Tawṣiyyet zeg uqemmum nnes
\m war zzayes arxuɣ.
\m Awařen n uqemmum nnes xemmřeɣ ten,
\m mahu min xef ttwaweṣṣiɣ.
\m 
\v 13 \add Maca\add* mařa Netta ḍidd n ca n yijjen,
\m man wen i t ɣa imenɛen zi man aya?
\m Min ixs řeɛmar nnes, ad t yegg. \x ◘ \xo 23:13 \xt Izhd. 115:3\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 Maɣar Netta isseqfař min i d ayi yura,
\m u aqa din aṭṭas n tmesřayin
\m am tina ɣares \add di řbař\add*.
\m 
\v 15 X uya ttnexřaɛeɣ zzat i uɣembub nnes,
\m aqa fehmeɣ tt mliḥ,
\m u tteggʷedeɣ zzayes.
\m 
\v 16 \add Maɣar\add* Arebbi issefciř uř inu,
\m Amzemmar x kuřci issnexřaɛ ayi.
\m 
\v 17 Maɣar war ttnexřiɛeɣ zi taǧest,
\m uřa zeg wudem inu
\m nni ittřeḥḥef s tubbarcent.
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Ayub isseqsa Ilifaz x min t icqan i Arebbi inni ittwaḥṣaren
\m 
\v 1 Mayemmi war ttwassnuffarent
\m řmijařat \add n uxeǧeṣ\add*
\m s ufus n wenni iǧan d Amzemmar x kuřci,
\m \add mayemmi\add* war ttwiřin inni t issnen
\m ussan nnes \add n nneqmet\add*?
\m 
\v 2 Nitni ssmuṭṭuyen řehdud,
\m ttacaren taḥimart uca arekkwsen tt. \x ◘ \xo 24:2 \xt Aɛwd. 19:14; 27:17; Awřn. 22:28; 23:10\x*
\m 
\v 3 Aɣyuř n iyujiřen ssaggʷajen t,
\m ttḥewwsen afunas n tajjač.
\m 
\v 4 Nitni ɛarrnen imezřaḍ zeg webrid.
\m Inni ittwaḥṣaren di temmurt
\m ttnuffaren jmiɛ. \x ◘ \xo 24:4 \xt Awřn. 28:28\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 Xzar, aqa aten am yiɣyař n řexřa.
\m Tteffɣen ɣar řxedmet nsen,
\m arezzun taneymart.
\m Řexřa iwca as macca i iḥenjiren nsen.
\m 
\v 6 Deg iyyar ḥettcen řeḥtic nnes,
\m řeqqḍen deg umarjeɛ n uḍiř n iɛeffanen.
\m 
\v 7 Ssɛeddun ǧiřet d iɛaryanen, nhřa arruḍ,
\m war ɣarsen bu dduri di teṣmeḍ.
\m 
\v 8 Zeg wenẓar iccaten zeg idurar ttuffen,
\m ttcebbaren di jjarf
\m maɣar war ɣarsen adurri.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Zeg iffan n \add yemmatsen\add* ttekksen ayujiř,
\m uca ttᵉṭṭfen aḍman zeg umezřuḍ.
\m 
\v 10 Gguren d iɛaryanen, nhřa arruḍ,
\m am ǧuẓen arebbun icuwwafen \add n imendi\add*. \x ◘ \xo 24:10 \xt Lawi 19:13\x*
\m 
\v 11 Jar řeḥyuḍ ttɛessaren zzect,
\m ɛeffsen x tsirt n uḍir,
\m maca ttɣiman ffuden. \x ◘ \xo 24:11 \xt Aɛwd. 25:4; Yaɛ. 5:4\x*
\m 
\v 12 Zi tendint itteffeɣ-dd řḥess
\m n useɣnef n yeryazen,
\m řeɛmar n yinni issuffɣen buḥbeř
\m isɣuyyu deg ujenna.
\m \add Waxxa amenni\add* Arebbi war iḥeṭṭi
\m min war iḥřin.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Inneɣni d imɣewwɣen x tfawt,
\m war ssinen ibriden nnes,
\m war ttɣimin di tibridin nnes.
\m 
\v 14 Qbeř \add dd-tusa\add* tfawt, ittekkar uqettař,
\m ineqq řmeskin d umezřuḍ
\m u di ǧiřet igga am uxewwan. \x ◘ \xo 24:14 \xt Izhd. 10:8, 9\x*
\m 
\v 15 Tiṭṭ n uzennay tḥeṭṭa taǧest.
\m Iqqar: ‘Uřa d ict n tiṭṭ war d ayi tḥeṭṭi!’
\m Iřeḥḥef i uɣembub nnes. \x ◘ \xo 24:15 \xt Izhd. 10:11; Awřn. 7:8, 9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 16 Di taǧest ttadfen ɣar tudrin.
\m S wass ttnuffaren,
\m war ssinen walu x tfawt. \x ◘ \xo 24:16 \xt Ayub 38:15; Yḥ. 3:20\x*
\m 
\v 17 Maɣar tuffut \add tban\add* asen-dd am tiři n řmewt,
\m maɣar ssnen inexřiɛen n tiři n řmewt.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Netta d afsus \add am ukuffu\add*
\m x wudem n waman i yeǧa.
\m Tettwanɛeř tesɣart nsen x temmurt.
\m War itteṭṭef \add ɛad\add* abrid
\m ɣar imarjaɛen n uḍiř.
\m 
\v 19 Řaẓaɣ d řeḥmu qeṭṭan
\m x waman n wedfeř,
\m \add ammu i tᵉttekkes\add* řaxart uřa d inni ixḍan.
\m 
\v 20 Aɛeddis n yemmas ad t ittu,
\m ikeccawen ad zzayes arren meẓri.
\m Ɛemmarṣ war t ttidaren \add ɛad\add*.
\m Ittwarẓ řɣecc am \add ict n tfrewt n\add* ukeccuḍ,
\m 
\v 21 \add ammu uřa d\add* wenni itteggen řɣar
\m di temɣart břa tarwa,
\m di tenni war ittirwen,
\m uřa d wenni itteggen
\m min war iḥřin ak-d tajjač.
\b
\m 
\v 22 S jjehd nnes issbedda
\m inni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa.
\m Ibedd wanita, \add maca\add* war issin nican
\m aqa tudart nnes di řaman.
\m 
\v 23 Netta iwca as řaman,
\m \add ařami\add* ɣares dd-tudef ttiqqet,
\m \add ɛad\add* tiṭṭawin nnes
\m aqa atent x webrid nsen.
\m 
\v 24 Ttwassuɛřan i yijj n řḥař d aquḍaḍ,
\m xenni war ǧin \add ɛad\add*.
\m Ad hwan, ad ttwakksen
\m am marra \add iwdan\add*,
\m am ixfawen n uɣedduy \add n yirden\add*
\m ad ttwaqessen.
\m 
\v 25 Ma war iǧi amenni?
\m Man wen i d ayi ɣa iṭṭfen ixarriqen,
\m \add man wen i ɣa\add* issebḍeř řhard inu?
\b
\b
\c 25
\s1 Řhard wiss třata n Bildad
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* yarra-dd \bd Bildad\bd*, i dd-yusin zi Cuḥa, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ṣṣulṭa d jjehd issaggʷaden
\m aqa aten ɣares,
\m Netta ittegg řehna di řuɛřa nnes.
\m 
\v 3 Ma izemmar ad ḥesben
\m mecḥař i ɣares n řɛeskar?
\m X man war tᵉttgeɛɛed tfawt nnes?
\m 
\v 4 Mammec \add xenni\add* \add izemmar\add* bnadem
\m ad yiři d amsegged zzat i Arebbi,
\m mammec izemmar
\m wenni dd-ittwarwen zi temɣart
\m ad yiři d amezdag? \x ◘ \xo 25:4 \xt Ayub 4:17, 18, 19; 15:14, 15, 16\x*
\m 
\v 5 Xzar, ɛad taziri simant nnes
\m war tᵉttwesseg s řeṣfayet,
\m itran war ṣfin di tiṭṭawin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 25:5 \xt Ayub 15:15\x*
\m 
\v 6 Ahta ɛad bnadem, \add wenni\add* d awekki,
\m u mmis n bnadem, \add wenni\add* d akeccaw. \x ◘ \xo 25:6 \xt Ayub 4:19; Izhd. 22:7\x*
\b
\b
\c 26
\s1 Tamwarrit n Ayub x Bildad: Řemɣaret n Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Mammec teggid tewcid afus
\m i wenni war ɣar iǧi jjehd,
\m \add mammec\add* tbedded ɣar uɣiř
\m n wenni war ɣar teǧi tzemmar!
\m 
\v 3 Zeɛma aqa tewcid aweṣṣi isebḥen
\m i wenni war ɣar teǧi tiɣit,
\m \add mammec\add* i tessargbed aṭṭas \add n twařawin\add*
\m mummu \add n tmesřact\add*!
\m 
\v 4 I umi tɛawded \add řexxu\add* awařen nnec?
\m Man nnefs dd-iffɣen zzayek?
\b
\m 
\v 5 Řexyařat \add n imettan\add* fessyen
\m sadu waman d imezdaɣ nsen.
\m 
\v 6 D aɛaryan tezzeř zzates řaxart,
\m war \add din\add* teǧi tqebbart i \add tesraft n\add* uhellek. \x ◘ \xo 26:6 \xt Izhd. 139:8, 11; Awřn. 15:11; Ɛbr. 4:13\x*
\m 
\v 7 Ibezzeɛ \add ajenna\add* di ccamal
\m tiwa řxawi n \add wudem n waman\add*,
\m yuyeř tammurt ɣar walu. \x ◘ \xo 26:7 \xt Izhd. 104:2 \x*
\b
\m 
\v 8 Netta ittcedda aman deg iseynuten nnes,
\m \add maca\add* war ittareẓẓi aseynu swadday.
\m 
\v 9 Issdurruy udem n řɛarc nnes,
\m ittbezzaɛ xas aseynu nnes. \x ◘ \xo 26:9 \xt Ayub 9:8; Izhd. 104:2, 3\x*
\m 
\v 10 Yarcem taquract x wudem n waman,
\m ař tma n tfawt ak-d taǧest. \x ◘ \xo 26:10 \xt Amz. 1:9; Ayub 38:8; Izhd. 33:7; 104:9; Awřn. 8:29; Irm. 5:22\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Ipilaren n ujenna ttarjijin,
\m ttnexřaɛen zeg uweddeb nnes.
\m 
\v 12 S jjehd nnes isshaj řebḥar,
\m s řefhamet nnes iřbez Rahab. \x ◘ \xo 26:12 \xt Ica. 51:15\x*
\m 
\v 13 S Arruḥ nnes ittissiq ujenna
\m \add am wudem n tenni war ittřeḥḥifen\add*,
\m afus nnes issnuqqeb
\m afiɣar itteḥřuǧuḍen s tazřa. \x ◘ \xo 26:13 \xt Izhd. 33:6\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 Xzar, man aya \add waha\add*
\m ixef n ibriden nnes,
\m nesřa \add mɣir\add* taḥessect
\m n \add ca n\add* wawařen zzayes.
\m Wi izemmaren \add xenni\add*
\m ad issen ajjaj n jjhed nnes?
\b
\b
\c 27
\s1 Řhard n Ayub x iɛeffanen
\m 
\v 1 Yarni issgeɛɛed \bd Ayub\bd* řhard n lmatal nnes, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 S tidett am iddar Arebbi
\m nni i d ayi ikksen tasɣart inu,
\m Amzemmar x kuřci
\m nni issarzagen řeɛmar inu,
\m 
\v 3 min ɣa yekk nnefs ɛad dayi
\m u arruḥ n Arebbi \add ɛad\add* deg wenzaren inu,
\m 
\v 4 war qqaren iyencicen inu řɣecc
\m u iřes inu war iqqar ixarriqen!
\m 
\v 5 Iggʷej xafi ad ggeɣ kenniw
\m di tseyyarest n tidett.
\m Ař ɣa ssuffɣeɣ buḥbeř inu,
\m war ttejjiɣ ad xafi kksen asegged inu.
\m 
\v 6 Ad ṭṭfeɣ di tsegda inu,
\m war zzayes arexxuɣ ca.
\m Uř inu war d as yarexxu
\m uřa x ijjen zeg wussan inu.
\m 
\v 7 Mři dd-iban řeɛdu inu d aɛeffan,
\m wenni akidi ittmenɣan
\m d mmis n řmuɛṣiyyet.
\b
\m 
\v 8 Maɣar man řayas n umnafeq,
\m xmi ɣa tᵉttwaqḍeɛ \add tudart nnes\add*,
\m xmi zzayes i ɣa iqřeɛ Arebbi řeɛmar nnes? \x ◘ \xo 27:8 \xt Mt. 16:26; Lk. 12:20\x*
\m 
\v 9 Ma ad iseř Arebbi i iɣuyyan nnes,
\m xmi xas dd ɣa iwḍa řḥeṣran? \x ◘ \xo 27:9 \xt Ayub 35:12; Izhd. 18:42; 109:7; Awřn. 1:28; 28:9; Ica. 1:15; Irm. 14:12; Ḥiz. 8:18; Mixa 3:4; Yḥ. 9:31; Yaɛ. 4:3\x*
\m 
\v 10 Ma ad ifarḥ ɣar Umzemmar x kuřci?
\m Ma ad iřaɣa x Arebbi meřmi ma?
\m 
\v 11 Necc ad awem ssřemdeɣ x ufus n Arebbi,
\m min iɛewweř Umzemmar x kuřci,
\m war t ssnuffareɣ.
\m 
\v 12 Xzar, kenniw marra idwem teẓrim \add t\add*.
\m Mayemmi tarennyem
\m tessuffuɣem min ibeṭṭřen \add teqqarem\add*:
\b
\m 
\v 13 “Ta d tasɣart n bnadem aɛeffan ɣar SIDI,
\m tasɣart n ayt n bu-řexcunet
\m nni i ɣa ṭṭfen zeg Umzemmar x kuřci: \x ◘ \xo 27:13 \xt Ayub 20:29\x*
\m 
\v 14 Xmi ɣa mmarenyen iḥenjiren nnes,
\m i ssif umi urin.
\m Iɣedduten nnes war ttyawanen aɣrum, \f ◼ \fr 27:14 \fk Iɣedduten\ft - ixs ad yini ‘iḥenjiren nnes’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 27:14 \xt Aɛwd. 28:41; Ḥuc. 9:13\x*
\m 
\v 15 wi zzayes i ɣa yarewřen
\m ad ttwaneḍřen s ṭṭaɛun,
\m tijjař nnes war ttrunt ca. \x ◘ \xo 27:15 \xt Izhd. 78:64\x*
\m 
\v 16 Waxxa ijarruw nnuqart anect n ucař,
\m u issewjad arruḍ anect n ucař,
\m 
\v 17 \add iwa, waxxa\add* ad t issewjed,
\m amsegged ad zzayes yarḍ
\m uca amezdag ad ibḍa nnuqart. \x ◘ \xo 27:17 \xt Awřn. 28:8; Amb. 2:26\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ad ibna taddart nnes am tcinda,
\m amecnaw tanwalt
\m i issbedda uɛessas \add i yixef nnes\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Ad \add dayes\add* iṭṭeṣ d bu-wagřa,
\m \add maca\add* war yarenni deg wagřa nnes.
\m Mařa yarzem tiṭṭawin nnes,
\m war din ittɣimi \add ɛad\add* walu. \x ◘ \xo 27:19 \xt Izhd. 49:18\x*
\m 
\v 20 Inexřiɛen ad xas arenyen
\m am \add iɣezran n\add* waman,
\m taḥaryaḍt ad t-i-dd-teqḍeɛ s ǧiřet. \x ◘ \xo 27:20 \xt Ayub 15:21; 18:11\x*
\m 
\v 21 Asemmiḍ zi ccarq ad t iksi,
\m iwa dinni ittraḥ,
\m ad t-i-dd-iqřeɛ zeg wemcan nnes.
\m 
\v 22 \add Arebbi\add* ad issiweḍ marra aya
\m x uzeǧif nnes, war xas issɛizzi ca.
\m Ad yarweř deɣya zi \add tecti n\add* ufus nnes.
\m 
\v 23 \add Iwdan\add* ad xas wwten deg ifassen nsen
\m \add am zzayes sthezzan\add*
\m uca ad xas ṣeffaren
\m zeg wemcan \add n tzeddiɣt\add* nnes.”
\b
\b
\c 28
\s1 Řhard n Ayub x tiɣit
\m 
\v 1 S tidett, aqa din amcan
\m mani tᵉttwaf nnuqart,
\m uřa din amcan i wureɣ
\m mani t ssizdigen.
\m 
\v 2 Uzzař ttawyen t-i-dd zeg ucař
\m u zeg weẓru ssfessyen nnḥas.
\m 
\v 3 Igga \add bnadem\add* qeṭṭu i taǧest,
\m netta yarezzu di mkuř amcan mani ma,
\m \add x\add* weẓru \add i dd-itteffɣen\add*
\m zi tubbarcent d tiři n řmewt.
\m 
\v 4 Yarzem ijj n wexjiḍ
\m břa i ɣa yiři ḥed \add akides\add*.
\m Ttwattun zeg iḍaren \add n yinni sennej nsen\add*,
\m uyřen ttraḥen tasen-dd
\m břa i ɣa yarra asen-dd ḥed řbař.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Itteffeɣ-dd weɣrum zi temmurt,
\m \add am\add* swadday nnes \add marra\add*
\m axmi s tmessi inneqřeb.
\m 
\v 6 Iẓra nnes d amcan mani ttafen ṣaffir,
\m dayes i teǧa uřa d taɛejjact n wureɣ.
\m 
\v 7 Ajḍiḍ ittkeccaḍen war issin
\m amesruq i ɣares iǧan,
\m tiṭṭ n ujḍid amessɣuy amuqḍiɛ n tiṭṭawin
\m ɛemmarṣ war t teḥḍi.
\m 
\v 8 Iyraden imeẓyanen ineffxen
\m war dayes uyuren,
\m uřa d ayrad izehharen war t ittcuqi.
\b
\m 
\v 9 \add Maca bnadem\add* isarreḥ afus nnes
\m ɣar sseǧaḥ iqesḥen,
\m issneqřab idurar kuřci.
\m 
\v 10 Di řejruf iqqaz iɣezran,
\m tiṭṭ nnes tᵉttwařa marra min iɣřan.
\m 
\v 11 Iḥewweq i iɣezran
\m ařami \add aman\add* war qqimen tteffɣen-dd,
\m min \add dayes\add* inuffaren
\m ittawyi t-i-dd ɣar tfawt.
\m 
\v 12 Tiɣit \add maca\add*, mani tᵉttwaf?
\m U mani teǧa tzeddiɣt n řefhamet?
\b
\m 
\v 13 Bnadem war issin řqimet nnes,
\m war tᵉttwif \add tiɣit\add*
\m di temmurt n yinni iddaren.
\m 
\v 14 \add Aman\add* ihewřen qqaren:
\m ‘Dayneɣ war teǧi ca!’,
\m řebḥar iqqar: ‘Ɣari war da teǧi ca!’ \x ◘ \xo 28:14 \xt Ayub 28:22\x*
\m 
\v 15 War izemmar ad immewc
\m wureɣ iqquren
\m deg wemcan nnes,
\m ssum nnes war zemmaren
\m ad t weznen s nnuqart. \x ◘ \xo 28:15 \xt Awřn. 3:14; 8:11, 19; 16:16\x*
\m 
\v 16 War zemmaren ad weznen \add ssum nnes\add*
\m s wureɣ iɣřan zi Ufir,
\m s weẓru n uniks iɣřan d ṣaffir aziza.
\b
\m 
\v 17 War zemmaren
\m ad mmquddan řqimet nnes
\m ak-d wureɣ niɣ kristal,
\m niɣ ad tt beddřen
\m s ict n řqecɛet n wureɣ ittwaṣeffan.
\m 
\v 18 War tteɛqiřen \add ɛad\add* x tyaqutin
\m d weẓru n ukristal,
\m maɣar twafit n tiɣit tuɛɛřa
\m x \add twafit\add* n řmarjan.
\m 
\v 19 Řeɛqiq azeggwaɣ zi Kuc
\m war dayes yarwis,
\m war tzemmar ad tᵉttwawzen \add tiɣit\add*
\m s wureɣ iṣfan iɣřan.
\m 
\v 20 Manis dd-tusa \add xenni\add* tiɣit
\m u mani teǧa tzeddiɣt n řefhamet? \x ◘ \xo 28:20 \xt Ayub 28:12\x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 Aqa-tt tnuffar x tiṭṭawin
\m n marra min iddaren,
\m tᵉttwařeḥḥef x ijḍaḍ n ujenna.
\m 
\v 22 Ahellek d řmewt qqaren:
\m ‘S imezzuɣen nneɣ nesřa xas řexbar!’ \x ◘ \xo 28:22 \xt Ayub 28:14\x*
\m 
\v 23 AREBBI ifehhem abrid nnes,
\m Netta issen tazeddiɣt nnes,
\m 
\v 24 maɣar ittwařa ař tineggura n temmurt,
\m iẓarr marra min iǧan sadu ijenwan.
\b
\m 
\v 25 Umi igga i usemmiḍ jjehd nnes,
\m \add umi\add* iɛbar řeɛbar n waman, \x ◘ \xo 28:25 \xt Awřn. 8:29\x*
\m 
\v 26 umi igga i wenẓar qeṭṭu,
\m ijj n webrid i wassam n wajjajen,
\m 
\v 27 xenni iẓra i-tt, issargeb i-tt,
\m uca issbedd i-tt deg wemcan nnes
\m uca ibeqqec dayes,
\m 
\v 28 uca inna i bnadem:
\m ‘Xzar, tiggʷudi zi Sidi d tiɣit,
\m abeɛɛed x min iǧan d aɛeffan,
\m d řefhamet.’ \f ◼ \fr 28:28 \fk Sidi\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Sidi inu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 28:28 \xt Izhd. 111:10; Awřn. 1:7; 9:10\x*
\b
\b
\c 29
\s1 Ayub issiweř x mammec tuɣa tudart nnes qbeř
\m 
\v 1 Uca yarni issgeɛɛed \bd Ayub\bd* řhard n lmatal nnes, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Mři ǧiɣ am deg uyenni n iyuren iɛdun
\m aṭṭas zeg wami,
\m am deg uyenni n wussan
\m řami d ayi tuɣa iḥeṭṭa Arebbi,
\m 
\v 3 řami igga řefnar nnes
\m ad yareɣ x uzeǧif inu,
\m u tuɣa ggureɣ di taǧest s tfawt nnes.
\m 
\v 4 \add Mři\add* ǧiɣ am deg wussan n temẓi inu,
\m umi amuni di řaman ak-d Arebbi
\m tuɣa ibedd x tqiḍunt inu,
\m 
\v 5 umi Amzemmar x kuřci
\m tuɣa-t ɛad akidi,
\m u iḥenjiren inu \add ɛad\add* nnḍen ayi-dd,
\m 
\v 6 umi iṣuraf inu tuɣa ɛummen di trussi,
\m u taṣḍart tuɣa tᵉttzeǧaɛ zzati
\m tiɣezratin n zzect!
\b
\m 
\v 7 Umi dd-ffɣeɣ ɣar tewwart n tendint,
\m jjiɣ ssbedden ayi řkursi inu deg wazzay,
\m 
\v 8 nnufaren iḥudriyyen řami d ayi ẓrin,
\m u imeccaybuten kkaren, qqimen bedden.
\m 
\v 9 Řḥukkam menɛen awařen nsen
\m u ssarsen afus x uqemmum nsen.
\m 
\v 10 Tmijja n řḥukkam tesqar,
\m iřseq iřes nsen ɣar waneɣ nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 11 Mařa isřa ayi umezzuɣ, issemɣar ayi,
\m mařa teẓra ayi tiṭṭ, teched x řxaḍar inu.
\m 
\v 12 Maɣar ssnejmeɣ řmeskin nni isɣuyen,
\m ayujiř nni war ɣares tuɣi
\m wenni t i ɣa iɛawnen. \x ◘ \xo 29:12 \xt Izhd. 72:12; Awřn. 21:13\x*
\m 
\v 13 Řxaḍar n wenni tuɣa ɛřayen ad ihellek,
\m tusa-dd xafi,
\m uř n tajjač ggiɣ t isřiwřew s řefraḥet.
\m 
\v 14 Yarḍeɣ tasegda u \add tasegda\add* tessyarḍ ayi.
\m Tuɣa ccreɛ inu am useřham u am areẓẓet. \x ◘ \xo 29:14 \xt Ica. 59:17; Afa. 6:10-17; 1 Ts. 5:8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 15 Tuɣa ayi d tiṭṭawin i idarɣařen,
\m uřa d iḍaren i iqiḍaren.
\m 
\v 16 Tuɣa ayi d babatsen i imezřaḍ,
\m uca ddeɛwet n wenni war ssineɣ,
\m beqqceɣ tt.
\m 
\v 17 Arẓiɣ tiɣmas n teɣmart
\m n wenni iggin min war iseggden
\m uca kkseɣ zzardet i teɣmas nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Nniɣ: ‘Ad ssuffɣeɣ buḥbeř inu
\m x řɛucc inu,
\m ad ddareɣ tudart tazirart
\m am ujḍid n funiks.’
\m 
\v 19 Iẓewran inu bezzɛeɣ ten ař aman
\m u di ǧiřet iqqim nnda x řefruɛ inu.
\m 
\v 20 Tuɣa řɛezz inu iqqim akidi \add řebda\add*,
\m řqews inu isheř deg ufus inu \add řebda\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 21 Sřin-dd ɣari, rajan,
\m sqaren di ṭṭweɛ n ccwar inu.
\m 
\v 22 Awarni wawař inu
\m war ssiwřen twařa nneɣni,
\m awařen inu udumen xasen.
\m 
\v 23 Nitni rajan ayi am \add rajan\add* anẓar,
\m arzmen aqemmum nsen
\m am t arezmen ɣar wenẓar n tefsut.
\m 
\v 24 \add Mařa\add* sfarnineɣ ɣarsen,
\m war zemmaren \add ɛad\add* ad ttiqqen,
\m \add maca\add* tafawt n uɣembub inu
\m war zmiren ad kides mmɛařan.
\m 
\v 25 Ixḍareɣ asen abrid,
\m beddeɣ asen ɣar uzeǧif,
\m zedɣeɣ am ujeǧid jar řɛeskar,
\m am wenni ittɛezzan inni iceḍnen.
\b
\b
\c 30
\s1 Ayub issiweř x řemḥayem nnes n yiḍa
\m 
\v 1 Řexxu maca tuɣa ḍeḥḥcen xafi iḥudriyyen
\m nni iǧan d imeẓyanen xafi deg wussan,
\m inni babatsen war ɣari sekkwin
\m maḥend ad ten ggeɣ
\m ɣar yiṭan i iǧan x wuǧi inu.
\m 
\v 2 Min ɣa ggeɣ \add xenni\add* s jjehd n ifassen nsen?
\m Aqa ifna \add jjehd nsen\add* zi ssibbet n tewsar.
\m 
\v 3 Zi řqiǧet u zi řaẓ dewřen isriwen,
\m ttmeɣzazen di řwaṭa yuẓɣen
\m di tubbarcent \add teccur\add*
\m s ureddeǧ d urebbej.
\m 
\v 4 Nitni řeqqḍen řebzar ameǧaḥ jar cbarq,
\m iẓewran n uzezzu d aɣrum nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Uẓẓřen xasen zi tmunet \add n iwdan\add*,
\m kkwaren ten am yixewwanen,
\m 
\v 6 ḥima ad zedɣen di teɣzurin issaggʷaden,
\m deg ifran n ucař u di řejruf.
\m 
\v 7 Sɣuyyun jar cbarq,
\m sadu tizeggwarin ssmunan.
\m 
\v 8 Tarwa n ibuhařiyyen d tarwa břa isem,
\m d inni uẓẓřen xasen zi temmurt s uzeǧaḍ.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Řexxu maca aqa ayi
\m deg izři nsen n tẓawart,
\m dewřeɣ asen i řhard. \f ◼ \fr 30:9 \fk izři nsen tẓawart\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘azenzun nsen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 30:9 \xt Ayub 17:6; Izhd. 69:13; Igjd. 3:14, 63\x*
\m 
\v 10 Carrhen ayi, ttaggʷajen xafi,
\m war ttseḍḥin ca
\m maḥend ad ssusfen x uɣembub inu. \x ◘ \xo 30:10 \xt Ayub 19:19\x*
\m 
\v 11 Maɣar Netta issefsi asɣun \add n tqiḍunt\add* inu
\m uca issehwa ayi.
\m Nitni nḍaren ssrimet \add nsen\add* zzati. \f ◼ \fr 30:11 \fk zzati\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i uɣembub inu’.\f*
\m 
\v 12 Ɣar uɣezdis afusi \add inu\add*
\m kkaren-dd xafi iɣeddiwen n tarrawt,
\m ɛarrnen iḍaren inu,
\m ssgeɛɛaden xafi imesraq n arẓiyyet nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Abrid inu arẓin t,
\m arennyen tamara x tamara inu
\m waxxa nitni simant nsen
\m war ɣarsen iǧi wi d asen ɣa iwcen afus.
\m 
\v 14 Axmi dd-ttasen
\m zeg ijj n unuqqib d miriw,
\m ttakkwaḍen am řemwaj yareddǧen.
\m 
\v 15 Ttwakebben-dd xafi inexřiɛen,
\m am usemmiḍ ḍeffaren nitni ccan inu,
\m iḍwa zzhar inu am yijj n useynu.
\b
\m 
\v 16 \add S uya\add* ifessi řexxu řeɛmar inu dayi,
\m ussan n řeɣben mennɛen ayi.
\m 
\v 17 Di ǧiřet issnuqqub ayi
\m iɣsan inu i dayi iǧan,
\m řeḥriq i d ayi ittɣezzan war yaressi.
\m 
\v 18 Ittwabeddeř warrud inu
\m s jjehd \add nnes\add* ameqqran
\m ařami war xafi tteɛqiřen \add ɛad\add*.
\m Icarf ayi am tma i innḍen
\m i warzem n yiri deg warruḍ.
\m 
\v 19 Inḍar ayi deg ubeǧaɛ,
\m dewřeɣ am ucař d yiɣɣeḍ.
\b
\m 
\v 20 Sɣuyyuɣ ɣarek,
\m \add maca\add* Cek war xafi dd-tᵉttarrid,
\m necc beddeɣ da
\m uca Cek tᵉqqimed tḥeṭṭid dayi.
\m 
\v 21 Cek tdewřed ayi am yijj n bu-řexcunet,
\m tᵉttdarraced xafi s ufus nnec ijehden.
\m 
\v 22 Cek tessgeɛɛaded ayi
\m u tneddhed ayi deg usemmiḍ,
\m tessefraɣed \add qaɛ\add* addud inu.
\m 
\v 23 Maɣar necc ssneɣ
\m aqa Cek ad ayi tnedhed ɣar řmewt,
\m ɣar taddart mani ttmunen
\m marra inni iddaren. \x ◘ \xo 30:23 \xt Ɛbr. 9:27\x*
\b
\m 
\v 24 Ma war ineṭṭar \add bnadem\add* afus \add nnes\add*
\m mařa iwḍa \add ḥed\add*,
\m ma war isɣuyyu walu qaɛ
\m ɣar arẓiyyet \add nnes\add*?
\m 
\v 25 Ma war ruɣ x wenni tuɣa ɣar iǧa
\m wussan n tamara,
\m ma war icḍin buḥbeř inu x umezřuḍ? \x ◘ \xo 30:25 \xt Izhd. 35:13, 14; Rum. 12:15\x*
\m 
\v 26 Umi ssitmeɣ ɣar min iṣebḥen,
\m aqa yusa-dd min iǧan d aɛeffan,
\m umi rajiɣ tafawt, tusa-dd taǧest.
\m 
\v 27 Adan inu ttnennan, war arsin,
\m iwḍen-dd wussan n tamara ɣari.
\b
\m 
\v 28 Necc ad uyureɣ deg wecḍan,
\m břa řehmu \add n tfuct\add*.
\m Ad kkareɣ deg wegraw \add n řgens\add*
\m uca ad qqimeɣ sɣuyyuɣ deg ujenna.
\m 
\v 29 I wuccanen n řexřa
\m dewřeɣ d umatsen zzaysen,
\m i yessis n nnɛamet d amɛacar. \x ◘ \xo 30:29 \xt Izhd. 102:7\x*
\m 
\v 30 Tiřmect inu tedweř xafi
\m d akarkuc abarcan,
\m zi tmessi cemmḍen iɣsan inu. \x ◘ \xo 30:30 \xt Izhd. 119:83; Igjd. 4:8; 5:10\x*
\m 
\v 31 Tedweř \add tirart n\add* řgambri inu i wecḍan,
\m tamja inu i řḥess n imeṭṭawen.
\b
\b
\c 31
\s1 Ayub iceffeɛ belli war dayes bu řɛib
\m 
\v 1 Necc ggiɣ řɛahd
\m ak-d tiṭṭawin inu,
\m mammec i ɣa xzareɣ \add xenni\add* di teɛzarect? \x ◘ \xo 31:1 \xt Izhd. 7:4-6; 15:1-5\x*
\m 
\v 2 Maɣar min \add iǧan xenni\add* tasɣart
\m n Arebbi zi sennej,
\m niɣ tasɣart n řwart n Umzemmar x kuřci
\m zeg \add ijenwan\add* yuɛřan?
\m 
\v 3 Ma war iǧi aḍeyyeɛ ikkar-dd i uɛeffan,
\m arẓiyyet i yinni itteggen řmuɛṣiyyet?
\m 
\v 4 Ma war ittwiři Netta ibriden inu,
\m ma war iḥesseb Netta řqedd
\m n marra iṣuraf inu? \x ◘ \xo 31:4 \xt 2 Im. 16:9; Ayub 34:21; Awřn. 5:21; 15:3; Irm. 32:19\x*
\b
\m 
\v 5 Mařa tuɣa uyureɣ di řexdeɛ,
\m niɣ iqeǧeq uḍar inu ɣar řɣecc,
\m 
\v 6 ejj SIDI ad ayi iwzen \add xenni\add*
\m di řmizanat iseggden,
\m \add ařami\add* i ɣa issen Arebbi řeṣfayet inu.
\m 
\v 7 Mařa iṣuraf inu ffɣen zeg webrid,
\m uř inu iḍfar tiṭṭawin inu
\m uca \add xenni\add* iřṣeq řɛib deg ifassen inu,
\m 
\v 8 \add xenni\add* ad zarɛeɣ necc,
\m \add maca\add* ijjen nneɣni ad icc,
\m u min ɣari dd-iɣemmayen ad ittwaqřeɛ!
\b
\m 
\v 9 Mařa uř inu ittwaɣwa ɣar ict n temɣart,
\m niɣ tuɣa ttḥamiɣ
\m ɣar tewwart n wajjar inu, \x ◘ \xo 31:9 \xt Ayub 24:15; Awřn. 7:25\x*
\m 
\v 10 ejj \add xenni\add* tamɣart inu
\m ad teḥri \add imendi\add* i yijjen nneɣni,
\m \add jjem\add* inneɣni ad xas aḍaren.
\m 
\v 11 Maɣar aya d řefḍiḥet,
\m d ict n ljarima \add i xas i ɣa wten\add* řquḍat.
\m 
\v 12 Maɣar aya d timessi tᵉttett ař ahellek,
\m tqeǧeɛ marra řɣiǧet inu.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Mařa ssḥeqqareɣ řḥeqq
\m n ismeɣ inu d tayya inu,
\m řami tuɣa ttemcubbucen akidi,
\m 
\v 14 min i ɣa ggeɣ \add xenni\add* mařa SIDI ikkar,
\m mařa Netta iqeǧeb ayi,
\m min xas dd ɣa yarreɣ \add xenni\add*? \x ◘ \xo 31:14 \xt Izhd. 44:22\x*
\m 
\v 15 Wenni d ayi iggin deg uɛeddis n yemma,
\m ma war t iggi uřa d netta?
\m Ma war iǧi d Ijj wenni d aneɣ dd-ixeřqen
\m deg uɛeddis n yemmatneɣ? \x ◘ \xo 31:15 \xt Ayub 34:19; Awřn. 14:31; 17:5\x*
\b
\m 
\v 16 Mařa qemmḥeɣ ameẓri n imezřaḍ
\m niɣ ssruɣ tiṭṭawin n tajjač,
\m 
\v 17 mařa necc mɣir cciɣ
\m ařeqquz n weɣrum inu,
\m am war zzayes icci uyujiř,
\m 
\v 18 - maɣar zi temẓi iyma netta ɣari
\m am iyma ɣar babas,
\m zeg uɛeddis n yemma nedheɣ tt -
\b
\m 
\v 19 mařa ẓriɣ ijjen ittwahellek
\m minzi war ɣares iǧi warruḍ,
\m niɣ minzi war din iǧi dduri i umezřuḍ,
\m 
\v 20 mařa \add ɛemmarṣ\add* war d ayi barkent
\m tejɛinnatin nnes,
\m minzi igga ad issiḥma ixef nnes
\m s waǧas \add n tḍuft\add* n izmaren inu,
\m 
\v 21 mařa afus inu ihudd x uyujiř,
\m minzi ẓriɣ aqa din twiza i necc
\m ɣar tewwart \add n tendint\add*, \f ◼ \fr 31:21 \ft \bd afessar\bd* - di tewwart n tendint aqa din amcan n řquḍat. Mařa řquḍat wwar carrɛen nican, ixs ad yini ixḍaren ṭṭarf n bu-wagřa niɣ n yenni ɣarsen ṣṣulṭa, ad dewřen ḥeṣṣaren i imezřad di tewwura n tendint.\f*
\m 
\v 22 ejj \add xenni\add* ad ayi tewḍa
\m teɣruḍt inu zeg ijiman,
\m ad ayi yarẓ uɣiř inu zeg yiɣes!
\m 
\v 23 Maɣar ad xafi dd-iwḍa
\m unexřiɛ ameqqran,
\m ict n řmuṣibet zi ɣar Arebbi,
\m war zemmareɣ ad ggeɣ walu
\m zzat i Uɛuǧi nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 24 Mařa ggiɣ ureɣ d atecři inu,
\m niɣ nniɣ i wureɣ iɣřan aṭṭas:
\m ‘Cek d řaman inu!’, \x ◘ \xo 31:24 \xt Mk. 10:24; 1 Tim. 6:17\x*
\m 
\v 25 mařa farḥeɣ umi imɣar wagřa inu,
\m umi afus inu iṭṭef aṭṭas \add d agřa\add*, \x ◘ \xo 31:25 \xt Izhd. 62:11\x*
\m 
\v 26 mařa ẓriɣ tafawt \add n tfuct\add* xmi tᵉttwesseg,
\m niɣ taziri xmi teggur di tissiqt \add nnes\add*, \x ◘ \xo 31:26 \xt Aɛwd. 4:19\x*
\m 
\v 27 uca ittwaɣwa wuř inu s tnuffra,
\m uca aqemmum inu, issudem i-t ufus inu,
\m 
\v 28 \add xenni\add* iři uřa d man aya d řmuɛṣiyyet
\m ad tt wcen i řquḍat,
\m maɣar \add xenni\add* ad nkareɣ Arebbi
\m nni iǧan sennej.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Mařa farḥeɣ i arẓiyyet
\m n wenni d ayi icarrhen,
\m farḥeɣ umi t iřqef řɣar! \x ◘ \xo 31:29 \xt Awřn. 17:5\x*
\m 
\v 30 Necc \add maca\add* war jjiɣ aneɣ inu ad ixḍa,
\m umi kkwareɣ řeɛmar nnes s nneɛřet! \x ◘ \xo 31:30 \xt Mt. 5:44; Rum. 12:14\x*
\b
\m 
\v 31 Mařa iryazen nni iǧan deg uqiḍun inu
\m war qqaren:
\m ‘Man wen war ittwassjiwnen
\m zeg yinni iksin zeg weysum nnes?’
\m 
\v 32 Uřa d ijj n řbarrani
\m war issens \add di barra\add* x webrid,
\m \add maɣar\add* i umsebrid arzmeɣ tiwwura inu.\x ◘ \xo 31:32 \xt Ɛbr. 13:2; 1 Bṭ. 4:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 33 Mařa necc, am Adam, dřiɣ axeṭṭu inu,
\m umi ssnuffareɣ řmuɛṣiyyet inu
\m deg weḥsin inu, \f ◼ \fr 31:33 \fk aḥsin\ft - niɣ ‘abeḥrur’.\f*
\m 
\v 34 minzi ggʷedeɣ zi řɣaci ameqqran,
\m niɣ issnexřeɛ ayi useḥqar n řwacun inu,
\m ařami qqimeɣ sseɣdeɣ,
\m war ffiɣeɣ \add ɛad\add* zi tewwart \add ɣar barra\add* ...
\b
\m 
\v 35 Mři ɣari ijjen wenni d ayi ɣa isřen.
\m Xzar, acemmiɛ inu
\m - Amzemmar x kuřci ad xafi dd-yarr -
\m uřa d adlis ittwannḍen nni t yura
\m weryaz nni kidi ittemcubbucen. \x ◘ \xo 31:35 \xt 1 Jh\x*
\m 
\v 36 Meɛlik ufiɣ ma war t arebbuɣ
\m x tɣarḍt inu,
\m ad t qqneɣ \add i uzeǧif inu\add* am yijj n ttaj.
\m 
\v 37 Iwa, ad as iniɣ řqedd n iṣuraf inu,
\m ad ɣares dd-qarrbeɣ am yijj n řḥakem.
\b
\m 
\v 38 Mařa řeɛraṣi inu isɣuy xafi,
\m iɛeyyaden nnes ad run
\m ak-d wayawya \add marra\add*,
\m 
\v 39 mařa cciɣ ṣṣabet nnes nhřa axeǧeṣ,
\m niɣ ggiɣ řeɛmar n ixemmasen nnes
\m iḍřeq i buḥbeř,
\m 
\v 40 ejj \add xenni\add* ad iɣmi cbarq ak-d isennanen
\m deg wemcan n yirden,
\m uřa d řeɛcub yarṣuden
\m deg wemcan n imendi.
\b
\m Aqa da i qḍan wawařen n Ayub.
\b
\b
\c 32
\s1 Řhard amezwaru n Ilihu: Tamezwarut
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* ssbedden třata n yeryazen nni maḥend ad dd-arren x Ayub, minzi tuɣa d amsegged jar tiṭṭawin \add n yixef\add* nnes.
\v 2 \add Xas uca\add* yarɣa lɣaḍab n Ilihu, mmis n Baraxyil, zi \add temmurt n\add* Buz, zi řaǧ n Ram. Yarɣa lɣaḍab nnes x Ayub minzi igga wanita ixef nnes d amsegged x AREBBI.
\v 3 Yarɣa lɣaḍab nnes uřa x třata n imeddukkař nnes, maɣar nitni, \add waxxa\add* war ufin min zi \add xas\add* i dd ɣa yarren, arrin řɛib di Ayub.
\b
\m 
\v 4 Ilihu \add maca\add* tuɣa iraja s wawařen qibač i Ayub, minzi nitni tuɣa mɣaren xas.
\v 5 \add Umi\add* iẓra Ilihu, aqa třata n yeryazen nni war ufin min zi dd ɣa yarren \add ɛad\add*, yarɣa uxeyyeq nnes.
\v 6 Uca iṭṭef \bd Ilihu\bd*, mmis n Baraxil, zi Buz, deg wawař, inna:
\b
\m Necc d ameẓyan deg iseggʷusa
\m u kenniw d imeccaybuten.
\m X uya rajiɣ u bburrneɣ
\m maḥend ad awem ssecneɣ tussna inu. \x ◘ \xo 32:6 \xt Ayub 32:4, 7; 15:10\x*
\m 
\v 7 Necc nniɣ:
\m ‘Ejj \add inni imɣaren deg\add* wussan ad ssiwřen,
\m \add ejj\add* řqedd ameqqran
\m n iseggʷusa \add n umeccaybu\add* ad issargeb tiɣit.’
\b
\m 
\v 8 S tidett, buḥbeř izdeɣ di bnadem,
\m asuḍi n nnefs n Umzemmar x kuřci
\m ittic asen řefhamet. \x ◘ \xo 32:8 \xt Ayub 12:13; 38:36; Awřn. 2:6; Amb. 2:26; Dan. 1:17; 2:21\x*
\m 
\v 9 Inni imɣaren deg iseggʷusa
\m war daysen teǧi tiɣit,
\m iwessura war fehhmen i ccreɛ. \x ◘ \xo 32:9 \xt Ayub 12:12\x*
\m 
\v 10 S uya qqareɣ: ‘Sřem-dd ɣari,
\m \add xenni\add* uřa d necc ad ssecneɣ tussna inu.’
\b
\m 
\v 11 Xzar, rajiɣ awařen nwem,
\m ssḥesseɣ ɣar řefhamet nwem,
\m am tuɣa tarezzum x wawařen \add iseggmen\add*.
\m 
\v 12 Necc ḥḍiɣ kenniw mliḥ,
\m aqa da, uřa d ijjen tuɣa izemmar
\m ad isseqneɛ Ayub,
\m uřa d ijjen zzaywem war izemmar
\m ad dd-yarr x wawařen nnes.
\m 
\v 13 \add S uya\add* war qqarem:
\m ‘Neccin nufa tiɣit!
\m Arebbi izemmar ad t inḍar,
\m war iǧi bnadem.’
\m 
\v 14 War ǧin wawařen nnes xafi
\m u s wawařen nwem war xas dd-arriɣ.
\b
\m 
\v 15 Ttwarnan nitni, war dd-ttarrin ɛad,
\m awařen ttwakksen zzaysen.
\m 
\v 16 Řajiɣ, \add maca\add* war ssiwřen,
\m maɣar ssbedden \add awař\add*,
\m war dd-ttarrin ɛad.
\m 
\v 17 Uřa d necc xseɣ
\m ad dd-arreɣ di nnubet inu,
\m uřa d necc ad ssecneɣ tussna inu.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Maɣar ccureɣ s wawařen,
\m iḥessar ayi buḥbeř di daxeř inu.
\m 
\v 19 Xzar, aɛeddis inu ittegg
\m am \add tziyyat n\add* binu
\m war yarzimen \add ɛad\add*,
\m am txuncay n yiřem n jdid,
\m aqa ittegg axmi i ɣa idduqqez.
\m 
\v 20 Ad ssiwřeɣ, ḥima ad fsuseɣ,
\m ad arzmeɣ iyencicen inu, ad dd-arreɣ.
\m 
\v 21 War tteggiɣ s wudmawen ak-d uřa d ijj,
\m war ssiwřeɣ uřa ak-d ijj n bnadem
\m s wawařen imiẓiden.
\m 
\v 22 Maɣar war zemmareɣ ad ggeɣ
\m s wawařen imiziḍen,
\m maɣar \add xenni\add* ad ayi ikkes
\m Wenni i d ayi iggin.
\b
\b
\c 33
\s1 Ilihu yarenni di řḥard amezwaru nnes
\m 
\v 1 Seř řexxu ɣar řhard inu, Ayub,
\m ewc amezzuɣ i wawařen inu marra.
\m 
\v 2 Xzar, arzmeɣ aqemmum inu,
\m issawař yiřes inu sadu waneɣ inu.
\m 
\v 3 Tteffɣen wawařen inu
\m zi řeṣfayet n wuř inu,
\m tussna teqqur ad xas harrden
\m iyencicen inu.
\b
\m 
\v 4 Arruḥ n Arebbi igga ayi,
\m asuḍi n nnefs n Umzemmar x kuřci
\m iwca ayi tudart.
\m 
\v 5 Mařa tzemmared, arr-dd xafi.
\m Sars ayi \add tamesřact\add*, bedd \add zzati\add*!
\m 
\v 6 Xzar, necc am cek zzat i Arebbi,
\m uřa d necc ttwaggeɣ zeg ubeǧaɛ. \x ◘ \xo 33:6 \xt Ayub 9:35; 23:10\x*
\m 
\v 7 Xzar, ahuddi inu
\m war cek issiggʷid ca,
\m war xak ttzeyyareɣ ca aṭṭas.
\b
\m 
\v 8 S tidett, aqa tennid \add t\add*
\m deg imezzuɣen inu,
\m sřiɣ i řḥess n wawařen\add -a\add*: \x ◘ \xo 33:8 \xt Ayub 10:7; 16:17; 23:10, 11; 27:5\x*
\m 
\v 9 ‘Necc d amezdag, břa ddenb,
\m d afurri \add i ǧiɣ\add*,
\m war dayi ca n řmuɛṣiyyet.
\m 
\v 10 Xzar, Netta yarezzu ssibbet
\m ḥima ad zzayi icetca,
\m iḥesseb ayi d řeɛdu nnes. \x ◘ \xo 33:10 \xt Ayub 13:24; 16:9; 19:11\x*
\m 
\v 11 Iḍaren inu iqqen i-ten ɣar ukeccuḍ,
\m iḥeṭṭa marra imesraq inu.’ \x ◘ \xo 33:11 \xt Ayub 13:27; 14:16\x*
\m 
\v 12 Xzar, ad ac iniɣ,
\m war teǧid ca d amsegged deg uya,
\m maɣar Arebbi d ameqqran x bnadem.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Min xef kides tᵉttemɛarrid?
\m Aqa Netta war ittegg řeḥsab
\m i marra timegga nnes!
\m 
\v 14 Maɣar Arebbi issawař ict n twařa,
\m \add wah,\add* tnayen n twařawin,
\m \add maca\add* bnadem war iḥeṭṭi:
\m 
\v 15 di tirja, s ijj n řewḥiy di ǧiřet,
\m xmi dd-iweṭṭa yiḍeṣ yuǧɣen x iwdan,
\m deg unudem di řectu.
\m 
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* yarezzem Netta
\m amezzuɣ n iwdan,
\m ittcemmeɛ \add s ucemmiɛ nnes\add*
\m x uweddeb nsen,
\m 
\v 17 ḥima ad issḥeyyed bnadem
\m x tmeggit nnes \add taɛeffant\add*,
\m ḥima ad issbedd nnfaxet x weryaz.
\m 
\v 18 Netta imenneɛ řeɛmar nnes zi turṣuḍi,
\m tudart nnes zeg uhellek s lansa.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Ijeyyeḥ i-t řeḥriq di qama nnes
\m uřa d amenɣi řebda deg iɣsan nnes.
\m 
\v 20 Tudart nnes tarra i-t ittɛiffa aɣrum
\m u řeɛmar nnes \add yarra i-t ittɛiffa\add*
\m macca iṣebḥen aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 33:20 \xt Izhd. 107:18\x*
\m 
\v 21 Iqeṭṭa weysum nnes zeg wudem \add nnes\add*,
\m ixsan nnes nni war ttwaẓrin \add ɛemmarṣ\add*,
\m aqa ttbanen řexxu.
\m 
\v 22 Ittqarrab řeɛmar nnes ɣar turṣuḍi,
\m tudart nnes ɣar ijarrayen n řmewt.
\b
\m 
\v 23 Mařa xenni din ijj n lmalak
\m ibedd as-dd ɣar uɣezdis,
\m ijj n Řɛadeř, ijjen zeg wařef,
\m ḥima ad isscen i bnadem tasegda nnes,
\m 
\v 24 \add xenni\add* ad xas iḥinn, ad yini:
\m ‘Fekk i-t, ařami netta
\m war ihekkwi ɣar turṣuḍi \add deg wenḍeř\add*,
\m aqa Necc ufiɣ aṣřaḥ \add xas\add*!’
\b
\m 
\v 25 Xenni ad tneɛneɛ arrimet nnes
\m ktar zi ṭṭri n temẓi,
\m ad dd-idweř ɣar wussan n temẓi nnes.
\m 
\v 26 Netta ad ittar Arebbi s tutra yuǧɣen
\m u Netta ad xas yarḍa,
\m ařami wanita ad iẓar udem nnes
\m deg usřiwřew \add n řefraḥet\add*,
\m u \add ammu\add* i ɣa yarr Netta
\m i bnadem tasegda nnes. \x ◘ \xo 33:26 \xt Izhd. 50:15; Ica. 58:9\x*
\m 
\v 27 Ad iɣennej i yewdan, ad yini:
\m ‘Necc xḍiɣ, ssfarɣeɣ min iseggden,
\m \add maca\add* Netta war zzayi \add tt\add* yexřif.
\m 
\v 28 Ifekk Arebbi řeɛmar inu
\m zi turṣuḍi \add deg wenḍeř\add*,
\m tudart inu txezzar
\m \add ammu d wammu\add* di tfawt.’
\b
\m 
\v 29 Xzar, marra aya ittegg i-t Arebbi,
\m tnayen niɣ třata n twařawin
\m ak-d weryaz,
\m 
\v 30 ḥima ad isseɛqeb řeɛmar nnes
\m zi turṣuḍi \add deg wenḍeř\add*,
\m \add ḥima\add* ad t yarr yareqq s tfawt n tudart. \x ◘ \xo 33:30 \xt Izhd. 56:14\x*
\m 
\v 31 Ḥḍa, Ayub! Seř-dd ɣari!
\m Sqar, xenni necc ad ssiwřeɣ.
\m 
\v 32 Mařa ɣarek awařen \add wejden\add*,
\m arr-dd \add xafi\add*,
\m siweř, maɣar ɣari s řxaḍar
\m ad xak barriɣ.
\m 
\v 33 Mařa lla, seř-dd ɣari!
\m Sqar, u ad ac ssɣareɣ tiɣit.
\b
\b
\c 34
\s1 Řhard wiss tnayen n Ilihu x mammec ittegg Arebbi řebda s řḥeqq
\m 
\v 1 Iṭṭef \bd Ilihu\bd* \add ɛawed\add* deg wawař, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Sřem-dd ɣar wawařen inu, \add a\add* imiɣisen,
\m wcem ayi amezzuɣ,
\m \add a kenniw\add*, ayt n tussna.
\m 
\v 3 Maɣar amezzuɣ inebbec deg wawařen,
\m \add am mammec\add* ittqasa waneɣ macca. \x ◘ \xo 34:3 \xt Ayub 12:11\x*
\m 
\v 4 Jjem aneɣ ad nixḍar jar aneɣ
\m min iǧan nican,
\m jjem aneɣ ad nessen jar aneɣ
\m min iǧan d aṣebḥan.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Maɣar Ayub inna: ‘Necc d amsegged,
\m Arebbi ikkes ayi tasɣart inu! \x ◘ \xo 34:5 \xt Ayub 27:2\x*
\m 
\v 6 Waxxa ɣari řḥeqq,
\m \add ɛad\add* ttɣimeɣ ttbaneɣ
\m am yijj n bu-ixarriqen!
\m \add Ayezzim n\add* fřitca i dayi iǧa,
\m war izemmar ad ittwassgenfa
\m am war din iǧi uɛeddi.’ \x ◘ \xo 34:6 \xt Ayub 6:4\x*
\m 
\v 7 Man wen iǧan d aryaz am Ayub,
\m wenni isessen astehzi am waman?
\m 
\v 8 Netta iggur deg webrid am ittɛacar
\m inni itteggen řmuɛṣiyyet,
\m iggur ak-d iryazen iɛeffanen.
\m 
\v 9 Maɣar inna: ‘War ineffeɛ walu i bnadem,
\m mařa netta d amarḍi ɣar AREBBI.’
\b
\m 
\v 10 S uya sřem-dd ɣari,
\m \add kenniw\add* iryazen i di teǧa řefhamet:
\m ‘Iggʷej x Arebbi maḥend ad yegg tuɛeffna,
\m uřa x Umzemmar x kuřci
\m maḥend ad yegg min ifarɣen.’ \x ◘ \xo 34:10 \xt Aɛwd. 32:4; 2 Im. 19:7; Ayub 8:3; 36:23; Izhd. 92:16; Rum. 9:14\x*
\m 
\v 11 Maɣar Netta ixřef zi bnadem
\m ɛlaḥsab timegga nnes,
\m u am mammec iǧa webrid n weryaz,
\m \add ammu\add* i d as ɣa yarr ad t yaf. \x ◘ \xo 34:11 \xt Izhd. 62:13; Awřn. 24:12; Irm. 17:10; 32:19; Ḥiz. 7:27; 33:20; Mt. 16:27; Rum. 2:6; 1 Kur. 3:8; 2 Kur. 5:10; Afa. 6:8; Kul. 3:25; 1 Bṭ. 1:17; Asa. 22:12\x*
\b
\m 
\v 12 S tidett, ɛemmarṣ war ittegg
\m Arebbi tuɛeffna,
\m Amzemmar x kuřci war issfarriɣ ccreɛ.
\m 
\v 13 Man wen t iwekkřen x temmurt,
\m man wen issarsen marra ddunect?
\m 
\v 14 Mařa Netta ad xas issneqřeb uř nnes,
\m mařa ad ɣares dd-yawi ɛawed
\m buḥbeř nnes d nnefs nnes, \x ◘ \xo 34:14 \xt Izhd. 104:29; Amb. 12:7\x*
\m 
\v 15 marra bnadem d řmař
\m ad ssuffɣen buḥbeř
\m u bnadem ad iɛqeb ɣar ucař. \x ◘ \xo 34:15 \xt Amz. 3:19; Amb. 12:7\x*
\b
\m 
\v 16 Mařa dayek řefhamet, seř \add xenni\add* i man aya,
\m ewc amezzuɣ nnec
\m i řḥess n wawařen inu.
\m 
\v 17 Ma izemmar wenni icarrhen řḥeqq
\m ad iḥkem,
\m niɣ texsed cek ad tedɛid
\m x wenni iǧan d Amsegged d ameqqran? \x ◘ \xo 34:17 \xt Amz. 18:25; Ayub 5:18; 8:3; 21:22; Rum. 3:5\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ma ad inin i ujeǧid:
\m ‘\add Cek\add* war tsekkʷid walu!’
\m u i tarwa n taṣiřet: ‘\add Kenniw\add* d iɛeffanen’?
\m 
\v 19 \add Mammec xenni\add* i Wenni
\m war issizwiřin řḥukkam
\m u war ittriḥ ak-d bu-wagřa x umezřuḍ,
\m maɣar marra nitni
\m d řxedmet n ifassen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 34:19 \xt Aɛwd. 10:17; 2 Im. 19:7; Ayub 37:24; Řex. 10:34; Rum. 2:11; Gal. 2:6; Afa. 6:9; Kul. 3:25; 1 Bṭ. 1:17\x*
\m 
\v 20 Mmuten deg wermac n wabřiwen,
\m deg wezyen n ǧiřet.
\m Ttwanhezzen nitni, řgens \add nni\add*,
\m uca hellken.
\m Wenni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa
\m ittwaɛarren ɣar uɣezdis,
\m břa \add ma iḥada i-t\add* ufus \add n bnadem\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 21 Maɣar tiṭṭawin nnes xezzarent
\m ɣar ibriden n mkuř ijj,
\m Netta ittwařa mliḥ marra iṣuraf nsen. \x ◘ \xo 34:21 \xt 2 Im. 16:9; Ayub 31:4; Izhd. 34:16; Awřn. 5:21; 15:3; Irm. 16:17; 32:19\x*
\m 
\v 22 War teǧi tubbarcent
\m u war teǧi tiři n řmewt,
\m mani zemmaren ad nnuffaren
\m inni itteggen řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 34:22 \xt Izhd. 139:12; Ɛam. 9:2, 3; Ɛbr. 4:13\x*
\m 
\v 23 War d as ittxeṣṣi ad ixzar
\m di bnadem aṭṭas n řweqt,
\m qbeř i dd ɣa yadef ɣar ddeɛwet
\m zzat i uɣembub n Arebbi.
\b
\m 
\v 24 Iřebbez jjwaḥeř břa aseqsi
\m uca igga inneɣni deg wemcan nsen.
\m 
\v 25 Maɣar Netta issen timegga nsen,
\m issneqřab i-ten di ǧiřet uca ttwařebzen.
\m 
\v 26 Iccat i-ten jar iɛeffanen,
\m deg ijj wemcan
\m mani ttbeddan \add iwdan\add* ttwařan,
\m 
\v 27 minzi nitni ḥeyyden xas,
\m war ttḥekkiren marra ibriden nnes, \x ◘ \xo 34:27 \xt Izhd. 28:5; Ica. 5:12\x*
\m 
\v 28 maḥend ad xas issiweḍ
\m tɣuyyit n imezřaḍ,
\m u maḥend ad istajeb
\m i iɣuyyan n řmusakin.
\b
\m 
\v 29 Mařa Netta yiwi-dd řhudnet,
\m man wen dayes i ɣa iggin řɛib?
\m Mařa issnuffar aɣembub nnes,
\m wi t ɣa iẓaren?
\m \add Iḥekkem\add* řa x řgens am x bnadem,
\m 
\v 30 ḥima war iḥekkem uřa d ijj n bnadem
\m i itteggen s tnayen n wudmawen,
\m u ḥima war ttiřint \add ɛad\add* txecifin i řgens.
\m 
\v 31 Mři inna \add bnadem nni\add* i Arebbi
\m ‘Ssgeɛɛdeɣ ixef inu,
\m war ttɛiwideɣ ad ggeɣ řɣar.
\m 
\v 32 Min war ttwiřiɣ, sɣar ayi t Cek!
\m Mařa ggiɣ min war iseggden,
\m war t tteggeɣ ɛad.’
\b
\m 
\v 33 Ma ittxeṣṣa ad ixřef Netta
\m am mammec t texsed cek?
\m Aqa tesseḥqared \add t\add*!
\m Aqa texsed ad tixḍared s yixef nnec,
\m necc \add maca\add* lla!
\m Mařa \add ittɣiř ac\add* aqa tessned tt, ini tt!
\m 
\v 34 Iryazen s řefhamet ad ayi inin,
\m am \add qaɛ\add* aryaz amiɣis ittesřa-dd ɣari,
\m 
\v 35 aqa Ayub war issiweř s tussna,
\m aqa awařen nnes břa řefhamet \add i yeǧan\add*.
\m 
\v 36 Iwa, ejj Ayub ad ittwaqeǧeb ař aneggar,
\m minzi ittarra-dd
\m am iryazen \add ccuren s\add* řmuɛṣiyyet.
\m 
\v 37 Maɣar i ddenb nnes yarenni \add ɛad\add* aɛeddi,
\m jar aneɣ iccat camxa s ifassen
\m u ttmarenyen wawařen nnes
\m ḍidd i Arebbi.
\b
\b
\c 35
\s1 Řhard wiss třata n Ilihu: Tasegda n bnadem war tneffeɛ zzat i Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 Yarra-dd \bd Ilihu\bd*, inna:
\m 
\v 2 Ma ittɣiř ac aya nican, aqa teqqared:
\m ‘Tasegda inu ktar x tenni n Arebbi’?
\m 
\v 3 Maɣar tennid: ‘Man řefḍeř ɣarek?
\m Min d ayi dd ɣa ikkaren
\m aqa necc war tteggeɣ ddnub?’ \x ◘ \xo 35:3 \xt Ayub 34:9\x*
\m 
\v 4 Ad xak dd-arreɣ,
\m uřa x imeddukkař nnec \add akidek\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Xzar ajenna, u xzar,
\m ḥekkar iseynuten tiwa nnec qaɛ!
\m 
\v 6 Mařa texḍid,
\m min i d as tᵉttegged s man aya?
\m Mařa iɛeddiyen nnec d aṭṭas,
\m min zzayes i d as i ɣa tawyed?
\m 
\v 7 Mařa cek d amsegged,
\m min i d as tᵉtticed \add s uya\add*,
\m niɣ min itteṭṭef Netta zeg ufus nnec? \x ◘ \xo 35:7 \xt Ayub 22:2; Izhd. 16:2; Rum. 11:35\x*
\m 
\v 8 Aqa tuɛeffna nnec
\m \add třeqqef\add* aryaz am cek \add waha\add*,
\m u tasegda nnec \add tᵉttiři\add*
\m di ṭṭweɛ n ijj n mmis n bnadem \add waha\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Sɣuyyun zeg waṭṭas n řeḥṣarat,
\m ttřaɣan ɣar twiza
\m zi ssibbet n uɣiř n ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa.
\m 
\v 10 \add Maca\add* uřa d ijjen iqqar:
\m ‘Mani iǧa Arebbi, wenni d ayi iggin,
\m wenni itticen izřan n uṣebbeḥ di ǧiřet,
\m 
\v 11 wenni d aneɣ isseřmaden
\m s řmař n temmurt,
\m d wenni d aneɣ itteggen d imiɣisen
\m s ijḍaḍ n ujenna?’
\m 
\v 12 Dinni sɣuyyun nitni,
\m \add maca\add* Netta war dd-ittarri,
\m zi ssibbet n nnfaxet n iɛeffanen. \x ◘ \xo 35:12 \xt Ayub 27:9; Awřn. 1:28; 15:29; Ica. 1:15; Irm. 11:11; Yḥ. 9:31\x*
\m 
\v 13 S tidett, Arebbi war ittesři
\m ɣar \add iɣuyyan\add* ibeṭṭřen,
\m Amzemmar x kuřci war \add kides\add* iřehhi.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Waxxa cek teqqared,
\m aqa cek war t tᵉttwiřid,
\m tᵉttɣima tmesřact \add ɛad\add* zzat i wudem nnes.
\m Raja t xenni.
\m 
\v 15 Mařa řexxu axeyyeq nnes
\m war iccit ɛad,
\m ma \add xenni\add* Netta war issin
\m x uɛeddi imɣar? \x ◘ \xo 35:15 \xt Ayub 11:6\x*
\m 
\v 16 Ayub icarreg aqemmum nnes baṭeř,
\m ittegg awařen imeqqranen nhřa tussna.
\b
\b
\c 36
\s1 Řhard wiss arebɛa n Ilihu x ujarreb d weɛqab ɣar Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 Yarni \bd Ilihu\bd* \add deg wawař\add*, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ṣbar cwayt akidi,
\m \add xenni\add* necc ad ac ssecneɣ,
\m aqa din ɛad řesbab \add ktar\add*
\m di ṭṭweɛ n \add tmesřact n\add* Arebbi.
\m 
\v 3 Necc ad dd-awyeɣ tussna inu
\m zi řaggʷaj,
\m ad neɛmeɣ tasegda
\m n wenni d ayi dd-ixeřqen.
\m 
\v 4 Maɣar s tidett,
\m awařen inu war ǧin d ixarriqen,
\m aqa \add da\add* zzatek wenni d bu-tussna s tidett.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Xzar, Arebbi imɣar aṭṭas,
\m \add maca\add* war isseḥqiri \add ḥed\add*,
\m imɣar jjhed n řefhamet \add nnes\add*. \x ◘ \xo 36:5 \xt Ayub 9:4; 12:13, 16; 37:23; 38:23\x*
\m 
\v 6 Aɛeffan war t ittejji ad iddar,
\m \add maca\add* i imezřaḍ ittaɣ asen tasɣart \add nsen\add*.
\m 
\v 7 Netta war issḥeyyid tiṭṭawin nnes
\m x umsegged,
\m \add maca\add* issɣimi ten i řebda
\m x řɛarc ak-d ijeǧiden,
\m \add uca ammu\add* i ɣa ttwassuɛřan. \x ◘ \xo 36:7 \xt Izhd. 33:18; 34:16; 113:8\x*
\b
\m 
\v 8 Mařa ttwawten nitni di řegyuḍ,
\m ttwaḥebbsen di ssnaseř n řeɣben,
\m 
\v 9 \add xenni\add* isscen asen timegga nsen
\m d iɛeddiyen nsen,
\m aqa mɣaren aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 10 Yarezzem amezzuɣ nsen i uwebbex,
\m iqqar asen ad dd-dewřen
\m zi řmuɛṣiyyet \add nsen\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 11 Mařa sřin u sexxaren as,
\m ad ssqefřen deg wefřaḥ ussan nsen
\m u di zzhar iseggʷusa nsen.
\m 
\v 12 \add Maca\add* mařa war sřin,
\m ad ttwahellken s lansa,
\m ad ssuffɣen buḥbeř
\m am war ɣarsen teǧi bu tussna.
\b
\m 
\v 13 Nitni inni issniɛmiřen deg wuř \add nsen\add*,
\m ttsettafen aɣḍab,
\m war tᵉttaren aɛawen
\m mařa Netta icarf i-ten.
\m 
\v 14 Řeɛmar nsen ad immet
\m umi nitni \add ɛad\add* di temẓi,
\m \add maɣar\add* ddaren jar imetleyyen. \x ◘ \xo 36:14 \xt Ayub 22:16\x*
\m 
\v 15 Ad ifekk amezřuḍ di řeɣben nnes,
\m di ddeǧ ad yarzem amezzuɣ nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Ammu i ɣa iɛarren uřa d cek
\m zeg wuḍuf n řeḥṣaret,
\m ɣar ttasiɛ mani war ittiři ɛad unedqef,
\m mani i ɣa tiři ṭṭabřa nnec
\m teccur \add s macca\add* i dayes tadunt. \x ◘ \xo 36:16 \xt Izhd. 23:5\x*
\m 
\v 17 \add Maca\add* cek tennuɣed
\m di ccreɛ ak-d uɛeffan,
\m \add maca\add* ddeɛwet d tenfuč
\m ttasent-i-dd ak-d wayawaya.
\m 
\v 18 Ḥḍa aqa asɛar
\m war cek ittɣarri i ustehzi
\m u řqedd n ddeyyet
\m war cek issuffuɣ zeg webrid.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Ma iɣuyyan nnec
\m ad cek ssaren zi řeḥṣaret,
\m niɣ marra min tᵉttegged
\m s marra tizemmar nnec?
\m 
\v 20 War ttmeẓri di ǧiřet,
\m xmi ɣa ttwakksen řegnus
\m zeg wemcan nsen.
\m 
\v 21 Ḥḍa ixef nnec, war ggur
\m x uɣezdis mani ittwaff řɣecc,
\m aqa cek ad tixdared aya x waḍar.
\b
\m 
\v 22 Xzar, Arebbi issɛuǧa s jjehd nnes,
\m man wen iǧan d Amseřmad am Netta?
\m 
\v 23 Man wen i d as isscanen abrid?
\m Niɣ man wen i d as innan:
\m ‘Cek teggid řɣecc’? \x ◘ \xo 36:23 \xt Aɛwd. 32:4; 2 Im. 19:7; Ayub 8:3; 34:10; Rum. 9:14\x*
\m 
\v 24 Ɛqeř ad tessɛuǧid
\m řxedmet \add n ifassen\add* nnes,
\m \add řxedmet nnes\add* i zi ttɣennajen iwdan.
\m 
\v 25 Kuř bnadem ittwařa tt,
\m zi řaggʷaj ttwařan \add tt\add* iwdan.
\b
\m 
\v 26 Xzar, Arebbi d ameqqran,
\m war nzemmar ad as nefhem,
\m řqedd n iseggʷusa nnes
\m war nzemmar ad \add dayes\add* narzu. \x ◘ \xo 36:26 \xt Izhd. 90:2; 92:9; 93:2; 102:13; Ica. 63:16; Igjd. 5:19; Dan. 6:27; Ɛbr. 1:12\x*
\m 
\v 27 Maɣar Netta ijebbed
\m tuddimin n waman,
\m tinni dd-ittwakksen zi tayyut
\m \add xenni\add* dewřent d anẓar,
\m 
\v 28 \add anẓar\add* nni zi ttnesnisin iseynuten,
\m \add anẓar\add* nni dd iweṭṭan
\m s ufeyyeḍ x iwdan.
\m 
\v 29 Man wen ittḥakan \add ɛemmarṣ\add*
\m deg ubezzeɛ n iseynuten,
\m uřa d řḥess isseggwaden
\m zi Texzant nnes?
\b
\m 
\v 30 Xzar, ittbezzeɛ tafawt nnes
\m tiwa n Yixef nnes,
\m ittřeḥḥaf \add zzayes\add*
\m ṭṭřufa yuǧɣen qaɛ n řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 36:30 \xt Izhd. 8:2\x*
\m 
\v 31 Maɣar s uya ittcarreɛ řegnus.
\m Itticc macca s waṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 36:31 \xt Ayub 37:13\x*
\m 
\v 32 Ittcurra ifassen nnes s tfawt,
\m iweṣṣa tt ad teřqef tandayt.
\m 
\v 33 Aḍarḍeḥ \add n wassamen\add* ittbarreḥ zzayes,
\m uřa d taḥimart \add tᵉttbarreḥ\add*
\m aqa Netta ad dd-yas.
\b
\b
\c 37
\s1 Akemmeř n řhard wiss arebɛa n Ilihu: řemɣaret n Arebbi di ṭṭabiɛa
\m 
\v 1 Wah, s uya ittarjij wuř inu,
\m ineṭṭu zeg wemcan nnes.
\m 
\v 2 Sřem mliḥ i zzhir n tmijja nnes,
\m i wejdab \add n wajjaj\add* i dd-ittekken
\m zeg uqemmum nnes. \x ◘ \xo 37:2 \xt Izhd. 29:3\x*
\m 
\v 3 Issekk i-t sadu marra ajenna,
\m uca \add issekk\add* tafawt nnes
\m ař ineggura n temmurt.
\m 
\v 4 Awarni as izehhar s tmijja \add ijehden\add*,
\m ihemhem s tmijja n lɛaḍama nnes
\m u war imenneɛ \add assamen\add*,
\m mařa tᵉttwaseř tmijja nnes.
\m 
\v 5 Arebbi iddardiḥ s tmijja nnes
\m s tebridt n řeɛjeb,
\m ittegg řeḥwayej timeqqranin,
\m neccin war asent nfehhem. \x ◘ \xo 37:5 \xt Ayub 5:9; 9:10; 36:26\x*
\b
\m 
\v 6 Maɣar iqqar i wedfeř:
\m ‘Wḍa ɣar temmurt!’,
\m uca \add xenni\add* ad dd-yas wenẓar,
\m anẓar iccaten s iɣezran nnes ijehden. \x ◘ \xo 37:6 \xt Izhd. 147:16\x*
\m 
\v 7 Netta ittcemmeɛ afus n mkuř bnadem,
\m ḥima marra iwdan ad ssnen,
\m aqa d řexdayem nnes.
\m 
\v 8 Řewḥuc ttnuffaren di řemrageḥ
\m u ttɣiman deg ifran nsen.
\m 
\v 9 Tettas-dd tḥaryaḍt z
\m eg wexxam nnes n daxeř
\m u ak-d usemmiḍ n ccamal
\m \add tᵉttas-dd\add* uřa d tesmeḍ.
\m 
\v 10 S usuḍi n nnefs \add nnes\add*
\m ittawi-dd Arebbi ajris,
\m jemden waṭṭas n waman. \x ◘ \xo 37:10 \xt Ayub 38:29, 30; Izhd. 147:17, 18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Wah, ittɛemmar iseynuten s tuffet,
\m ittbezzeɛ aseynu n tfawt nnes.
\m 
\v 12 Wanita ittraḥ ittas-dd,
\m mammec t ineddeh Netta,
\m ḥima ad ggen marra
\m min i d asen yumur
\m x wudem n temmurt, x temmurt.
\m 
\v 13 Ad taf ad t tẓared am yijj n weɛmud,
\m niɣ am i \add řefḍeř\add* n temmurt,
\m niɣ am \add wescan n\add* tmexsa icuwwaren. \x ◘ \xo 37:13 \xt Uf. 9:18, 23; 1 Ṣm. 12:18, 19; Ɛiz. 10:9; Ayub 36:31\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 Ewc amezzuɣ i man aya, \add a\add* Ayub,
\m bedd, \add sqar\add*, u ḥḍa x řeɛjayeb n Arebbi.
\m 
\v 15 Ma tessned
\m mammec i xasen iḍebbar Arebbi,
\m mammec issruɣa tfawt n useynu nnes?
\m 
\v 16 Ma tessned
\m mammec tteḥraran iseynuten,
\m \add ma tessned\add* řeɛjayeb
\m n wenni ɣar teǧa tussna tmun.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Cek, wenni umi iḥemma warruḍ,
\m mařa Netta issarsa tammurt
\m s arriḥ n ljanub,
\m 
\v 18 ma tbezzɛed akides řqubbet n ujenna,
\m tenni \add din\add* ibedden
\m am yict n tisit ifesyen? \x ◘ \xo 37:18 \xt Amz. 1:6\x*
\m 
\v 19 Sargeb aneɣ cek min i d as ɣa nini,
\m maɣar neccin war \add nzemmar\add*
\m ad nfessar walu mliḥ zzates
\m zi ssibbet n taǧest.
\m 
\v 20 Ma ad as hajan, aqa ssiwřeɣ \add ammu\add*?
\m Mařa ca n yijjen ad \add tt\add* yini,
\m ad ittwaṣarḍ nican. \f ◼ \fr 37:20 \fk ad ittwaṣard nican\ft - ixs ad yini s lɣaḍab n SIDI.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 21 Řexxu war ittwiři \add bnadem\add* tafawt,
\m tenni yareqqen deg iseynuten,
\m \add maca\add* mařa iɛdu usuḍi n usemmiḍ,
\m aqa ifarreḍ i-ten.
\m 
\v 22 Zi ccamal ittas-dd wureɣ,
\m tissiqt issaggʷaden \add tarsa\add* x Arebbi.
\m 
\v 23 Amzemmar x kuřci,
\m wenni war nzemmar ad t naf,
\m wenni d ameqqran di jjehd,
\m Netta war ittdeǧi řḥeqq
\m d tsegda ifeyyḍen. \x ◘ \xo 37:23 \xt Ayub 9:4; 12:13, 16; 36:5; Izhd. 99:4\x*
\m 
\v 24 S uya tteggʷeden zzayes iwdan,
\m Netta war ixezzar
\m ɣar yinni \add iḥessben ixef nsen\add* d imiɣisen.
\b
\b
\c 38
\s1 Arebbi issiweř ak-d Ayub x wexřaq n marra min iǧan
\m 
\v 1 Awarni as yarra-dd \bd SIDI\bd* x Ayub zi tḥaryaḍt, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Man wen issbarrcnen acawar,
\m s wawařen břa tussna? \x ◘ \xo 38:2 \xt Ayub 42:3\x*
\m 
\v 3 Byes \add xenni\add* tijɛinnatin nnec am weryaz.
\m Necc xseɣ ad cek sseqsiɣ
\m u cek, arr-dd xafi!
\b
\m 
\v 4 Mani cek tuɣa
\m umi ggiɣ Necc dsas n tammurt?
\m Ini t mařa ɣarek řefhamet \add s tidett\add*. \x ◘ \xo 38:4 \xt Awřn. 8:29\x*
\m 
\v 5 Man wen iggin řeɛbar nnes,
\m \add wah,\add* cek tessned tt,
\m \add ma war iǧi amenni\add*?
\m Man wen xas imeḥḍen afiřu n řeɛbar?
\m 
\v 6 Min xef hwan dsusa nnes,
\m niɣ man wen issarsen
\m aẓru n teɣmart nnes,
\m 
\v 7 umi itran n ṣṣbeh
\m ɣennjen \add jmiɛ\add* s řefraḥet,
\m umi sřiwřewen
\m marra arrawen n AREBBI?
\b
\m 
\v 8 Man wen ibellɛen řebḥar s tewwura,
\m umi dd-idduqqez
\m uca iffeɣ-dd zeg uɛeddis n yemmas, \x ◘ \xo 38:8 \xt Amz. 1:9; Ayub 26:10; Izhd. 33:7; 104:9; Awřn. 8:29; Irm. 5:22\x*
\m 
\v 9 umi d as ggiɣ iseynuten d arruḍ nnes,
\m ijj n useynu ibbumbes d amendiř
\m maḥend ad dayes t ssehnunnḍeɣ,
\m 
\v 10 umi d as arẓiɣ afray inu
\m \add am ijj n weḥfur yuǧɣen\add*,
\m u umi d as ggiɣ aɛmud
\m i ubelleɛ d tewwura,
\m 
\v 11 nniɣ: ‘Ař da i dd ɣa tased, war ɛeddu.
\m Danita ad tᵉttwassbedd
\m nnfaxet n řemwaj nnec.’
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ma tumured cek \add ateffu n\add* ṣṣbeḥ
\m deg wussan nnec?
\m Ma tesscaned i tfawt n řefjar
\m amcan nnes,
\m 
\v 13 maḥend ad tᵉṭṭef afriwen n temmurt,
\m ařami ad zzayes zzerzen iɛeffanen?
\m 
\v 14 Ad tedweř \add temmurt\add*
\m am tarrist \add sadu\add* ṭṭabeɛ,
\m \add marra timesřayin\add*
\m ad \add xas\add* ttwassbeddent \add ɛawed\add*
\m am mammec i teǧa ijj n warruḍ.
\m 
\v 15 Iɛeffanen ad asen tᵉttwakkes
\m tfawt nsen
\m u aɣiř ittwassgeɛɛden
\m ad ittwarẓ.
\b
\m 
\v 16 Ma tiwḍed ɣar řɛunṣarat n řebḥar,
\m ma tuyured \add ɛemmarṣ\add* x wudem
\m n \add temmurt\add* n \add waman\add* ihewřen?
\m 
\v 17 Ma ttwaɛarrant
\m tewwura n řmewt i cek,
\m ma teẓrid tiwwura n tiři n řmewt?
\m 
\v 18 Ma tᵉttawi-dd řefhamet nnec
\m ař ineggura n temmurt?
\m Ini t mařa tessned aya marra.
\m 
\v 19 Mani iǧa webrid ɣar tzeddiɣt n tfawt?
\m U taǧest, mani teǧa tzeddiɣt nnes,
\m 
\v 20 ḥima ad tzemmared ad tt tnedhed
\m ɣar wemcan nnes,
\m u ad tessned mliḥ imesraq
\m ɣar taddart nnes?
\m 
\v 21 Cek aqa tessned man aya \add niɣ\add*,
\m minzi cek tuɣa txeřqed, \add niɣ lla?\add*
\m U \add ma war iǧi\add*
\m řqedd n wussan nnec d aṭṭas?
\b
\m 
\v 22 Ma tudfed ɣar ixxamen
\m n řexzen n wedfeř,
\m \add ma\add* teẓrid řehrit n tebruri,
\m 
\v 23 nni x ceṭṭareɣ i řweqt n řeḥṣaret,
\m i wass n garra d umenɣi?
\m 
\v 24 Mani iǧa webrid ittbeṭṭan tifawt,
\m uřa d \add abrid\add* i zi ittwabezzeɛ
\m usemmiḍ n ccarq x temmurt?
\m 
\v 25 Man wen ifeǧeq řmizab
\m i řḥemřet n wenẓar,
\m uřa d abrid i wassam n wajjajen
\m 
\v 26 ḥima ad issekk anẓar x temmurt
\m nni di war \add izdiɣ\add* ḥed,
\m x řexřa i war di \add izdiɣ\add* uřa d ijj,
\m 
\v 27 ḥima ad issarwa
\m jjwayeh ixřan u ittwaxřan
\m u ḥima ad isseɣmi arbiɛ d ṭṭri? \x ◘ \xo 38:27 \xt Izhd. 107:35\x*
\b
\m 
\v 28 Ma anẓar ɣares ca n babas,
\m niɣ man wen i dd-ittejjan
\m tuddimin n nnda?
\m 
\v 29 Zi man aɛeddis i zi dd-iffeɣ wejris,
\m u nnda ijersen n ujenna,
\m wi i-t-i-dd-yurwen?
\m 
\v 30 Ddakkwařen waman am weẓru
\m uca ijars wudem n \add waman\add* ihewřen.
\b
\m 
\v 31 Ma tzemmared ad tcedded
\m Agraw n Sebɛa n Yetran,
\m niɣ tfessyed ssnaseř \add n yetran\add* n Uriyun? \x ◘ \xo 38:31 \xt Ayub 9:9; Ɛam. 5:8\x*
\m 
\v 32 Ma tzemmared ad dd-tessuffɣed
\m itran n Zudyak ɣar řḥař nsen,
\m uřa d Ddub \add Ameqqran\add* ak-d tarwa nnes?
\m 
\v 33 Ma tessned izerfan n ujenna,
\m niɣ tzemmared ad tḍebbared
\m x uqarri nsen di temmurt? \x ◘ \xo 38:33 \xt Irm. 31:35\x*
\b
\m 
\v 34 Ma tzemmared ad tessgeɛɛded
\m ɣar iseynuten tmijja nnec,
\m ařami cek i ɣa tdeř
\m ict n řḥemřet n waman?
\m 
\v 35 Ma tzemmared ad tessekked assamen
\m maḥend ad qeǧqen,
\m ad ac inin: ‘Aqa-neɣ da’?
\m 
\v 36 Man wen issarsen tiɣit
\m di daxeř \add n bnadem\add*?
\m Niɣ man wen iwcin řefhamet i řeɛqeř? \x ◘ \xo 38:36 \xt Ayub 32:8; Amb. 2:26; Dan. 1:17\x*
\m 
\v 37 Man wen ifarrzen iseynuten s řeɛqeř,
\m iɣarrafen \add n waman\add* n ujenna
\m wi ten ittzeǧaɛen,
\m 
\v 38 ařami ittwafsiy ucař,
\m idweř d abeǧaɛ,
\m uca řesqen ibursa n temmurt?
\b
\m 
\v 39 Ma tzemmared
\m ad tᵉṭṭfed zzardet i tayradt,
\m niɣ ad tesseřhud
\m řaẓ n wayraden imeẓyanen, \x ◘ \xo 38:39 \xt Izhd. 104:21\x*
\m 
\v 40 řami nuffaren deg ifran nsen,
\m u ttḥaman zi řemrageḥ nsen?
\m 
\v 41 Man wen issewjaden
\m i ubaɣeř macca nnes,
\m xmi sɣuyyun imeẓyanen nnes
\m ɣar Arebbi,
\m xmi ttemhafan nhřa macca? \x ◘ \xo 38:41 \xt Izhd. 147:9; Mt. 6:26\x*
\b
\b
\c 39
\m 
\v 1 Ma tessned meřmi ttarwent
\m tɣaydin n tṣuḍar?
\m Ma tḥeṭṭid tirwa n tudadin? \x ◘ \xo 39:1 \xt Izhd. 29:9\x*
\m 
\v 2 Ma tzemmared ad tḥesbed
\m iyuren n tkessit nsent,
\m ma tessned řḥař n tirwa nsent?
\m 
\v 3 Nitenti tteqwisent,
\m ttarwent imeẓyanen nsent,
\m řewjeɛ n tarut nsent ssuffuɣen ten.
\m 
\v 4 Meḥḍen imeẓyanen nsent,
\m meqqaren di řexřa,
\m tteffɣen ɣar barra
\m u war ɣarsent ttɛiqqiben.
\b
\m 
\v 5 Man wen yarxun i weɣyuř n řexřa
\m u tisarrifin n weɣyuř n řexřa,
\m man wen tent ifesyen?
\m 
\v 6 Necc wciɣ as tanezruft d taddart,
\m řewḍa ameǧaḥ d tizeddiɣin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 39:6 \xt Ayub 24:5; Irm. 2:24\x*
\m 
\v 7 Netta iḍeḥḥec
\m x řɣaci inhewřen n tendint,
\m war ittesři iɣuyyan
\m n yinni izeyyaren \add isemɣan\add*.
\m 
\v 8 Jjwayeh n idurar
\m d ddmani nnes n tarewsa,
\m yarezzu \add daysen\add* x qaɛ min iǧan d aziza.
\b
\m 
\v 9 Ma ad ixs iɣayḍ n řexřa
\m ak-d waccawen d iziraren
\m ad xak isexxar?
\m Ma ad issens ɣar řmedwed nnec?
\m 
\v 10 Ma tzemmared ad tmenɛed
\m iɣayḍ n řexřa
\m ak-d waccawen d iziraren
\m s wesɣun nnes ɣar uɛeyyed \add n wecraz\add*?
\m Ma ad icarz tiysarin awarni ac?
\m 
\v 11 Ma tᵉttcařed xas,
\m minzi netta ijhed aṭṭas,
\m ma ad as tejjid řxedmet nnec?
\m 
\v 12 Ma ad xas tᵉttecřed
\m ad \add ɣarek\add* dd-yarr zzariɛet nnec,
\m ad tt yawi ɣar unedrar nnec?
\b
\m 
\v 13 Afriwen n nnɛamet ccaten s řxaḍar.
\m Maca ma aqa-ten d afriwen
\m d warric idařfen n ubellarj? \f ◼ \fr 39:13 \fk nnɛamet\ft - niɣ ‘tanhalt’ (tinhalin)\f*
\m 
\v 14 Maɣar tᵉttejja timeǧařin nnes
\m deg ucař n temmurt,
\m tᵉttejja i-tent tteḥmant deg ijdi.
\m 
\v 15 Tᵉttᵉttu aqa ijj n uḍar
\m izemmar ad tent iřbez,
\m aqa řewḥuc n řexřa
\m zemmaren ad xasent ɛefsen.
\m 
\v 16 Nettat tqesseḥ deg imeẓyanen nnes
\m axmi war ǧin nnes.
\m Baṭeř i tᵉttegg tizemmar nnes,
\m maɣar nettat war tkessi s wemnus,
\m 
\v 17 maɣar Arebbi ijja i-tt ad tᵉttu tiɣit,
\m war d as iwci bu tesɣart di řefhamet.
\m 
\v 18 \add Maca\add* mařa teksi deg uḍar nnes,
\m tessgeɛɛad ixef nnes,
\m tḍeḥḥec x uyis d wenni xas inyin.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Ma tzemmared ad tewced jjehd i uyis?
\m Ma tzemmared ad tessyarḍed
\m ijiman nnes s ssbib?
\m 
\v 20 Ma tzemmared ad t yarr ineṭṭu
\m am uburxes?
\m Řɛezz n usneḥneḥ nnes
\m issaggʷad aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 21 Xebbcen \add iysan\add* s iḍaren nsen
\m \add am ttrajan\add* di řewḍa n teɣzurt,
\m ifarḥ \add uyis\add* s jjehd nnes,
\m itteffeɣ, maḥend ad immeřqa
\m ak-d řesnaḥ.
\m 
\v 22 Iḍeḥḥec x marra min issaggʷaden,
\m war ittnexřiɛ zi walu,
\m war iddikkwiř ɣar ḍeffar zi ssif.
\m 
\v 23 Ittqarqub weqrab n fřitcat
\m sennej nnes,
\m lansa d fřitca ttissiqen.
\m 
\v 24 S ddriz \add n tceḍyin\add* d zzɛamet
\m iṣarreḍ tammurt,
\m war izemmar ad ittwassbedd
\m ɣar usuḍi n uyicc n icarri.
\m 
\v 25 Ɣar tmijja n usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri
\m issneḥniḥ: ‘Heheh!’
\m Ittaca ak-d umenɣi zi řaggʷaj,
\m zzga n řḥukkam d iɣuyyan n umenɣi.
\b
\m 
\v 26 Ma iṭṭaw řbaz zi řefhamet nnec,
\m aqa ittbezzaɛ afriwen nnes ɣar ljanub?
\m 
\v 27 Ma issgeɛɛad ugidar ixef nnes
\m sennej qaɛ s řumur nnec,
\m ittegg řɛucc nnes di řuɛřa? \x ◘ \xo 39:27 \xt Irm. 49:16; Ɛub. 4\x*
\m 
\v 28 Izeddeɣ u issnusa x jjarf,
\m x ucenqub n jjarf, aqa-t d lburj \add nnes\add*.
\m 
\v 29 Ssenni iḥeṭṭa zzardet,
\m tiṭṭawin nnes xezzarent i-tt-dd
\m zi řaggʷaj.
\m 
\v 30 Imeẓyanen nnes sekkfen idammen
\m u mani ǧan inni ittwanɣen, aqa-t din \add i yeǧa\add*. \x ◘ \xo 39:30 \xt Mt. 24:28; Lk. 17:37\x*
\b
\b
\c 40
\s1 SIDI issiweř ak-d Ayub
\m 
\v 1 Yarni yarra-dd \bd SIDI\bd* x Ayub, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 Ma ixs wenni ittemcarraɛen
\m ak-d Umzemmar x kuřci ad \add t\add* iseggem?
\m Ejj wenni ixsen ad idɛa Arebbi,
\m ad dd-yarr!
\b
\m 
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd \bd Ayub\bd* x SIDI, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 4 Xzar, necc drus,
\m min zemmareɣ ad xak dd-arreɣ?
\m Necc ad ggeɣ afus inu x uqemmum inu. \x ◘ \xo 40:4 \xt Izhd. 39:10\x*
\m 
\v 5 Aqa ssiwřeɣ ict n twařa,
\m \add maca\add* war dd-ttarriɣ \add ɛad\add*.
\m twařa wiss tnayen war \add d as\add* arenniɣ!
\b
\m 
\v 6 \add Xas uca\add* yarni yarra-dd \bd SIDI\bd* x Ayub zi tḥaryaḍt, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 7 Byes \add xenni\add* tijɛinnatin nnec am weryaz.
\m Necc xseɣ ad cek sseqsiɣ
\m u cek, arr-dd xafi!
\m 
\v 8 Ma texsed s tidett ad tarẓed řḥukm inu?
\m Ma texsed ad ɣari dd-tarred řɛib,
\m maḥend ad tbaned cek d amsegged? \x ◘ \xo 40:8 \xt Izhd. 51:6; Rum. 3:4\x*
\m 
\v 9 Ma ɣarek aɣiř am Arebbi?
\m Ma tzemmared ad teddardḥed
\m am wajjaj s tmijja \add nnec\add*?
\b
\m 
\v 10 Qqen xenni ixef nnec
\m s lɛaḍama d uɛuǧi,
\m arḍ s tissiqt d řɛezz.
\m 
\v 11 Ejj aduqqez n ufugem nnec ad izeǧeɛ,
\m xzar ɣar kuř bu nnfaxet,
\m uca sehwa i-t!
\m 
\v 12 Xzar mliḥ ɣar mkuř bu-nnfaxet,
\m sehwa i-t,
\m řbez iɛeffanen deg wemcan nsen.
\m 
\v 13 Ffar i-ten marra am munen deg ucař,
\m cfen iɣembab nsen
\m di tnuffra \add sadu tammurt\add*.
\m 
\v 14 Xenni uřa d Necc ad cek ssemɣareɣ,
\m minzi afus nnec afusi issenjem i cek.
\b
\m 
\v 15 Xzar maca Řweḥc, \add ‘Bᵉhimut’\add*,
\m wenni ggiɣ am mammec cek ggiɣ.
\m Ittett arbiɛ am ufunas.
\m 
\v 16 Xzar jjehd nnes di tejɛinnatin nnes,
\m řɛezz nnes deg iẓewran nnes n uɛeddis!
\m 
\v 17 Mařa ixs, ad igg akennas nnes
\m am tcejjart n tengelt,
\m iẓewran n tmeṣṣaḍin nnes
\m meḥḍen mmuden.
\m 
\v 18 Ixsan nnes tteggen
\m am yiqudas n nnḥas,
\m am barrat n wuzzař
\m iḍaren d iɣaǧen nnes.
\b
\m 
\v 19 Netta d amezwaru n ibriden n Arebbi.
\m Wenni t yeggin, iwca as ssif nnes.
\m 
\v 20 Iwa, idurar ttawyen as-dd arbiɛ,
\m marra řewḥuc n yeyyar ttiraren dinni.
\m 
\v 21 Ibbuzzeř sadu i tcejjura itteggen tiři,
\m deg udurri n uɣanim, di ssebxet.
\m 
\v 22 Ad xas dduryent tcejjura i itticen tiři,
\m kuř ict s tiři nnes,
\m tinemrač n tɣezratin ttennḍent as-dd.
\m 
\v 23 Xzar, mařa ihaj yeɣzar, war ittarjiji,
\m ittɣima yarsa mařa řḥemřet n L’Urdun
\m tudef as-dd ɣar uqemmum.
\m 
\v 24 Ma izemmar \add bnadem\add* ad t iṭṭef
\m \add am ixezzar netta nican\add* di tiṭṭawin nnes,
\m ad as issnuqqeb tinzart s tesɣunin?
\b
\m 
\v 25 Ma tzemmared ad tjebded ‘Liviyatan’
\m s tsennart n weymar,
\m niɣ ad tessehwid iřes nnes
\m deg ufiřu \add n weymar\add*?
\m 
\v 26 Ma tzemmared ad as tegged
\m taxadent n uɣanim di tenzart nnes,
\m niɣ ad tessnuqqbed
\m aɣesmir nnes s uɣanču?
\m 
\v 27 Ma ad zzayek ittar aḥinni?
\m Ma ad issiweř akidek
\m s wawařen imiziḍen?
\m 
\v 28 Ma ad yegg akidek řɛahd?
\m Ma tzemmared ad t teksid
\m d ismeɣ i řebda?
\m 
\v 29 Ma tzemmared akides tᵉttirared
\m am ak-d ijj n ujḍiḍ,
\m niɣ ad t teqqned i teḥramin nnec?
\b
\m 
\v 30 Ma zemmaren ineymaren
\m ad dayes sebbeben?
\m Ma zemmaren ad t bḍan
\m jar ayt n Kenɛan?
\m 
\v 31 Ma tzemmared ad tejjud
\m tiřmect nnes s fřitcat,
\m niɣ s lansa n iseřman azeǧif nnes?
\m 
\v 32 Sars xas afus nnec,
\m xemm ɣar umenɣi,
\m war t tteggid ɛemmarṣ ɛad.
\b
\b
\c 41
\m 
\v 1 Xzar, \add qaɛ\add* araji ad ifceř,
\m mɣir tamuɣři nnes
\m tesseɛgaz \add bnadem\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 2 War iǧi uřa d ijjen ammu d azeɛɛam
\m ařami t i ɣa ihweř,
\m man wen \add xenni\add* izemmaren
\m ad iqqim ibedd
\m zzat i uɣembub inu?
\m 
\v 3 Man wen i d ayi iwcin \add ca\add* d amezwaru,
\m ařami d ayi ittxeṣṣa
\m ad ɣares t-i-dd-arreɣ?
\m Marra min iǧan sadu ijenwan inu! \x ◘ \xo 41:3 \xt Uf. 19:5; Aɛwd. 10:14; Izhd. 24:1; 50:12; Rum. 11:35; 1 Kur. 10:26, 28\x*
\b
\m 
\v 4 Necc war ttesqariɣ x iḍaren nnes,
\m x řemɣaret n jjehd \add nnes\add*
\m u x ucuwwar n waddud nnes.
\m 
\v 5 Man wen izeɛɛmen ad iqejjeɛ
\m taqcurt n warruḍ nnes,
\m man wen izeɛɛmen ad dd-iqarreb
\m ɣar tyuya n řesdud n teɣmas
\m n iɣesmar nnes?
\m 
\v 6 Man wen izemmaren
\m ad yarzem tiwwura
\m ɣar uɣembub nnes?
\m Min innḍen i teɣmas nnes
\m mɣir d anexřiɛ.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Řesdud n tseddariyin
\m x weɛrur nnes cennɛen,
\m \add kuř ijj zzaysen\add* ittwabelleɛ
\m s ṭṭabeɛ iqqnen nican.
\m 
\v 8 Ijjen iqqnen \add nican\add* ɣar ijj n nneɣni,
\m war izemmar ad din dd-yadef
\m arriḥ jar asen.
\m 
\v 9 Řessqen deg wayawya,
\m udfen deg ixef nsen
\m maḥend war temmsebḍin.
\b
\m 
\v 10 Mařa iɛḍes, tᵉttceɛciɛ tfawt,
\m tiṭṭawin nnes ggint
\m am wabřiwen n tfawt n řefjar.
\m 
\v 11 Zeg ujeqmim nnes
\m tteffɣen-dd iṣefḍawen,
\m tifeṭṭutin n tmessi dduqquzent \add zzayes\add*.
\m 
\v 12 Ddexxan ittfewwar
\m zeg ixubac n wenzaren nnes,
\m am zeg ijj n uṭenjir ittnennan
\m s uɣanim idduxxunen.
\m 
\v 13 Twarrit n nnefs nnes tᵉssekkara
\m timessi di řefḥem,
\m zeg uḥerqum nnes
\m itteffeɣ-dd uḥaduq n tmessi.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Jjehd izdeɣ deg ijiman nnes,
\m ɣar zzat nnes ineṭṭu unexřiɛ.
\m 
\v 15 Ṭṭrufa n weysum \add n uɛeddis\add* nnes
\m mmřesqen,
\m am xasen fesyen,
\m war zemmaren ad ttwanhezzen.
\m 
\v 16 Uř nnes iqseḥ am weẓru,
\m iqseḥ am teṣḍart n swadday n tsirt.
\m 
\v 17 Xmi issgeɛɛad ixef nnes,
\m ttnexřaɛen inni ijehden,
\m zeg uqezzeb xeṭṭan di tendayt.
\b
\m 
\v 18 Mařa iřqef i-t ca n yijjen s ssif,
\m war ittiři, \add war iǧi s\add* uḥric,
\m řa s lansa uřa s fřitca.
\m 
\v 19 Uzzař ɣares am uřum,
\m nnḥas am ukeccuḍ yarcan.
\m 
\v 20 Fřitca n řqews war t tesstewwej,
\m iẓra n iǧiy ddakkwařen zzates d aqecqac.
\m 
\v 21 Idebbuzen iḥesseb i-ten am uqecqac,
\m iḍeḥḥec x uzebzeb n uḥric.
\b
\m 
\v 22 Ɣar wadday n \add uɛeddis nnes\add*
\m aqa din iceqfan iqeḍɛen,
\m ittjarra řemwas iqeḍɛen nni
\m \add am teřwiḥt itteḥřuǧuḍen i usarwet\add*
\m tiwa n ubeǧaɛ.
\m 
\v 23 Igga řaǧaɣ ad isstextex am teydart,
\m ittegg řebḥar am umeqraj itthajan.
\m 
\v 24 Ittejja awarni as jjurret
\m tareqq d amesraq,
\m \add aman\add* ihewřen ttbanen
\m am ucuwwaf n umeccaybu.
\m 
\v 25 War din iǧi uřa d ijj x temmurt
\m yarwes dayes,
\m ittwagg ḥima ɛemmarṣ war itteggʷed.
\m 
\v 26 Inḍar tiṭṭawin nnes x marra wi yuɛřan,
\m aqa-t d ajeǧid x marra
\m iyraden imeẓyanen ineffxen.
\b
\b
\c 42
\s1 Ayub inɛem i Arebbi
\m 
\v 1 \bd Ayub\bd* yarra-dd x SIDI, inna:
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Necc ssneɣ
\m aqa Cek tzemmared i kuřci
\m war issbeṭṭiř uřa d ijj n wenway nnec.
\m 
\v 3 \add Cek teqqared:\add*
\m ‘Man wen issbarrcnen břa tussna
\m ccwar \add n Arebbi\add*?’
\m S uya ssiwřeɣ x min war fhimeɣ,
\m x tmesřayin nni di ttbehteɣ aṭṭas,
\m war tent ssineɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 42:3 \xt Ayub 38:2; Izhd. 40:6; 131:1; 139:6\x*
\b
\m 
\v 4 “Seř maca uca ad ssiwřeɣ,
\m xseɣ ad Cek sseqsiɣ
\m uca \add xenni\add* Cek ad ayi \add xas\add* tessargbed.
\m 
\v 5 S umezzuɣ xak i sřiɣ \add waha\add*,
\m maca řexxu tiṭṭ inu teẓri Cek.
\m 
\v 6 X uya ttɛiffiɣ ixef inu uca ndemmeɣ,
\m qqimeɣ di tɛejjajt d yiɣɣeḍ.”
\b
\s1 Arebbi idebbar x weṣřaḥ d usgenfi
\m 
\v 7 Awarni řami tuɣa issiwiř SIDI awařen-a ak-d Ayub, inna SIDI i Ilifaz zi Tayman: “Lɣaḍab inu yarɣa xak u x tnayen n imeddukkař nnec, maɣar kenniw war xafi tessiwřem ca nican am mammec xafi issiweř umsexxar inu Ayub.
\v 8 Xenni řexxu, ksim kenniw sebɛa n ifunasen imeẓyanen d sebɛa n icarriyyen, uca uyurem ɣar umsexxar inu Ayub uca qeddmem ten d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i yixef nwem. Jjem amsexxar inu Ayub ad xawem iẓẓaǧ. Maɣar Necc ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ aɣembub nnes \add i westajeb\add*, ḥima war tteggeɣ akidwem am tubbuheřya nwem, minzi kenniw war xafi tessiwiřem nican am mammec xafi issiwiř umsexxar inu Ayub.”
\b
\m 
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ Ilifaz zi Tayman, Bildad zi Cuḥa d Ṣufar zi Naɛmat uca ggin nitni am mammec d asen inna SIDI. SIDI issgeɛɛed aɣembub n Ayub \add i ustajeb n tẓaǧit nnes\add*.
\v 10 Awarni řami tuɣa ittẓaǧa Ayub di ṭṭweɛ n imeddukkař nnes, inneqřeb SIDI tameḥbast n Ayub i di iǧa netta \add zi ssibbet n řehřac nnes\add*, uca yarni SIDI di marra agřa n Ayub tnayen n tseqqar.
\m 
\v 11 Usin-dd ɣares marra aytmas d marra suyᵉtmas d marra inni t issnen zic. Nitni ccin akides aɣrum di taddart nnes uca ssecnen as aziǧez nsen uca ɛezzan t x marra řɣar xas dd-iɣḍeř SIDI. Iwca as kuř ijjen zzaysen ijj n řewzen n nnuqart uřa d ict n txadent n wureɣ.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ibarek SIDI taneggarut n Ayub ktar zi tmezwarut nnes, maɣar tuɣa ɣares arebɛa-ařaf n wuǧi d setta-ařaf n iřeɣman d wařef n ifunasen n teɣnact d wařef n teɣyař.
\m 
\v 13 Tuɣa ɣares sebɛa n iḥenjiren d třata n yessis. \x ◘ \xo 42:13 \xt Ayub 1:2\x*
\m 
\v 14 Tamezwarut igga as Yamima, wiss tnayen qqaren as Qaṣiɛa d wiss třata qqaren as Qarn-Haffuk.
\v 15 War ufin di marra tammurt tiḥramin cnant am yessis n Ayub. Babatsent iwca asent tasɣart jar aytmatsent.
\m 
\v 16 Ayub iddar awarni i uya mya u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa. Netta iẓra iḥenjiren nnes d iḥenjiren n iḥenjiren nnes \add ɣares ař\add* jjiř wiss arebɛa.
\b
\m 
\v 17 Ayub immut awarni řami iwsar aṭṭas u tuɣa ijjiwen ussan \add n tudart nnes\add*. 
